NK076(mu)001:1: // rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud kyi de kho na nyid snang ba'i brgyan ces bya ba bzhugs so //
NK076(mu)001:2: rnam 'byor chen po'i rgyud kyi de kho na nyid snang ba'i brgyan ces bya ba //
NK076(mu)001:3: 'jam dbyangs mgon po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK076(mu)001:4: chos dbyings mkha' chos sku la rtog pa'i sprin rnams rab zhi zhing //
NK076(mu)001:5: zag med longs sku bde chen d+r+wa ba mtshan gyi 'od zer can //
NK076(mu)001:6: jiltara mos bzhin sprul sku gdul bya'i pad mo rgyas mdzad pa //
NK076(mu)001:7: dkyil 'khor gtso bo sku gsum nyi ma khyod phyag 'tshal //
NK076(mu)001:8: mtha' gnyis dor ba'i rig lam gnyis pa la //
NK076(mu)001:9: gtan tshig 'khor lo'i shugs kyis rab drangs te //
NK076(mu)001:10: ma nor don 'bras gya nom gter gyur pa //
NK076(mu)001:11: dbyer med ston pa'i ngag la'ang phyag 'tshal lo //
NK076(mu)001:12: zab mo de nyid ji bzhin rnam gzigs shing //
NK076(mu)001:13: ma nor gzhung lugs 'jebs dang dri med can //
NK076(mu)001:14: dul ba'i blo gros gzhan la phan brtson pa //
NK076(mu)001:15: chos kyi rje btsun bla ma nyid la 'dud //
NK076(mu)001:16: rig 'dzin sde snod dri med rgya mtsho la //
NK076(mu)001:17: log rtog rba rlabs stong gis 'khrigs gyur kyang //
NK076(mu)001:18: rnam rig 'dab bzang dbang pos rnam phye ste //
NK076(mu)001:19: grub mtha' 'o ma'i snying po bsdus te bshad //
NK076(mu)001:20: brjod bya'i don chen gzhi lam 'bras bu nyid //
NK076(mu)001:21: yongs dag kun khyab gsum gyi gzi ldan zhing //
NK076(mu)001:22: rtog ge srin bu'i 'od stong 'joms byed pa //
NK076(mu)001:23: nges don tshad ma'i ngag 'di mnyan par gyis //
NK076(mu)001:24: nga yi rigs lam me 'od phreng ba 'dir //
NK076(mu)001:25: sdang zhugs phrag dog rlung dag brgyas bskyod na'ang //
NK076(mu)001:26: dpal gyi me lce thur du mi ltung zhing //
NK076(mu)001:27: phyir rgol mun sde bye ba'ang sel byed yin //
NK076(mu)001:28: 'dir theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi lugs shes shing nyams su blang nas /
NK076(mu)001:29: 'gro ba sgrol ba'i ded dpon du phyogs pa'i skyes bu /
NK076(mu)001:30: rgyud sde zab cing rgya che ba dpag par dka'
NK076(mu)001:31: ba dag la dri ma med pa'i blo gros kyi
NK076(mu)001:33: nges par rig pa'i thur ma dag gis ma rig
NK076(mu)001:34: pa'i ling tog sel bar gzo ba rnams kyis legs
NK076(mu)001:35: par gsungs pa la brten pa'i don gsang sngags mtha'
NK076(mu)001:36: dag gi snying po rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud sgyu
NK076(mu)001:37: 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i man ngag 'di la rnam par dbye
NK076(mu)001:38: ba'i don / rnam par bsdu ba'i don /
NK076(mu)001:39: shes bya spyir gtan la dbab pa /
NK076(mu)001:40: shes bya bye brag tu gtan la dbab pa dang bzhis bstan te /
NK076(mu)001:41: dang po ni mtshan gzhi gsang sde bcu gsum las
NK076(mu)001:42: dang po dag la mtshan nyid gnyis med pa 'di
NK076(mu)001:43: nyid kyis mtshon par nus pa'i mtshon bya sgyu 'phrul
NK076(mu)001:44: d+r+wa ba'i chos / rnam par dbye na /
NK076(mu)001:46: rang bzhin bde gshegs gdul bya'i ces pas /
NK076(mu)001:47: shes rab dang gtan tshig kyis chos gsum ldan /
NK076(mu)001:48: ma dpyad pas gzhir gyi snang ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:49: rang bzhin kun rdzob la sgyu ma'i chos drug las log rtog don dang 'gal bar 'dzin pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:50: rten 'brel rgyu rkyen las bskyed gnyis rang bzhin gyi chos su ji ltar rung ba sam na /
NK076(mu)001:51: chos 'ga' zhig mthun gyi gsum char tshang ba'i mtshan
NK076(mu)001:52: nyid pa ni ma yin te don gyi zlas grangs
NK076(mu)001:53: so // 'jug pa'i rnam pa thun mong dang khyad par gyi theg pa gsum dang /
NK076(mu)001:55: tha dad pa gdul bya lam gyi snang ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:56: bral ngo bo nyid thob med pa'i yon tan nar son pa 'bras bu bder gshegs pa'i snang ba'am /
NK076(mu)001:57: zhar rang bzhin gyi las byung ba 'khrul ba'i snang
NK076(mu)001:58: ba ces bzhi yang 'khrul ngo la chos nyid don
NK076(mu)001:59: dam snang ngam mi snang gnyis pa ltar rang bzhin
NK076(mu)001:60: tha dad du thal 'dod na chos nyid rtog par
NK076(mu)001:61: 'khrul snang mi mngon par 'gyur la dang po ltar
NK076(mu)001:62: na so so'i skye bo kun bden mthong du thal
NK076(mu)001:63: ce na / khyab pa ma grub ste snang yang ma nges pa'i phyir rdul phran bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:64: pas snang ba gsum mam bzhir yang bshad /
NK076(mu)001:65: rgyud gsum nges par gsal gsum las gsal byed pa'i zhes pas /
NK076(mu)001:66: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa gzhi yi rgyud /
NK076(mu)001:67: rang bzhin sngon du byed pa thabs kyi rgyud /
NK076(mu)001:68: rang bzhin sngon du 'gyur zhing mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i rgyud de /
NK076(mu)001:69: 'brel gsum ka yang zhing rgyun chags pa'i mtshan nyid
NK076(mu)001:70: can gyi rgyud gzhi dang lam gnyis shes bya shes
NK076(mu)001:71: byed du 'brel / lam dang 'bras bu gnyis thob bya thob byed du 'brel la /
NK076(mu)001:72: gzhi dang 'bras bu gnyis bdag nyid gcig par 'brel to //
NK076(mu)001:73: de nyid kyis na rgyun chags pa zhes kyang bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:74: rgyun ni rgyun chags zhes bya ste ces pa dang
NK076(mu)001:75: 'brel dang ma tshang med phyir dang ces pas so
NK076(mu)001:77: dri gsum las gzhi lam 'bras bu'i shes bya rnam zhes pas /
NK076(mu)001:80: mthar son pa 'bras bu'i shes bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:81: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du 'bad pa bshad do //
NK076(mu)001:82: spyan 'grel las rnam 'byor gsum gyi phung po la /
NK076(mu)001:83: rigs dang snang ba'i yan lag bzhag /ces pas /
NK076(mu)001:84: 'khor 'das gnyis med du gnas par bya ba gzhi'i rnal 'byor /
NK076(mu)001:85: lta ba dang ting nge gnyis med kyis 'jug par byed pa rkyen gyi rnal 'byor /
NK076(mu)001:86: rang don gzhan don gnyis med sngon du byas pa
NK076(mu)001:87: bya bral 'bras bu'i rnal 'byor te rnal 'byor te
NK076(mu)001:89: ngo bo gzhan du mi 'gyur zhing /
NK076(mu)001:90: phyi mo'i rigs dang sems lnga skyes pas rgyud du
NK076(mu)001:91: byung zhing gol sgrib kyi dbang du mi gtong pa
NK076(mu)001:92: rtsol ba'i rigs dang rgyud du byung zin lam rtsol
NK076(mu)001:93: gyi pas bya ba med pa mthar thug gi rigs
NK076(mu)001:94: te rigs gsum du'ang bshad do //
NK076(mu)001:95: de ltar na'ang dbye sgo bcu gnyis pa'i de dag ngo bo gnyis su chad pa zhig gam /
NK076(mu)001:96: ldog byas kyi dbye ba'ang med par cig pa zhig yin /
NK076(mu)001:97: dang po ltar na de dang ngo bo gcig la rim par snang ba ni zhes pa dang 'gal /
NK076(mu)001:98: gnyis pa ltar na rang bzhin bder gshegs gdul bya'i
NK076(mu)001:99: ces pa 'thad par bshad pa ji ltar drang zhe
NK076(mu)001:101: ngo bo cig la mtshon tshul gyi dbye ba tha dad pas gnyis ka'i skyon mi mtshungs te /
NK076(mu)001:103: ngo bo gcig pa ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:104: de lam rim ltar ye shes rang gnas pa //
NK076(mu)001:105: lam dang 'bras bu kun ngo bo //
NK076(mu)001:107: gnyis pa'ang ldog pa tha dad ni ro drug gam /
NK076(mu)001:108: gsal dang brtag pas tha dad phyir zhes pas mngon no //
NK076(mu)001:109: rnam par bsdu ba'i don ni /
NK076(mu)001:110: shes bya'i chos kun kyang gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du 'dus te /
NK076(mu)001:111: sngar bstan pa dag mtshon tshul tsam nyid las ngo bo tha dad du grub pa med pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:112: dper nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gcig nyid la'ang rta bdun dang /
NK076(mu)001:114: pad mo'i gnyen sogs rnam grangs du mar brtags pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:115: de ltar bsdu ba'i don gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum spyir bstan pa la bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:121: gang las dbye ba'i gzhi dang /
NK076(mu)001:122: gang dag dbye ba'i chos dang /
NK076(mu)001:123: ci'i phyir dbye ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK076(mu)001:124: dbye ba nges par 'byed pa'i tshad ma bsam pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:125: dang po ni dbye ba thams cad dbye gzhi la ltos nas dbye dgos te /
NK076(mu)001:126: dbye gzhi med pa'i dbye sgo mi mtshungs pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:127: shes pa dang shes bya tshogs pa'am /
NK076(mu)001:128: mkhas pa dang mi mkhas pa'i blo yul zer ba'ang
NK076(mu)001:129: yod de dbye sgo dang khyad tha dad du 'gyur
NK076(mu)001:131: shes ldan dag zhal 'cham par shes bya tsam po las phye bar 'dod de /
NK076(mu)001:134: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i dbye ba rnams //
NK076(mu)001:135: 'bru mthun tshig gnyer shes don phyir //
NK076(mu)001:136: rnam gsum brgyud kyi don dam du bsdus /
NK076(mu)001:138: de lta na'ang gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi yang shes byar thal te /
NK076(mu)001:139: dbye gzhi khyab bya yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:141: dape'am tshad ma'am gtan tshig sam //
NK076(mu)001:142: rjes su dpag pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK076(mu)001:143: rtogs par nus pa ma yin te //
NK076(mu)001:144: dmus long mkha' la mtho mjal 'dra //
NK076(mu)001:147: de min zhen pa dgrol phyir las /
NK076(mu)001:148: tha snyad gnyis par bsam brjod 'das ces /
NK076(mu)001:149: shes bya yul du ma gyur par gsung pas bsal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:150: gang du khyab dbye gzhi chos la ma khegs na khyab bya la'ang ngo bo'i gzhir mtshungs te /
NK076(mu)001:151: shing tsam dang sha ba a ru ra bzhin zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:155: dang po ni kha cig kyi me nyag na re /
NK076(mu)001:156: ngo bo nyid shes yul min kyang lam du shes
NK076(mu)001:157: byar gnas 'gyur nas gtan la phebs ces zer ba
NK076(mu)001:159: gzhi med pa la gnas 'gyur mi srid pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:160: sol ba brdar yang dkar por mi 'gyur ba bzhin no gsungs /
NK076(mu)001:161: bla ma nyid ni gnas lugs de nyid shes byar thal lam /
NK076(mu)001:162: gtan la 'bebs ldog shes byar thal zer /
NK076(mu)001:163: dang po gtan tshig ma grub cing /
NK076(mu)001:164: gnyis pa ni 'dod pa'ang zhes rnam par phye ste brjod pa'ang /
NK076(mu)001:166: gtan la dbab bya kho na gnas lugs de yin pa'i phyir ro /
NK076(mu)001:167: rang lugs ni gnas lugs su gnas par thal 'gyur nyid 'dod pa kho nar khas blang ngo /
NK076(mu)001:168: sngar gyi lung gi gsal yang gnas lugs kyi don
NK076(mu)001:169: de rtog ge'i rig pas mi rtog pa la dogs
NK076(mu)001:170: kyi / kun khyab kyi gtan tshigs gsum gyi mi rtog pa la dogs pa ma yin zhing /
NK076(mu)001:171: man ngag kyang gnas lugs la tha dad pa la brjod kyi /
NK076(mu)001:172: gtan la 'bebs tshul la brjod pa ma yin no //
NK076(mu)001:173: 'on kyang shes bya la dngos po dngos med gnyis su kha tshon chod dam ma chod ce na /
NK076(mu)001:174: de tsam du 'dir lam mtha' dag lta ba dang
NK076(mu)001:175: ting nge gnyis su 'dus sam ma 'dus ces bya
NK076(mu)001:176: // ma 'dus ces na 'dir yang ma chod do //
NK076(mu)001:177: shes bya kha tshon gcod pa'i tshad ma rgyun chad du thal /
NK076(mu)001:178: shes bya la phung po gsum pa srid par kyang 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:179: de yang lam mtha' dag lta ba dang ting nge gnyis su 'dus par bshad pa dang 'gal /
NK076(mu)001:180: grol lam gyi gtso bo gsum pa zhig kyang srid par 'gyur ro zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:181: 'dus par khas len na 'dir yang chod do //
NK076(mu)001:182: gnas lugs de dngos po 'am dngos med kyi mthar thal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:183: lam yang lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin gang rung
NK076(mu)001:184: zhig gis mtshon nus par thal zhes mgo 'dre bar
NK076(mu)001:185: 'gyur ro // des na lam mtha' dag lta ba
NK076(mu)001:186: dang ting nge 'dzin gnyis su 'dus kyang lam tsam
NK076(mu)001:187: zhig spyi khyab du gnas pa bzhin du /
NK076(mu)001:188: shes bya mtha' dag dngos po dang dngos med gnyis
NK076(mu)001:189: su kha tshon chod kyang gnas lugs kyi gzhi de
NK076(mu)001:190: spyi khyab du gnas pa ni gtan la dbab byar
NK076(mu)001:193: phyi nang bye brag ji snyed pa'i //
NK076(mu)001:194: chos rnams thams cad byang chub sems //
NK076(mu)001:195: ji bzhin nang du ye nas babs //
NK076(mu)001:196: shes par bya ba'i rgyud don yin //
NK076(mu)001:198: gang dag dbye ba'i chos ni gzhi lam 'bra bu gsum mo //
NK076(mu)001:199: ci'i phyir dbye ba'i dgos ched ni /
NK076(mu)001:200: chos nyid kyi gzhi de la brten nas 'bras bu
NK076(mu)001:201: la brod pa bskyed pas lam gyi rtsol ba la
NK076(mu)001:202: mi lta bar lam du 'jug pa'i dgos pa yod
NK076(mu)001:203: / dper na rgyu sa bon rang la gnas pa
NK076(mu)001:204: la brten nas 'bras bu ston thog la brod pa
NK076(mu)001:205: bskyed pas so nam gyi rtsol ba la mi lta
NK076(mu)001:206: bar 'jug pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK076(mu)001:207: dbye ba nges par 'byed pa'i tshad ma bsam pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:208: de ltar dbye ba'i sgo gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum
NK076(mu)001:209: kho nar nges pa de nyid tshad mas shes sam
NK076(mu)001:210: tshad ma ma yin pas shes /
NK076(mu)001:211: gnyis pa ltar na sgro 'dogs kyi blor zad yid brtan du mi rung pa /
NK076(mu)001:212: dang po ltar na mngon sum gyis shes sam /
NK076(mu)001:213: rjes dpag gis shes ce na /
NK076(mu)001:214: 'di dag ni rtog ge rang gzo mkhan gyi rigs pa yin gyi //
NK076(mu)001:215: de lta bus chos nyid kyi don rtogs par bdag mi 'dod de /
NK076(mu)001:216: tha snyad pa'i shes ngo la 'das pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:218: dgongs 'dus dape'am tshad ma'am gtan tshigs sam //
NK076(mu)001:219: rjes su dpag pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK076(mu)001:220: rtog pa nus pa ma yin te //
NK076(mu)001:221: dmus long mkha' la mthong mjal 'dra //
NK076(mu)001:223: de'i phyir 'dir ni kun khyab kyi tshad ma gsum gyi shes te /
NK076(mu)001:225: lung dang man ngag rigs pa dag gis thag bcad de /
NK076(mu)001:227: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' dri ma med pa lung gi tshad ma dang /
NK076(mu)001:228: sngon gyi mkhas pa rnams kyis mdzad pa man ngag gi tshad ma dang /
NK076(mu)001:229: de dag gi rjes su mthun par skyes pa rigs pa'i tshad ma dang gsum ste /
NK076(mu)001:230: shin tu lkog gyur gyi don la chad lhag med
NK076(mu)001:231: par 'jal ba de dag las gzhan med pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:234: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK076(mu)001:235: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK076(mu)001:236: rang byung sku lnga lhun gyis grub //
NK076(mu)001:240: gzhi lam 'bras bu shes bya rnams //
NK076(mu)001:241: 'bru mthun tshig don shes bya'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:242: rnam gsum rgyud kyi don du bsdus /
NK076(mu)001:245: dbye gzhi shes bya tsam po de chos can /
NK076(mu)001:246: dbye sgo gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du nges te /
NK076(mu)001:247: de dag ma 'tshog par thams cad mkhyen pa mi 'byung zhing /
NK076(mu)001:248: der shes bya'am chos kun ma 'dus pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:249: gtan tshigs ma grub ce na /
NK076(mu)001:250: rgyu mtshan gnyis pa ni bdag cag so so'i skye
NK076(mu)001:251: ba'i rigs ngo nas mi snang mod kyi sngar gyi
NK076(mu)001:252: lung gis grub pa zhig yin no //
NK076(mu)001:253: gnyis pa ngo bo bstan pa la gsum las /
NK076(mu)001:256: gzhi'i spyi'i ngo bo ni rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK076(mu)001:259: ngo bo thams cad sems yin te //
NK076(mu)001:260: gser gyi dpe bzhin gnyis su med //
NK076(mu)001:262: gnas lugs kyi ngo bo ni byed pa po med par rtsal ma 'gags par snang ba ste /
NK076(mu)001:264: snying po rang snang ba nyid ces so //
NK076(mu)001:265: brtag gzhi'i ngo bo ni snod bcud log pa'i zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:266: snang yul dang bcas pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:269: ngo bo snod bcud 'jig rten gyi //
NK076(mu)001:270: snang dang zhen pa'i chos rnams so //
NK076(mu)001:272: lam gyi ngo bo ni shes rab gsum gyi sgo nas sems gzhi'i lam lnga rims pas skye ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:275: ngo bo shes rab rnam gsum gyi //
NK076(mu)001:276: sems bzhi skye bar bstan pa yin /
NK076(mu)001:278: 'bras bu'i ngo bo ni sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga te /
NK076(mu)001:280: khog gzhung 'bras bu'i ngo bo sku gsung thugs //
NK076(mu)001:281: yon tan phrin las rnam pa lnga //
NK076(mu)001:284: chos thams cad kyi 'byung gzhir gyur pas na gzhi zhes bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:285: rim gsum tha snyad gnyis kyi chos rnams kun //
NK076(mu)001:286: ma lus 'byung phyir gzhi zhes bya /
NK076(mu)001:288: gang gi gong du bgrod byar gyur pas na lam zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:290: bgrod dang de chos ldan pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:292: grub pa'am mthar phyin pa'i don gyis na 'bras bur bshad /
NK076(mu)001:294: spyi don bzhi pa mtshan nyid la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:297: dang po ni 'dod gzhung tha dad de sngon gyi zur tsho kha cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:300: 'bras bu shes zin par byas pa'am /
NK076(mu)001:303: 'bras bu gsal bar byed zin pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:305: lam de shes shing gsal bar bya dgos sam mi dgos /
NK076(mu)001:307: mi dgos na 'bras bu thal lo //
NK076(mu)001:308: gzhan yang yul can mig gi rnam shes /
NK076(mu)001:310: sngon por rtogs pa gsum kyang sgyu 'phrul gyi gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du thal bar 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:311: yang yam shud kha cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:314: smon cing mthar phyin pa 'bras bu zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:315: ru na re de ltar na lam la brten cing gnas sam /
NK076(mu)001:316: mi gnas mi gnas na gang la gnas /
NK076(mu)001:318: gnyis tshal ba yang kha cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:321: smin pa 'bras bu ces pa ldog pa chig rkyang
NK076(mu)001:322: du 'dod pa'ang mi 'thad de skyon snga so na
NK076(mu)001:323: gnas shing / lam gyi mtshan nyid kyang lha bal ma khyab ste /
NK076(mu)001:324: de nyid shes byed yin gyi 'jug byed ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:328: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:330: smyos rang snang du gtan la 'bebs pa'i rten du gyur pa gzhi /
NK076(mu)001:331: rim dang cig char du nyams su len pa lam
NK076(mu)001:332: zag med mthar phyin bskyed du byar med pa 'bras
NK076(mu)001:334: lam du rig 'dzin gyur pa'i 'bras la mtshan nyid phyi ma de ma khyab la /
NK076(mu)001:335: gzhi'i mtshan don ldog gzhan du 'gyur te lam la khyab ces pa nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:336: yang kyi sa kha cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:337: lam gyi gtan la dbab byar gnas pa gzhi /
NK076(mu)001:338: gzhi gtan la dbabs shing 'bras bu thob par byed pa de lam /
NK076(mu)001:339: lam gyi mthar thug pa'i don mngon du byas pas
NK076(mu)001:340: rtsol ba las grol ba ni 'bras bu zer ba
NK076(mu)001:341: mi 'thad de / mtshon tshul 'dres pa'i skyon chags la /
NK076(mu)001:342: gzhan yang 'bras bu de lam gyis gtan la dbab dgos sam mi dgos /
NK076(mu)001:343: dang po ltar na gzhir 'gyur zhing /
NK076(mu)001:344: gnyis pa ltar na 'bad med du grol thar sngon du byed pa thal lo //
NK076(mu)001:345: bla ma ni rog sngon gyi mkhas pa dag zur sh+aakya seng ge dag gi rjes su 'brangs nas /
NK076(mu)001:346: ye nas gnas pa brtag bya dang bcas pa ni gzhi /
NK076(mu)001:347: bgrod par byed pa rtog byed dang bcas pa ni lam /
NK076(mu)001:348: mthar thug pa'i don sngon du byas pas rtsol ba
NK076(mu)001:349: las grol ba ni 'bras bu 'o zhes bzhed na'ang
NK076(mu)001:351: de ltar gsang sngags kyis lugs kyis na lam dang
NK076(mu)001:352: 'bras bu gnyis ye nas gnas pa'i so sor rtogs
NK076(mu)001:353: pa'i shes rab brtag bya yin nam min /
NK076(mu)001:354: dang po ltar na shes bya gsum char mtshan nyid gcig gis mtshon nus par thal /
NK076(mu)001:355: chos mthun pa'i phyir rtags khas blangs kyis grub1 /
NK076(mu)001:356: 'dod 2na mtshan nyid phyi ma lam 'bras gnyis ci'i phyir dgod /
NK076(mu)001:357: rang mtshan gyis mi mthun phyogs gang 3du rnam par
NK076(mu)001:358: dpyad bya gzhan med par mtshungs pa la mtshan nyid
NK076(mu)001:360: yul tha dad gsum gyi bum pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:362: de ltar lam rim ye shes rang gnas pa lam dang 'bras bu kun ngo bo /
NK076(mu)001:364: brtag gzhi gnyis su bstan pa'i chos 'khor dang mya
NK076(mu)001:365: ngan las 'das par gsung pa ces pa'i lung spangs
NK076(mu)001:366: par mi nus la rgyu med kyi 'bras bu srid
NK076(mu)001:367: par 'gyur zhing / 'bras bu'i mchog nyid kyang lam
NK076(mu)001:368: du gyur pa'i 'bras bu la ma khyab nges pa'o
NK076(mu)001:369: par 'gyur zhing / // 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid kyang
NK076(mu)001:370: lam du 'gyur ba'i 'bras bu la ma khyab par
NK076(mu)001:371: par 'gyur zhing / // nges so // yang me nyag kha cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:372: gzhi'i spyi'i mtshan nyid spyir mi mtshungs pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:373: mtshan gzhi gnas tha dad 'khrul pa'i phyir zer ma
NK076(mu)001:374: ba'ang mi 'thad de 'khrul snang dang ngo bo chos
NK076(mu)001:375: nyid ngo bo tha dad du thal /
NK076(mu)001:376: 'dod na brgyad pa ma rig ye shes tha dad min ces pas bsal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:377: khyab pa'ang rang rgyud la grub bo //
NK076(mu)001:378: sems kyi mtshan nyid kyang rnam par dkar ba'i don
NK076(mu)001:379: la 'jug cig thob par byed pa'i thabs khyad par
NK076(mu)001:380: du gyur pa'o ces pa'ang lta ba la ma khyab
NK076(mu)001:381: te / 'jug byed ma yi zhing shes byed yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:382: 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid lam gyis ci rigs pa mngon du byas pa'o zer ba'ang mi rung ste /
NK076(mu)001:383: byas pa'i phyir mi rtag par 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:384: khyab bya khyab byed yin pa'i phyir bum pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:385: rang lugs ni chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas na gzhi /
NK076(mu)001:386: shes 'jug gi byed rtsol dang bcas pa ni lam /
NK076(mu)001:387: chos nyid mngon 'gyur bskyed du byar med son pa 'bras bu ste /
NK076(mu)001:388: dang po ni ngo bo dang brtag gzhi gnyis ka
NK076(mu)001:389: la khyab cing lam dang 'bras bu rnam par gcad
NK076(mu)001:390: pa / gnyis pas ni lta bu dang ting nge
NK076(mu)001:391: gnyis che la khyab cing gzhi 'bras rnam par gcad
NK076(mu)001:392: pa / de / gsum pas ni gnas skabs dang
NK076(mu)001:393: mthar thug gnyis char la khyab cing gzhi lam rnam
NK076(mu)001:394: par bcad de skyon mtha' dag las grol ba nyid
NK076(mu)001:395: pas mkhas pa rnams kyis basngagasa par 'os pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:396: bye brag tu gtan la dbab pa la gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum so sor ston pa las /
NK076(mu)001:397: dang po la'ang gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi dang /
NK076(mu)001:398: 'khrul pa brtag pa'i gzhi'i gnyis te //
NK076(mu)001:401: dang po rnam pa gnyis yin te /
NK076(mu)001:402: ngo bo'i gzhi dang brtags pa'i gzhi /
NK076(mu)001:404: dang por gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi /
NK076(mu)001:406: rang gi mtshan nyid ngos bzung ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:407: ka dag dang lhun grub kyi dbye ba rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:408: grub mtha' bden pa gsum gyi gnas lugs dang /
NK076(mu)001:409: nges byed kyi tshig la bsam pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:410: dang po la mtshan nyid ngos bzung ba de sgrub pa /
NK076(mu)001:411: skabs 'phros kyi gzhal bya gsum las /
NK076(mu)001:412: dang po ni rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems
NK076(mu)001:413: shes bya dngos po'i gshis mtha' dang bral bar gnas
NK076(mu)001:414: tsam zhig ste / ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:416: mtshan nyid mtha' dang kun bral bas //
NK076(mu)001:417: ci yang bzung du med pa'o /
NK076(mu)001:419: 'thad pa gtan tshig /gnyis pa de bsgrub pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:420: lam rim bye brag bsdus pa'i kun khyab gsum ces pas /
NK076(mu)001:421: kun khyab kyi gtan tshigs rnam pa gsum gyis sgrub par bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:423: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems /
NK076(mu)001:424: de ni lung gi tshad mar bshad /
NK076(mu)001:427: lha phreng chos thams cad sems la gnas ces so //
NK076(mu)001:428: rigs pa ni mthun snang gi chos can gcig la bsgrub na /
NK076(mu)001:431: 9yongs gcod bsgrub bya sems yin te /
NK076(mu)001:432: 9snang ba sems kyi gzhi dbang btsan du byas pa'i dus so //
NK076(mu)001:433: sems las ma gtogs pa'i chos gzhan med pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:435: gdos pa can gyi chos med phyir //
NK076(mu)001:436: shes pa 'ba' zhig kho na'o ces so //
NK076(mu)001:437: gtan tshigs ma grub ce na /
NK076(mu)001:438: 9zlog na gnod pa can gyi tshad ma sems las
NK076(mu)001:439: ma gtogs chos gzhan zhig shes nas yod dam ma
NK076(mu)001:440: shes kyang yod / gnyis pa ltar na mig gi yul na'ang sgra yod par thal /
NK076(mu)001:442: khyab pa 9dngos po'i stobs zhugs kyi tshad ma rang rgyud la grub bo //
NK076(mu)001:443: dang po ltar na 'brel ba yod nas shes sam med kyang shes /
NK076(mu)001:444: gnyis pa mig gis kyang sgra thos par thal /
NK076(mu)001:445: gal te zung 'khor mig shes kyi sgra mi thos
NK076(mu)001:446: kyang 'brel pa med pa'i gzugs mthong na ci ste
NK076(mu)001:447: khyab pa ma grub ces na /
NK076(mu)001:448: 'brel med mnyam po la sgra mi shes par gzugs ma shes pa ci'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:449: de ni mig gi dbang po gzugs 'dzin du skyes
NK076(mu)001:450: la sgra 'dzin du skyes la sgra 'dzin du ma
NK076(mu)001:451: skyes te bdag rkyen gyi byed pa tha dad pa'o
NK076(mu)001:452: ce na / 'brel pa'i mtshan nyid rag las shes shing las chos su 'byung ba ma yin tam /
NK076(mu)001:453: de ltar na'ang rnam shes skye ba de yul gzugs la rag las sam ma las /
NK076(mu)001:454: gnyis pa ltar na bems pos kyang gzugs mthong bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:458: dang po ltar na 'brel med du shes pa'i dam bca' nyams so //
NK076(mu)001:459: yang 'brel yod du shes zer na /
NK076(mu)001:460: ngo bo dbyer med pa'i tshul gyis chos gzhan mi 'dor ba /
NK076(mu)001:463: ltos pa'i tshul gyis chos gzhan mi 'dor ba de las byung bar 'brel /
NK076(mu)001:465: sems la phyi rol gyi don byung ngam /
NK076(mu)001:466: phyi rol gyi don las sems byung /
NK076(mu)001:467: gnyis pa ltar na bems po las kyang rig pa 'byung bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:469: khyab pa ma grub ce na /
NK076(mu)001:470: phyi rol gyi don shes pa'i dngos po thal /
NK076(mu)001:471: don byed nus pa'i dang po chos las bem rig gnyis las mi srid pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:472: dang po ltar na de las byung zhing de nyid snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:473: chos thams cad sems las grub par nges so //
NK076(mu)001:474: dang po bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel pa yod pa shes na /
NK076(mu)001:475: sems phyi rol gyi don du phar bdag gcig gam /
NK076(mu)001:476: phyi rol du sems su tshul bdag gcig /gnyis pa ltar na /
NK076(mu)001:477: sems de nyid rig pa las log pa'i bems po dngos su thal /
NK076(mu)001:478: rtags ma grub na dam bca' nyams /
NK076(mu)001:479: gang du phyi rol gyi don du bdag gcig pa la bems dngos kyis khyab te rags pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:481: dang po ltar na sems las ma gtogs pa'i chos gzhan med pa'i gtan tshigs grub ste /
NK076(mu)001:482: ngo bo de nyid du bdag gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:483: gang du sems las ma gtogs pa'i chos gzhan med pa la bum pa sems yin pas khyab ste /
NK076(mu)001:484: gser gling du phyin pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:485: thun mong ma yin pa'i gtan tshigs kyis mtha' bral
NK076(mu)001:486: du bsgrub pa ni 'og tu ston par zad do
NK076(mu)001:487: // gsum pa skabs 'phros kyi gzhal bya ni /
NK076(mu)001:488: de ltar na'ang so so snang la sor bzhag pa
NK076(mu)001:489: 'di gnas lugs ngo bo'am rang bzhin gyi gzhi yin
NK076(mu)001:491: dang po ltar yang mi rung te /
NK076(mu)001:494: gal te snang ba la gsang sngags bya na sangs
NK076(mu)001:495: rgyas kyi dgongs pa dang sems can gyi 'du shes
NK076(mu)001:498: lam rim man ngag las kyang /
NK076(mu)001:499: bden min ma grol bcings pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:500: dus sgras 'joms bslus mi rtag dang //
NK076(mu)001:501: 'phags lam bral dgos btson rar tshud //
NK076(mu)001:505: so skye'i shes pa 'di chos can /
NK076(mu)001:506: yang dag gi tshad mar thal /
NK076(mu)001:507: shes bya ma nor ba yul du byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:508: 'dod na 'khrul pa rgyun chad du thal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:509: rtags ma grub na ni dam bca' nyams la /
NK076(mu)001:510: gang du shes bya ma nor ba yul du byed
NK076(mu)001:511: pa la ma 'khrul bas khyab te 'phags pa'i mkhyen
NK076(mu)001:512: dngos bzhin no // gnyis pa ltar na'ang /
NK076(mu)001:514: gal te mi snang ba las gsang basngagasa bya na
NK076(mu)001:515: gzhan du mu stegs chad pa'ang sangs rgyas nyid du
NK076(mu)001:517: lam rim man ngag las kyang //
NK076(mu)001:518: bla med theg pa chen por ni //
NK076(mu)001:519: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /kun rdzob tu yang dbyer med de //
NK076(mu)001:520: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK076(mu)001:522: rigs pa'i gnod pa'ang 'khrul snang 'di chos can /
NK076(mu)001:523: chos nyid kyi khyab bya yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:524: ngo bo tha dad pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:525: 'dod na rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med zhes pas bsal /
NK076(mu)001:526: gtan tshigs ma grub na tha dad pa'i tshul du khyab bam /
NK076(mu)001:527: tha dad med pa'i tshul du khyab /
NK076(mu)001:528: dang po ltar na chos nyid spros bcas su thal cing /
NK076(mu)001:529: gnyis pa ltar na gzhi rang yang 'khrul par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:530: gang du ngo bo tha dad pa nyid khyab pa'i
NK076(mu)001:531: bya byed du mi rung ste ka ba dang bum
NK076(mu)001:533: len la gnyis las gzhan lugs dgag pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:534: ka ri ba kha cig na re rtog pa'i dus su gzhir ma gyur pa med la /
NK076(mu)001:535: ma rtog pa'i 'khrul ngo 'di ma yin no //
NK076(mu)001:537: rtogs pa ni rkyen la rag las sam /
NK076(mu)001:540: rang bzhin gyi snang ba ma yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:541: rkyen la rag lus pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:542: 'dod na rang bzhin 'dus byas su thal lo //
NK076(mu)001:543: gnyis pa ltar na ma rtogs pa'i dus su gzhi min la /
NK076(mu)001:544: rtogs pa'i dus na yin par khas blangs so //
NK076(mu)001:545: yang skyo rin chen kha cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:546: snang ba 'di chos nyid dngos ni min la /
NK076(mu)001:547: chos nyid kyi khyab bya yin no zhes zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:548: tha dad kyi tshul du khyab bam //
NK076(mu)001:549: tha dad med pa'i tshul du khyab ces brtag te sngar bkag zin no //
NK076(mu)001:550: yang kyi tsakra kha cig na re snang 'di chos
NK076(mu)001:551: nyid kyi dngos su ma spangs la mi ldan pas
NK076(mu)001:553: ma spangs ces pa de yod chos yin nam med chos yin /
NK076(mu)001:554: dang po ltar na ldan pa nyid du thal /
NK076(mu)001:555: gnyis pa ltar na ma spangs pa'i dam bca' nyams so //
NK076(mu)001:556: yang slas rdo rje 'od kha cig na re snang
NK076(mu)001:557: ngo nas chos nyid rang snang yin pas chos nyid
NK076(mu)001:558: yin gyi / zhen ngo la phyogs su zhen pas
NK076(mu)001:559: ma yin te ltos pa tha dad la ltos pa'o
NK076(mu)001:561: snang zhen gnyis blo rdzas ngo bo gcig gam tha dad /
NK076(mu)001:562: dang po ltar na zhen ngo nas kyang chos nyid rang snang du thal /
NK076(mu)001:563: rdzas gcig la snang mi snang cha gnyis 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:564: 'dod na zhen ngo nas ma yin par 'dod pa nyams shing /
NK076(mu)001:565: gang du sngon 'gyur gyi rdzas gcig la snang mi
NK076(mu)001:566: snang cha gnyis mi mtshungs pas khyab ste ud pal
NK076(mu)001:568: gnyis pa ltar na zhen 'khrul spangs pa'i tshe snang 'khrul mi spongs par thal /
NK076(mu)001:569: rdzas tha dad pa'i phyir ces bya /
NK076(mu)001:570: 'dod na 'phags pas mnyam bzhag la chos 'ga' yang
NK076(mu)001:571: ma mthong ba ni lam gyi ye shes ci las
NK076(mu)001:572: bsal / gang du rdzas tha dad la spang bya
NK076(mu)001:573: tha dad kyis khyab te dug dang tsher ma bzhin
NK076(mu)001:575: rang bzhin chos nyid du yongs su rdzogs rnam pa 'khrul ldog tu ma 'dres /
NK076(mu)001:576: ngo bo la dbyer med ces bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:579: zhe sdang ma 'dres mnar sems pa //
NK076(mu)001:580: yongs su rdzogs par stong bdag med //
NK076(mu)001:581: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs na //
NK076(mu)001:582: ma bcos de gzhin nyid kho na //
NK076(mu)001:584: de ltar na'ang yongs rdzogs de nyid ma 'dres pa de nyid yin nam min /
NK076(mu)001:585: yin na ma 'dres pa chos nyid min pa bzhin
NK076(mu)001:586: du yongs rdzogs kyi ngos nas kyang min par thal
NK076(mu)001:587: / ma yin na dbyer med du mi 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:588: de tsam du snum de nyid til 'bru yin nam min /
NK076(mu)001:589: yin na til 'bru khu bar mi snang ba bzhin du snum yang khu bar mi snang bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:590: ma yin na til 'bru dang snum rdzas dbyer med du mi 'gyur zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:591: gnyis pa ka dag dang lhun grub kyi dbye ba rgyas par bstan pa la bzhi /
NK076(mu)001:592: rnam dbye ngos bzung ba gcig dang tha dad kyi brtag pa bsam pa /
NK076(mu)001:593: skyon can gyi gzhi dgags pa /
NK076(mu)001:594: rang gzhung skyon med du bsgrub pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:595: dang po la'ang spyir dbye ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:597: dang po ni gser dang gser gyi g.ya' ltar chos
NK076(mu)001:598: nyid kyi gzhi la ma rig pa mtshungs ldan du
NK076(mu)001:600: shel dang shel gyi kha dog ltar chos nyid kyi gzhi la 'khrul pa'i rgyu med cing /
NK076(mu)001:601: dri ma glo bur bar 'dod pa'i ka dag pa gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:603: ma rig ye shes tha dad min //
NK076(mu)001:604: ma rtogs rtogs pa'i lam 'dir gcig /ces pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:606: thams cad dag ces bya ba'ang //
NK076(mu)001:607: dngos po gsal dag ma yin te //
NK076(mu)001:608: rnam dpyad nyid na rnam par dag /ces pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:609: gnyis pa bye brag tu dbye ba ni /
NK076(mu)001:615: dbyings ka dag /ye shes ka dag /dag pa chen
NK076(mu)001:616: po dang gsum ste drug go /gnyis pa gcig tha
NK076(mu)001:617: dad kyi brtag pa bsam pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:618: 'di ltar ngo bo'i gzhi nges med phyogs med du gnas pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:619: 'khrul pa'am gzhi ngos can phyogs can gyi snang ba
NK076(mu)001:620: 'di chu dang 'o ma 'dres pa bzhin du mtshon
NK076(mu)001:621: tshul gyi dbye ba'ang med par cig pa zhig gam
NK076(mu)001:622: / bum pa dang snam bu bzhin du ngo bo tha dad pa zhig gam /
NK076(mu)001:623: byas pa dang mi rtag pa bum pa la gcig
NK076(mu)001:624: pa bzhin du ngo bo ga cig la mtshon tshul
NK076(mu)001:626: thang khrom zos pa'i snang ba la nam mkha' la
NK076(mu)001:627: skra shad kyi 'khor lo 'dzings par snang ba bzhin
NK076(mu)001:628: du gsungs te glang ru g.yas g.yon 'dzin de nyid
NK076(mu)001:629: dang gzhan du brjod du med pa zhig yin ces
NK076(mu)001:630: pa dang bzhi 'god pa nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:631: gsum pa gzhan lugs kyi lan du skyon can gyi khas len brjod pa la gcig ste /
NK076(mu)001:632: ka dag skyon spyal can dang /
NK076(mu)001:633: lhun grub skyon skyo can no //
NK076(mu)001:634: dang po dgag pa la'ang gnyis /
NK076(mu)001:635: spyir ka dag dgag pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:637: dang po la'ang gnyis las phyogs snga 'god pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:638: ka dag skyon can thun mong gi lugs kyis chos
NK076(mu)001:639: nyid dang ma rig pa gnyis ngo bo dang 'thad
NK076(mu)001:642: log par rtog rtags rnam dag cing //
NK076(mu)001:643: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK076(mu)001:644: ces bshad pas so zer to /
NK076(mu)001:645: de dgag pa ni gsum las /
NK076(mu)001:648: bdag dang gzhan du rtog pa'i rgyu /
NK076(mu)001:649: bdag dang gzhan phyir gzhan med de //
NK076(mu)001:650: rnam dag dbyings nyid tshul gcig go /ces pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:653: yang dag gshegs dang log rtog gnyis //
NK076(mu)001:654: ngo bo nyid kyis gnas 'gyur na //
NK076(mu)001:655: yang dag lam gyis bcos su med //
NK076(mu)001:659: chos nyid dang ma rig pa ngo bo tha dad
NK076(mu)001:660: na chos nyid mthong yang 'khrul snang dung gser gyi
NK076(mu)001:661: dri ma bzhin mi spongs par thal /
NK076(mu)001:662: ma rig pa logs su grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:663: gnyis pa chos dang chos nyid rang ka bum ma yin bzhin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:664: ngo bo tha dad pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:666: 'khor ba dang rnam byang gnyis gang zag gi shes rgyud skad cig gis steng du skyes bu dang /
NK076(mu)001:667: dus gcig la dmigs par thal /
NK076(mu)001:668: skyes bu bzhin ngo bo tha dad pa'i phyir 'dod
NK076(mu)001:669: na 'gro la shes rgyud gnyis len du 'gyur ro
NK076(mu)001:670: // bzhi pa 'khrul snang dag phyogs su bsgyur du mi btub par thal /
NK076(mu)001:671: ngo bo tha dad pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:672: nor bu dang mching bu bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:674: gnyis pa bye brag tu dgag pa la'ang phyogs snga ma gsum las /
NK076(mu)001:675: dang po dbyings ka dag ni gnas lugs kyi gzhi
NK076(mu)001:676: stong pa'i chos nyid la 'khrul pa med par 'dod
NK076(mu)001:677: pa ste / de la'ang mtshan nyid yongs su chad
NK076(mu)001:678: pa'i kun brtags 'khrul ri bong gi rwa pa 'byung
NK076(mu)001:679: rung gi rgyu tsam yang med de glo bur bar
NK076(mu)001:680: pa ste / 'dod pa dang / rnam grangs kyi
NK076(mu)001:681: kun brtags log rtog tsam nyid las rang rgyud par
NK076(mu)001:683: dang po dgag pa ni de ltar rgyud dag gi sangs rgyas la'ang 'khrul pa 'byung bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:684: rgyu la ma grub kyang glo bur du 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:685: 'dod par mi nus shing khyab pa rang rgyud glo
NK076(mu)001:686: bur 'byung rgyu la rgyud dag pa ma yin pas
NK076(mu)001:691: gnyis pa dgag pa'i phyir rang bzhin dang 'khrul snang
NK076(mu)001:692: ga cig gam tha dad ces dris pa'i lan du
NK076(mu)001:693: / snang tsam du gcig mod kyi /
NK076(mu)001:694: 'khrul ngo la ltos nas 'khor ba'i chos rang rgyud la nag ril lo //
NK076(mu)001:695: ma 'khrul pa'i ngo la ltos nas myang 'das bden
NK076(mu)001:696: pas stong pa'i chos su dkar ril lo zer na
NK076(mu)001:697: ci snang tsam du gcig pa de nyid dri dang
NK076(mu)001:698: sgog pa ltar tshogs pa gcig pa zhig gam /
NK076(mu)001:699: shing tsam dang sha ba ltar rang bzhin gcig zhig gam /
NK076(mu)001:700: dang po ltar na 'khrul snang kheg pa'i tshe snang chos gzhan dag kyang khegs par thal /
NK076(mu)001:701: tshogs pa'i bye brag khegs pa'i phyir rgog pa khegs
NK076(mu)001:702: na de dang 'tshogs pa'i dri khegs pa lta bu
NK076(mu)001:703: / 'dod na kun rdzob mkhyen pa'i ye shes rgyun chad du 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:704: gnyis pa ltar na rang bzhin nam grub pa de
NK076(mu)001:705: dang 'dra gcig pu 'khrul snang yang grub par thal
NK076(mu)001:706: / rang bzhin gcig pa'i rigs kyi bye brag gang
NK076(mu)001:707: du grub pa na rigs sha ba la shing tsam
NK076(mu)001:709: 'dod na 'khrul ba glo bur du 'dod pa nyams so //
NK076(mu)001:710: gnyis pa ye shes ka dag ni gnas lugs sku
NK076(mu)001:711: dang ye shes la 'khrul pa'i dri ma med par
NK076(mu)001:712: 'dod pa ste / ci de ltar sems can gyi rgyud la log shes rgyun chad du thal /
NK076(mu)001:713: gzhi nyid 'bras bu bden zhing 'khrul pa'i dri ma med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:714: gzhi la ma grub lam khyab bsgrub kyang glo bur bas sgribs te ci zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:715: glor bur ba la rgyud yod dam med /
NK076(mu)001:716: yod na ma rig pa'o ce na /
NK076(mu)001:717: de kho na rang gis rang ma rig gam /
NK076(mu)001:718: spu ris kyi rnam pa gzhan gyis ma rig dang po ltar na tha dad pa nyams la /
NK076(mu)001:719: gnyis pa ltar na rgyud tha dad kyi ma rig pas gcig gi ye shes nyid 'gebs par thal /
NK076(mu)001:720: rgyud gcig la shes pa'i rdzas tha dad 'gal ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:721: 'dod na don grub pa sangs rgyas don med du 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:722: gnyis pa ltar rgyu med par rgyu med rang gi
NK076(mu)001:723: rtags mthong na 'byung na'ang med pa'i chos bzhi med
NK076(mu)001:725: ces pas srid par 'gyur te mi 'thad do //
NK076(mu)001:726: gsum pa dag pa chen po ni chos thams cad
NK076(mu)001:727: kyi rang bzhin nam ngo bo nyid mtha'i dri ma
NK076(mu)001:728: thams cad dang bral bar 'dod pa 'og nas yongs
NK076(mu)001:730: gnyis pa lhun grub skyon can la'ang spyir dgag pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:732: dang po la'ang gnyis las phyogs snga ni chos nyid dang /
NK076(mu)001:733: ma rig pa mtshon tshul gyi bye brag med par shin tu gcig par 'dod pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:735: bde gshegs snying pos ma rig dang zhes pa'am /
NK076(mu)001:736: rgyu mtshungs ces bshad pas so zer to //
NK076(mu)001:737: de dgag pa la gsum las lung ni /
NK076(mu)001:738: snying po phyogs bcu'i stong khams ye nas dben /
NK076(mu)001:739: srid pa gsum nyid dag pa'i zhing ces pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:741: lam rim ye nas dag mnyam rtogs pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:743: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing //
NK076(mu)001:746: mtshon tshul yang dbye ba med na ma rig pa'i
NK076(mu)001:747: 'khrul snang 'di mthong bas chos nyid mthong bar thal
NK076(mu)001:749: rang mtshan gyi bye brag bzhin ma rig pa'i snang
NK076(mu)001:750: ba las zag pa 'phel ba bzhin du chos nyid
NK076(mu)001:752: gcig pa'i phyir zhe sdang rang rgyud bzhin /
NK076(mu)001:753: 'dod na lam don med du 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:754: yang chos nyid la dbye ba med pa bzhin du
NK076(mu)001:755: ma rig pa'i 'khrul snang la'ang dbye ba med zhe
NK076(mu)001:758: 'dod na mngon sum gyis gsal lo //
NK076(mu)001:759: yang ma rig pa'i snang ba 'di mthong thos las
NK076(mu)001:760: logs su grub pa bzhin du chos nyid kyang mthong
NK076(mu)001:761: thos la logs su grub par thal /
NK076(mu)001:763: 'dod na chos nyid dbang po'i mngon sum du dmigs par thal lo zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:764: gnyis pa bye brag tu dgag pa la'ang phyogs snga
NK076(mu)001:765: ma gsum las spyi'am chos nyid lhun grub du 'dod
NK076(mu)001:766: pa rnams gnyis can ma spangs par gnyis med du
NK076(mu)001:767: lhun gyis grub ces zer ba ni mi rung ste
NK076(mu)001:768: / gnyis med gnyis can du bzlog pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:769: gnyis pa bye brag gam chos can lhun grub ni
NK076(mu)001:770: tshon skra'i nyag ma lta bu la 'khor 'das kyi
NK076(mu)001:771: chos thams cad grub par 'dod pa'ang mi rung ste
NK076(mu)001:773: gzhan yang mu stegs grangs can pa dag rtsa mchog
NK076(mu)001:774: gcig gi rtse la glang chen brgyas za ba rang
NK076(mu)001:775: rtsa mchog rtse la glang chen brgyas //
NK076(mu)001:776: sngon chad ma mthong yong do zhes //
NK076(mu)001:777: de dag drang can phyugs las gzhan //
NK076(mu)001:778: ngo mtshar bcas pa su zhig tshol //
NK076(mu)001:780: bzhin gyi grub ces zer ba dgag /de ni mi mtshungs te mi snang ba'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:781: khyed kyi yang mi mtshungs te mi snang ba'i phyir zhes mgo snyoms kyis khegs pa nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:782: gsum pa lhun grub kha 'byams pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:783: chos nyid ma nges pa'i don rtog na gang yang yin par smra ba te /
NK076(mu)001:784: snang ba la skyon bkal na stong pa yin zhes zer /
NK076(mu)001:785: stong pa la skyon bkal na snang ba yin zhes zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:786: lta ba khong du ma chud cing grub mtha' ma
NK076(mu)001:787: nges pa'i phyir rkyang khra'i byi'u bzhin shes rab 'chal
NK076(mu)001:788: ba'i tshig tu 'gyur ba nyid yin pas mkhas pa
NK076(mu)001:789: rnams kyis tshab cher spang bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:790: yang khyed kyi 'khor 'das kyi chos kun ma spangs
NK076(mu)001:791: pa'i lhun grub de la rtag chad gnyis grub sam
NK076(mu)001:792: ma grub / gnyis pa ltar na lhun grub kyi rang tshig nyams shing /
NK076(mu)001:793: dang po ltar na phyi rol pa dang mtshungs par thal /
NK076(mu)001:794: 'dod na lta ba rnams kyi nang nas mtha' chad
NK076(mu)001:795: pa nyid du phyi ma'i lan du rdzas ma spangs
NK076(mu)001:796: la mtshon tshul ma grub ces pa skad gsung /
NK076(mu)001:798: des na skyon can gnyis ni phung 'tshings mkhan gyi lta ba yin pas mi 'thad gsungs /
NK076(mu)001:799: bzhi pa rang gzhung skyon med lhun grub pa spyi mtshan nyid /
NK076(mu)001:801: chos nyid ka dag chos nyid dang ma rig skyon
NK076(mu)001:802: med pa gnyis de nyid dang gzhan brjod du med
NK076(mu)001:803: pa'am / ngo bo gcig la lhun grub bskyon med
NK076(mu)001:804: zlog byas kyi dbye bas tha dad du 'dod pa
NK076(mu)001:805: pa'am / ste / 'di gnyis don gcig gsung ma
NK076(mu)001:806: rtogs pa'i ngo gnyis pa'i go don rdzas chos nyid
NK076(mu)001:807: ma spang ma rig pa'i zlog par mtshan rtog pa'i
NK076(mu)001:808: ngo la rdzas ma rig ma spangs ye shes kyi
NK076(mu)001:809: pa'am / ste / bzlog par mtshon / chos dang
NK076(mu)001:810: chos nyid du 'brel ba ngo bo'i rdzas sangs rgyas
NK076(mu)001:811: kyis kyang mi phyed pa ni lhun grub chen po
NK076(mu)001:812: pa'am / ste / bzlog par mtshon / zhes bya ste / ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:813: rgyas pa ma rig ye shes tha dad min //
NK076(mu)001:814: ma rtogs rtogs pa'i lam 'dir gcig /ces pas so //
NK076(mu)001:815: yang dang po'i go don ma rig pa'i snang ba
NK076(mu)001:816: 'di nyid kyang chos nyid rang mtshan dri ma med
NK076(mu)001:818: rnyog ma dang bcas pa'i tshe chu'i rang bzhin mi snang ba ltar /
NK076(mu)001:820: sems can rnams kyis ma rig sogs 'bras kyi //
NK076(mu)001:821: lpags sbubs nang chud chos khams dge ba nyid //
NK076(mu)001:823: 'dir spangs na gzhan du'ang brjod pa med pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:825: 'khor ba spangs nas gzhan du ni //
NK076(mu)001:828: ka dag chen po zhes bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:830: thams cad dag ces bya ba yang //
NK076(mu)001:831: dngos po gsal dag ma yin te //
NK076(mu)001:832: rnam dpyad nyid na rnam par dpyad //
NK076(mu)001:834: de la btsan pa gsum las dang po ni /
NK076(mu)001:835: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi sar gnas kyi ma rig pa spangs sam ma spang /
NK076(mu)001:836: dang po ltar na gzhi ji ltar ba bzhin mngon du byas pa ma yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:837: gzhi'i dus na ma rig pa dang dbyer med du yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:838: 'dod na'ang rang gnas 'bras bus shub bur bshad pa spangs bar mi nus shing /
NK076(mu)001:839: gnyis pa ltar na sangs rgyas kyi ye shes la 'khrul pa ma kheg pa thal /
NK076(mu)001:840: ma rig pa ma spangs pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:841: 'dod na lam rgyud la brten pa don med do //
NK076(mu)001:844: dang po 'di re zhig khas mi len la /
NK076(mu)001:845: gnyis pa ltar na ngo bo ma spangs pa'i phyir ram /
NK076(mu)001:846: mtshon tshul ma spangs pa'i phyir zer /
NK076(mu)001:847: gnyis pa'i rtags ma grub te khas mi len cing /
NK076(mu)001:848: dang po ltar na ngo bo ma spangs kyang mtshon
NK076(mu)001:849: tshul mi gnas pas 'khrul par mi 'gyur na ci
NK076(mu)001:850: ste khyab pa ma grub gsungs /
NK076(mu)001:851: ci de ltar na mtshon tshul de ngo bo'i steng
NK076(mu)001:852: na rdzas dbyer med du ldan pa zhig yin nam
NK076(mu)001:854: de tsam du til 'bru nyid snum gyi ngo bor
NK076(mu)001:855: rdzas dbyer med du ldan pa zhig yin nam min
NK076(mu)001:856: zhes bya'o // ldan no zhe na 'dir yang ldan pa kho na'o //
NK076(mu)001:857: rdzas dbyer med pa'i phyir mtshon tshul yang ma spangs par thal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:858: der yang rdzas dbyer med pa'i phyir btags rtsag byas
NK076(mu)001:859: pa'i snum la'ang til gong ma spangs bar thal zhes
NK076(mu)001:860: bya'o // yang mi ldan zhes na 'dir yang mtshungs so //
NK076(mu)001:861: mtshon tshul ngo bo la mi ldan pa'i phyir ma rig pa'ii 'khrul snang spangs bar thal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:862: gong du nyid khu ba las mi ldan pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:863: snum gyis til 'bru spangs par thal zhes pa'i rdul
NK076(mu)001:864: bral tshangs pa'i blos kyang dpags par mi nus so
NK076(mu)001:865: // gnyis pa chos nyid nyams su blangs pas grol
NK076(mu)001:866: ba bzhin du ma rig pa nyams su blangs pas
NK076(mu)001:868: ngo bo gcig pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:869: ngo bo gnyis med kyi rang bzhin shes nas grol bar thal zhe'am /
NK076(mu)001:870: ma shes kyang grol bar thal zer /
NK076(mu)001:871: dang po 'dod thog gnyis pa ci'i phyir ngo bo gcig pa'i zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:872: gcig kyang gcig pa'i rang bzhin ma shes pas mi grol na ci ste khyab pa med do //
NK076(mu)001:873: gsum pa chos nyid dang 'khrul snang la bzang ngan med par thal /
NK076(mu)001:874: ngo bo gcig pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:875: ngo bo gnyis med du shes nas bzang ngan med par thal zer ram /
NK076(mu)001:876: mi shes kyang bzang ngan med par thal zer dang po 'dod thog gnyis pa ci'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:877: ngo bo gcig kyang ma rtogs pa'i shes ngo la
NK076(mu)001:878: bzang ngan du snang ba ci to te khyab pa
NK076(mu)001:879: med do // de bzhin du gong ma tha dad
NK076(mu)001:880: la bskal pa'i skyon rnams ngo bo gcig pas spangs
NK076(mu)001:881: med do // shing / gcig pa la bkod pa'i
NK076(mu)001:882: skyon rnams mtshon tshul tha dad pas spangs pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:883: dri ma med pa'i lta ba nyid du shes par
NK076(mu)001:884: med do // shing / bya'o // gsum pa grub mtha' bden pa gsum gyi gnas lugs la gsum /
NK076(mu)001:892: dang po ni rgyu yi theg pa thun mong dag rig pas dpyad na mi gnas pa'am /
NK076(mu)001:893: blo 'khrul ba'i bzad pa yul du bden pa 'di
NK076(mu)001:894: mi rigs te don dam la khyab ches pa ni
NK076(mu)001:895: ji skad du / kun rdzob 'di ltar snang ba 'di /
NK076(mu)001:896: rig pas brtags na 'ga' mi rnyed /
NK076(mu)001:897: ma rnyed pa ni don dam ste /
NK076(mu)001:898: ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:900: dang dmyal ba bden pa'i spros pas stong pa /
NK076(mu)001:901: 'di don la khyab chos sam som zhes 'dod la
NK076(mu)001:902: 'bras theg ma h+aa'i lugs kyi 'dir lhag pa kun
NK076(mu)001:903: rdzob kyi mtshan nyid bden pas stong pa'i snang ba
NK076(mu)001:905: de bsgrub pa la dngos dang /
NK076(mu)001:906: skabs 'phros kyi rtsod spong bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:909: rgyas pa kun rdzob chu zla ltar yin pas //
NK076(mu)001:910: ci yang 'gyur zhing cir yang 'grub zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:912: lam rim chu zla sgyu ma sprul pa bzhin ces so //
NK076(mu)001:913: phyogs chos rigs kyi spyi rigs pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:914: rigs lnga sgyu ma'i snang ba yin te /
NK076(mu)001:915: dam bca' snang ba'i ngo bo ma nges pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:916: gtan tshigs bzlog gnod kyi tshad ma ma grub par khas len tam /
NK076(mu)001:917: 'o na steng na dmyal ba la'ang bum pa nyid du snang bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:918: nges pa nyid dngos gzhan du mi 'gyur pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:920: lcags sregs sa gzhi su yi byas /
NK076(mu)001:921: me sogs de dag ci las byung //
NK076(mu)001:922: de 'dra de dag thams cad ni //
NK076(mu)001:923: sdig sems 'byung ba nga yis bshad //
NK076(mu)001:925: dmyal ba gnyis sems me sogs snang zhes pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:926: rdzas kyi dngos po gcig las log mthong drug dang
NK076(mu)001:927: yang dag dgu /ces snang ba ga cig pas gsal
NK076(mu)001:928: / gang du gzhan du mi 'gyur ba'i bden mthong
NK076(mu)001:929: la tha dad du ma dmigs pas khyab te 'phags
NK076(mu)001:931: de ltar na'ang nga la bum pa snang ba bzhin du khyod la mi snang bar thal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:932: rnam par dbye ste las mthun mi lta bu shes
NK076(mu)001:933: ngo thun mongs pa la ma nges pa'i phyir zer
NK076(mu)001:934: / khyad par ba la ma nges pa'i phyir zer /
NK076(mu)001:935: mi mthun pa byol song lta bu /
NK076(mu)001:936: dang po ltar na rtags ma grub la gnyis pa
NK076(mu)001:937: la ni las mthun la nges par snang yang mi
NK076(mu)001:938: mthun pa la ma khyab te dper na mig ser
NK076(mu)001:939: gyi nad kyis btab pas dung dkar po la ser
NK076(mu)001:940: por mthun par mthong ba de /
NK076(mu)001:941: dung ser po yod nas mthong lugs mthun pa med
NK076(mu)001:942: de nad rigs kyi dbang gis mthun par mthong ba
NK076(mu)001:943: bzhin no // yang dus gsum sdod tshugs la nges
NK076(mu)001:944: kyang dus gsum snga phyi ba la ma nges te
NK076(mu)001:945: bzhin no // / dus sngar gyi sa 'jim dus
NK076(mu)001:946: kyi phyis kyi jo dum da lta gyi bum pa
NK076(mu)001:947: rnams snang ba'i ngo bo ma nges pa'i phyir ro
NK076(mu)001:948: bzhin no // / // khyab pa ma grub ce na /
NK076(mu)001:949: gang du snang ba'i ngo bo ma grub pa la
NK076(mu)001:950: rigs pa rgyu las snang ba yin pas khyab te
NK076(mu)001:951: sgyu ma'i rta glang bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:952: gnyis pa nges tshig la'ang gnyis te thun mong pa dag te sam kri ta'i sgra las drangs te /
NK076(mu)001:953: ngan pa'am sgrib byed du gyur pa zhig la 'dod la /
NK076(mu)001:954: 'di nyid du mi bden pa'i phyir kun rdzob ces bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:955: gsum pa dbye ba la'ang 'og ma'i lugs kyis snang
NK076(mu)001:956: ba snang bzhin du me la mer don byed nus
NK076(mu)001:957: pa la yang dag kun rdzob dang /
NK076(mu)001:958: snang bzhin don byed mi nus smig rgyu la chur
NK076(mu)001:959: snang ba log pa'i kun rdzob bden gnyis su 'dod
NK076(mu)001:960: la / 'dir ma dag pa 'khor ba'i kun rdzob bden pa phung khams su rtog pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:961: dag pa myang 'das kyi kun rdzob bden pa lha
NK076(mu)001:962: dang lha mor snang ba'am sgyu ma'i chos drug tu
NK076(mu)001:964: bzhi pa 'og ma las dpag lugs gsum las /
NK076(mu)001:965: 'og ma'i kun rdzob ni rgyu rkyen gyis bskyed la /
NK076(mu)001:966: 'dir rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pas ngo bos dpags te /
NK076(mu)001:968: las rim rgyu rkyen rag lus med pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:970: gnyis pa 'og ma'i kun rdzob tu rkyen gyis bskyed pas mtshan nyid skye 'jigs can yin la /
NK076(mu)001:971: 'dir ni rgyu rkyen las ma skyes pas mtshan nyid skye 'jigs dang bral te /
NK076(mu)001:972: lam rim sgyu ma rdo rje btsan po mchog ces so //
NK076(mu)001:973: gsum pa 'og ma'i kun rdzob bden gnyis bzang ngan med pas rang bzhin gyis spags te /
NK076(mu)001:974: lam rim snang stong gnyis med rnal 'byor mtha' ces so //
NK076(mu)001:975: de ltar na'ang kun rdzob dang bden pa dbyer med
NK076(mu)001:976: la rtogs pa tha dad la ltos pa'i log mtshams
NK076(mu)001:977: kyi khyad ci yod zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:978: snang yang bden pas stong pa tsam du ngo bo
NK076(mu)001:979: gcig kyang gtan la 'bebs lugs kyi ldog pa tha
NK076(mu)001:980: dad de / dang por snang ba kun rdzob kyi
NK076(mu)001:981: bden par gtan la phab pas rang bzhin med par
NK076(mu)001:983: dngos su khyab pa'i rang mtshan mthong pas chu lkog gyur du shug las rtogs pa lta bu'o gsungs /
NK076(mu)001:986: lhag pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa la kun rdzob spyi mtshan nyid gyi khyabs sam ma khyab drangs /
NK076(mu)001:987: dang po ltar na lhag pa'i kun rdzob nyid log shes sgrib phyogs su thal /
NK076(mu)001:989: gang zhig gis sems gang dag la //
NK076(mu)001:990: yang dag sgrib byed kun rdzob 'dod //
NK076(mu)001:992: 'dod na sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom bya yang dag gi lam du bsal /
NK076(mu)001:993: gal te rigs spyis khyab kyang log shes su mi 'gyur na ci sto zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:994: gang du khyab grub kun rdzob kyi rigs spyis khyab pa la dag pa'i lam las kheg te /
NK076(mu)001:995: yang dag gi sgrib byed so so'i skye bo'i las lam bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:996: gnyis pa star na kun rdzob la rigs spyi khegs par thal /
NK076(mu)001:997: spyi mtshan gyis ma khyab pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:998: 'dod na shes bya lhag pa'i kun rdzob dngos po la mi gnas par thal /
NK076(mu)001:999: rigs spyi shing tsam khegs pas bye brag sha pa
NK076(mu)001:1000: la sogs pa kun khegs pa lta bu'o zhe na
NK076(mu)001:1001: / lan du khyab par khas blangs dgos te spyi
NK076(mu)001:1002: la ltos pa'i bye brag mi srid pa'i phyir ro
NK076(mu)001:1003: / // de ltar na lhag pa'i kun rdzob log shes nyid du thal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:1004: khyab pa ma grub ste snang tsam rigs kyi spyi
NK076(mu)001:1005: yin yang 'dir zhen yul du mi snang ba'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:1007: ji ltar snang ba 'di kho na /
NK076(mu)001:1008: kun rdzob kyi rigs spyi snang tsam la bzhag pa yin //
NK076(mu)001:1009: zhes gsung mod kyi bdag ni sngar gyi skyon brjod do //
NK076(mu)001:1010: skyon sel gnyis ka 'khrul par sems te /
NK076(mu)001:1011: dang por nges tshig la mtshan nyid du bsam nas
NK076(mu)001:1012: brjod cing gnyis par mtshan gzhi la mtshan nyid du
NK076(mu)001:1013: bsam nas bsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1014: des na kun rdzob spyi mtshan bden pa'i spros pa'i
NK076(mu)001:1015: stong pa yin pa'i phyir des lhag pa'i kun rdzob
NK076(mu)001:1016: la khyab pa ni 'gal ba ci'ang med do /
NK076(mu)001:1018: gnyis pa yang khyed lhag pa'i kun rdzob 'di ltar
NK076(mu)001:1019: snang ba kun lha'i dal du 'dod pa de ye
NK076(mu)001:1020: nas med pa la sgro btags pa zhig gam /
NK076(mu)001:1021: ngo bo nyid kyis yongs su grub pa gcig yin drang /
NK076(mu)001:1022: dang po ltar na lung las ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:1024: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK076(mu)001:1025: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK076(mu)001:1026: sa chu spyan dang ma ma ki /me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK076(mu)001:1027: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK076(mu)001:1028: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas zhing //
NK076(mu)001:1031: lam rim gsang ba nang gi 'dod yon lnga //
NK076(mu)001:1032: de rdzas rang bzhin mchod pa ste //
NK076(mu)001:1033: ces pa dang 'gal zhing rigs pa yang /
NK076(mu)001:1034: lam lha'i rnal 'byor bsgom pa don med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:1035: sgros btags ni mtshan nyid yongs su chad pa'i kun
NK076(mu)001:1036: brtags dngos med yin la dngos med ni don byed
NK076(mu)001:1037: nus pa mtha' dag gis stong pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1038: ri bong khyab grub gi rwa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:1039: gnyis pa yongs su grub pa ltar na'ang /
NK076(mu)001:1042: lus ngag sems dang chos thams cad //
NK076(mu)001:1043: gang nas mi gnas mi dmigs la /
NK076(mu)001:1044: mig yor tshul du sbyor ba yis /
NK076(mu)001:1046: man ngag lam rim las kyang /
NK076(mu)001:1047: rtog gnyis bral ba'i thabs mkhas kyis //
NK076(mu)001:1048: lhar gsal dngos po med bsgom na //
NK076(mu)001:1049: rang bzhin med las ci yang 'grub //
NK076(mu)001:1050: ces lha sgro btags su bshad pa dang 'gal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:1051: rigs pa ni lhar bskyed byed kyi don shes pa tsam la'ang ma rtog ltos par thal /
NK076(mu)001:1052: phung khams lha yi rang bzhin du grub zin nyid /
NK076(mu)001:1053: rgyu rkyen gzhan la mi ltos pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1054: gser sa khyab grub le sgrom bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:1055: gtan tshigs ma grub ste ltos na yongs grub kyi
NK076(mu)001:1056: dam bca' nyams pa nyid ma yin nam zhe na
NK076(mu)001:1057: / lan du rog bla ma rgan ni tha mal
NK076(mu)001:1058: gyi rtog pa spong pa'i gnyen po'i rnams rnam grangs
NK076(mu)001:1059: kyi kun rtags su bzhed de /
NK076(mu)001:1060: mthar lam gyi skad cig phyi ma la gnyen po
NK076(mu)001:1061: sangs rgyas rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin kyis
NK076(mu)001:1062: lam gyis spang gnyen gnyis char yang spong ba'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:1063: / zhes gsungs pa ni 'thad par mi sems te /
NK076(mu)001:1064: de ltar na lam rim kun brtags mtshan nyid med pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:1065: ces sgro btags rdzun pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1066: bskyed rim nyid log shes su thal /
NK076(mu)001:1067: dung ser khyab grub 'dzin bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:1068: 'dod na des 'khrul snang spong bar nus sam mi nus /
NK076(mu)001:1069: nus na mig ser can gyi skyes bus gzhan dag
NK076(mu)001:1070: tu ser 'dzin gyi log shes spong nus par thal
NK076(mu)001:1071: zhing / mi nus na bskyed rim bsgom pa don med du 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:1072: rang lugs ni yongs grub du 'dzin te /
NK076(mu)001:1073: sngar gyi lung gis kyang grub 'dus las kyang //
NK076(mu)001:1074: mdor na phung po lnga rnams ni //
NK076(mu)001:1075: sangs rgyas lngar ni rab tu grags //
NK076(mu)001:1076: rdo rje skye mched bdag nyid kyang //
NK076(mu)001:1077: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK076(mu)001:1078: sa ni spyan zhes bya ba ste //
NK076(mu)001:1079: chu yi khams ni ma ma ki /dkar dang sgrol ma zhes bya ba //
NK076(mu)001:1080: me dang rlung du rab tu grags //
NK076(mu)001:1083: man ngag las kyang ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:1084: man ngag dbang po thams cad kun //
NK076(mu)001:1085: rang bzhin yongs kyi dag pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:1086: ting 'dzin de bzhin gshegs pa sngar //
NK076(mu)001:1087: ye nas ma bcos ngang gis gnas //
NK076(mu)001:1090: rang lus 'dod nas phyag rgya che //
NK076(mu)001:1091: bsgom pas mngon du gyur pa'i lha //
NK076(mu)001:1092: mtshan dpe bzhi dang mngon drug rdzogs //
NK076(mu)001:1093: ces legs par mang du gsung la /
NK076(mu)001:1095: phung khams ltag rdzogs 'di dag chos can /
NK076(mu)001:1096: rang bzhin gyi 'gyur ba med pa'i yongs grub lha'i dal du yongs su grub te /
NK076(mu)001:1097: rang bzhin mthar phyin gyis phyin ci ma logs pa'i
NK076(mu)001:1098: yongs grub gzugs sku lam gyis byas pas mngon du
NK076(mu)001:1099: byar rung ba'i phyir dngul rdo khyab grub la dngul
NK076(mu)001:1100: rang bzhin gyis gnas pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:1101: de nyid kyis rang bzhin 'dus byas su'ang mi 'gyur
NK076(mu)001:1102: te med pa zhig yod par bsgrub pa ma yin
NK076(mu)001:1103: gyi / rang gnas nyid mngon du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1105: rol pa'i rgyud chos kyi dbyings ni thog ma nas gnas pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1106: de mngon du gyur pa ni rgyud dag ces bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:1108: gnyis pa don gyi bden pa la'ang bzhi /
NK076(mu)001:1112: dang po ni thun mong dag rigs pas dpyad na gnas pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:1113: blo ma 'khrul pa'i yul du bden pa'am /
NK076(mu)001:1114: bden rdzun gnyis char gyi spros pas stong pa zhes pa la 'dod la /
NK076(mu)001:1115: 'dir lhag ma ha'i lugs kyis pa don dam gyi
NK076(mu)001:1116: mtshan nyid ni rig pa spros pa dang bral ba
NK076(mu)001:1117: la snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis
NK076(mu)001:1118: grub pa'o // de bsgrub pa la dngos dang /
NK076(mu)001:1122: snying po gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid 'di //
NK076(mu)001:1123: pho mo ma yin ma ning min //
NK076(mu)001:1124: mtshan mar ma yin rigs rgyud min //
NK076(mu)001:1125: kha dog ma yin dbyibs ma yin //
NK076(mu)001:1126: gnas lugs ma yin gang yang min //
NK076(mu)001:1127: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK076(mu)001:1128: thabs kyi phyag rgya kun gyi rgyu //
NK076(mu)001:1131: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pa //
NK076(mu)001:1132: rtog pa smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK076(mu)001:1135: thun mong gi rigs pa rang bzhin med pa spros bral du sgrub pa /ni /
NK076(mu)001:1136: bum pa chos can phyogs chos yang dag par bsgrub bya rang bzhin med de /
NK076(mu)001:1137: gcig he du dang du ma dang bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1139: bum pa nyid gcig tu yod dam du mar yod /
NK076(mu)001:1140: dang po ltar na cha shas dang bcas par yod dam /
NK076(mu)001:1142: bcas par yod na du mar thal te /
NK076(mu)001:1143: skar khyab ma'i tshogs bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:1144: bral bar 'dod na rdul gyi gong bu rtsom pa'i
NK076(mu)001:1145: tshe phyogs cha drug gi rdul gyis bskor ram ma
NK076(mu)001:1146: bskor / ma bskor na gong bu rags pa mi 'grub cing /
NK076(mu)001:1147: bskor na dbus rdul gyi ngos te phyogs rdul drug la lta'am mi blta /
NK076(mu)001:1148: gnyis pa ltar na gzugs can ma yin pa'i thal te /
NK076(mu)001:1149: dbus rdul te drug po de la mi lta ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1150: dang po ltar na ngos thad ka thad kar lta'am /
NK076(mu)001:1151: ngos gcig gis kun la blta /
NK076(mu)001:1152: dang po ltar na dbus rdul chos can /
NK076(mu)001:1154: dbus rdul de nyid phyogs drug las lta ba'i cha re re yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1155: gnyis pa ltar na phyogs lnga'i rdul chos can phyogs re re'i nang du thim par thal /
NK076(mu)001:1156: dbus rdul gyi ngos gcig gcig gi lta ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1158: khyab pa tshad ma te 'dod na rags snang 'di nub par sems tsam nyi shu pa las /
NK076(mu)001:1159: drug gi gcig char sbyar ba na //
NK076(mu)001:1160: phra rab rdul cha drug tu 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:1161: drug po dag kyang go gcig na //
NK076(mu)001:1162: gong bu'ang rdul phran nyid du 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:1165: yang du mar yod na'ang du ma de gcig la ltos sam mi ltos /
NK076(mu)001:1166: dang po ltar na gcig tu thal /
NK076(mu)001:1169: ma ltos na khyab byed gcig la ma grub pa'i
NK076(mu)001:1170: phyir rang rgyud khyab bya du ma'ang ma grub par
NK076(mu)001:1171: thal / rdul gnyis kyi gseng thams cad /
NK076(mu)001:1172: grangs gcig la ma ltos par du mar mi 'ong la /
NK076(mu)001:1174: gang gcig dang du ma las kyi spros pa dang
NK076(mu)001:1175: bral ba la rang bzhin med pas khyab te nam
NK076(mu)001:1176: mkha' bzhin no // gnyis pa thun mongs ma yin
NK076(mu)001:1177: pa'i rigs pas spros bral de nyid snang ba ngo
NK076(mu)001:1178: bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub pa nyid du
NK076(mu)001:1179: mkha' bzhin no // bsgrub pa ni / gong gi spros bral de chos can /
NK076(mu)001:1180: snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur grub ste /
NK076(mu)001:1181: snang tsam nyid nas brtags na yang du ma ma grub cing snang tshod ma bkag pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1182: gtan tshigs ma grub na snang stong la 'brel pa yod dam med /
NK076(mu)001:1183: dang po ltar na grub pa nyid bdag gcig gam de byung yin /
NK076(mu)001:1184: dang po ltar na'ang bdag gcig gi 'brel ba'i mtshan
NK076(mu)001:1185: nyid rang bzhin dbyer med yin la de las byung
NK076(mu)001:1186: ba'i de 'brel ba'i mtshan nyid med na mi 'byung
NK076(mu)001:1187: pa'i rgyu 'bras yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1188: gnyis pa ltar na gzhi'i dus na chos dang chos nyid ma yin pa thal /
NK076(mu)001:1189: lam dus na tshogs gnyis brten pa'i rgyu tha dad du thal /
NK076(mu)001:1190: 'bras bu'i dus na sku nyid ngo bo phan tshun gcig gi ga cig spang bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:1191: snang stong 'brel ba med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1193: 'jig rten brtan g.yo las las so //
NK076(mu)001:1194: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK076(mu)001:1195: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK076(mu)001:1196: rang bzhin ngang gis de ltar gnas ces so //
NK076(mu)001:1198: gang du 'brel med la rdzas phan tshun spangs pas khyab ste /
NK076(mu)001:1199: bum pa dang ka ba bzhin /
NK076(mu)001:1200: khyab pa'ang sngar gyi rtags rang rgyud la grub pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1201: gnyis pa nges tshig ni gnyis char mthun par pa
NK076(mu)001:1202: ra ma d+hi'i sgra las drangs pas dam chos pa
NK076(mu)001:1204: rdzogs pa'i khyad par yang dag gi 'bras bu las mi bslu ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:1206: 'og ma'i lugs kyi spros pa phyogs re bkag pa rnam grangs don dam bden pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:1207: spros pa ma lus par bkag pa rnam grangs ma
NK076(mu)001:1208: yin pa'i don dam bden pa gnyis su 'dod la
NK076(mu)001:1209: / 'dir ni chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin spros
NK076(mu)001:1210: pa dang bral bar rang bzhin nam don dam skor
NK076(mu)001:1211: bdun rig pa la lhun gyis grub pa 'bras bu'i
NK076(mu)001:1212: / don dam / shes bya la sgrib g.yogs kyi dben pa ye shes don dam gsum du dabye'o //
NK076(mu)001:1213: de ltar na'ang rang bzhin dang 'bras bu ni mngon du byas pa dang ma byas pas phye la /
NK076(mu)001:1214: 'bras bu dang ye shes spyi dang bye brag gi phye zhing //
NK076(mu)001:1215: rang bzhin dang ye shes gzhi 'bras kyi cha las phye ba nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:1216: bzhi pa spags lugs ni gsum las /
NK076(mu)001:1217: 'og ma'i don dam ni stong mthar thug te ltogs
NK076(mu)001:1218: mo rke stong dang 'dra la 'dir stong mtha' las
NK076(mu)001:1219: kyang grol te / rnam pa ngo bo nyid kyi
NK076(mu)001:1220: rgyu lhun gyis grub pa'i ngo bos spags te bzang
NK076(mu)001:1223: dpag bsam shing dang rin chen ltar //
NK076(mu)001:1224: de kun ngo bo nyid bsgyur gnas //
NK076(mu)001:1226: yang 'og ma pa'i snang chos dor ba'i stong zlog rkyang pa yin la /
NK076(mu)001:1227: 'dir ma spangs la mi ldan pa'i phyir mtshan nyid kyi spags te /
NK076(mu)001:1228: gang yang ma spang mi ldan pa'i //
NK076(mu)001:1229: ma bral phyir na bral zhes bya //
NK076(mu)001:1231: yang 'og ma'i don skye med sgra ji bzhin par
NK076(mu)001:1232: sogs pas byin rlabs rig pa dang rang snang du
NK076(mu)001:1233: mi 'char la / 'dir ni rig pa rang snang
NK076(mu)001:1234: lha dang gzhal yas khang los sar 'char ba'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:1235: byin gyis rlabs kyis spags te /
NK076(mu)001:1236: mnyam nyid ngang las ma g.yos bzhin //
NK076(mu)001:1237: thabs kyi phyag rgya chen por ston //
NK076(mu)001:1240: de ltar na spros bral la snang ba ngo bo
NK076(mu)001:1241: nyid kyi rgyu grub pa ste bskyed byed kyi rgyu
NK076(mu)001:1242: yin / rnam 'jog gi rgyu min drang /
NK076(mu)001:1244: don dam nyid dngos por thal /
NK076(mu)001:1245: bskyed byed kyi rgyur grub pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:1248: gnyis pa ltar na kun rdzob de nyid don las mi bslu ba'i 'jug yul du thal /
NK076(mu)001:1249: don dam gyi rnam par bzhag pa'i 'bras bu yin na'ang phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1252: yang kun rdzob tsam po 'jug yul min yang lhag pa'i kun rdzob 'jug yul du rung ste /
NK076(mu)001:1253: rtogs don las mi bslu ba'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:1254: spyi mtshan gyi khyab ma khyab rtags pas khogs so ces zer te /
NK076(mu)001:1255: lan ni rdzas ma spangs par 'dog pa min gnas pa ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu ste /
NK076(mu)001:1256: lcags nag mer ldan bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:1257: de ltar na'ang don dam la spros pa ma khegs par thal /
NK076(mu)001:1258: kun rdzob kyi rdzas ma spang pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:1259: bden mod kyi de tsam du lcags nag grang mo
NK076(mu)001:1260: la me ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub
NK076(mu)001:1262: gnyis pa ltar na 'khregs rdo dang sprad pa'i rkyen rtsol ba don med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:1263: rgyu med rkyen la mi ltos pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1264: dang po ltar na lcags nag grang mo la bsregs
NK076(mu)001:1265: byed mngon gyur gyi don byed ma khegs par thal
NK076(mu)001:1266: / me rdzas ma spang ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1268: spros bral gyi dam bca' bud ce na /
NK076(mu)001:1269: grang mo'i dam bca' bud do //
NK076(mu)001:1270: rtags ma grub ste grangs mo rkyang pa khas ma blangs pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:1271: 'dir yang mtshungs te spros bral kyang khas ma blang pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1272: gang du spros pa ma khegs pa nyid don dam du 'gal te kun rdzob bzhin zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:1273: khyod kyi me'i rang mtshan ma khegs pa nyid grang mor 'gal te /
NK076(mu)001:1274: me nyid bzhin zhes brjod pa'am /
NK076(mu)001:1275: yang don dam stong nyid rang gis stong ngam mi stong /
NK076(mu)001:1276: gnyis pa ltar na nyi tshe ba'i stong nyid du 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:1277: spros pa phyogs gcig las ma chod pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1278: dang po ltar na stong nyid dngos po thal te /
NK076(mu)001:1279: rang gi bsgrub chos kyis dor ba'i phyir zhes mgo 'dre bar 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:1280: gsum pa bden pa dbyer med la'ang bzhi /
NK076(mu)001:1285: theg pa gzhan nyan thos pa bzhin du snang ba
NK076(mu)001:1286: la stong pa'i rtsis ma zin pa'i snang ba nyid
NK076(mu)001:1287: snang ba rang rgyud du mi 'dod /
NK076(mu)001:1288: dbu ma pa bzhin du stong pa la snang ba'i
NK076(mu)001:1289: rtsis ma zin pa'i stong pa ga cig pu bar
NK076(mu)001:1290: mi 'dod de / 'dir ni snang stong dngos mnyam
NK076(mu)001:1291: gyi bden pa shes bya bden pa dbyer med blo'i
NK076(mu)001:1293: de sgrub pa la dngos dang /
NK076(mu)001:1298: bden pa gnyis ka dbyer med pas //
NK076(mu)001:1299: 'phrul dag'i tshul de tha dad med //
NK076(mu)001:1302: snang stong dbyer med rnal 'byor mtha' //zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:1305: bden pa dbyer med yin te /
NK076(mu)001:1306: snang stong gang gi phyogs su ma thug pa'i phyir ro /
NK076(mu)001:1307: gtan tshigs ma grub zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:1312: dper na rdo yi dngos po las //
NK076(mu)001:1313: brtag sam phye mar byas nas ni //
NK076(mu)001:1314: rlung gi ngo la bskyod byas na //
NK076(mu)001:1315: de la rang bzhin gang yang med //
NK076(mu)001:1317: sngar gyi gcig du bral gyis kyang gnod la /
NK076(mu)001:1318: gnyis pa ltar na da lta snang ba gsal lo //
NK076(mu)001:1319: ma yin te 'khrul ngo la snga ma'i don snang ba yin gyi /
NK076(mu)001:1320: rigs pas dpyad na mi gnas pa'i phyir chos kun stong pa'i mtha' can nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:1322: de nyid dbyer med pa kho na'o //
NK076(mu)001:1324: gtan tshigs la the tshom za'o zhe na //
NK076(mu)001:1325: rgyu mtshan yod nas za'am med nas za /
NK076(mu)001:1326: dang po ltar na nges shes bskyed pa la'ang the tshom za bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:1327: gnyis pa ltar na 'brel ba yod nas za'am /
NK076(mu)001:1329: gnyis pa ltar na mig gis kyang sgra snyan mi snyan la the tshom za bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:1330: 'dod na sgra yul na med par the tshom za mi za'i brtags pa mi mtshungs so //
NK076(mu)001:1331: dang po ltar na bdag gcig gam de las byung /
NK076(mu)001:1332: bdag gcig na byas pas kyang mi rtag pa la the tshom za bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:1333: de las byung na du bas kyang me la the tshom za bar thal lo //
NK076(mu)001:1334: khyab pa ma grub ce na /
NK076(mu)001:1335: gang na gang snang stong gang gi yang phyogs su
NK076(mu)001:1336: ma thug pa la dbyer med kyis khyab te chu
NK076(mu)001:1337: zla bzhin no // mdor na snang ba ma spangs snang mtha' las grol /
NK076(mu)001:1338: stong pa ma spangs stong mtha' mi 'dzin /
NK076(mu)001:1339: gnyis ka ma spangs thad kyi dben /
NK076(mu)001:1340: dbyer med ces brjod pa nyid kyang tha dad du zhen pa rnam par bcad pa tsam nyid las /
NK076(mu)001:1341: yongs gcod dbyer med du 'dzin pa dang yang bral te /
NK076(mu)001:1342: blo'i spyod yul dang bral ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:1344: de min zhen pa dgrol phyir las //
NK076(mu)001:1345: tha snyad gnyis par bsam brjod 'das //
NK076(mu)001:1348: snang stong gang gi'ang ris su ma chad pa'i phyir dbyer med do //
NK076(mu)001:1350: gcig la gnyis med pa'i dbyer med sems tsam gyi
NK076(mu)001:1351: gzungs 'dzin gnyis med pa'i rang rig rang gsal dang
NK076(mu)001:1352: / mtha' gnyis bkag pa'i dbyer med dbu ma sgyu
NK076(mu)001:1353: ma lta bu'i rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam
NK076(mu)001:1354: / dang / shes ngo la ltos pa'i rnam grangs
NK076(mu)001:1355: dbyer med rab tu mi gnas pa'i rnam gcad khegs
NK076(mu)001:1357: ngo bo dbyer med gsang sngags pa'i snang stong zung 'jug gi grub mtha'o //
NK076(mu)001:1359: 'og ma'i snang stong res 'jog tu gyur pas ngo bo skur 'debs su song la /
NK076(mu)001:1360: 'dir ni snang stong dus gcig du chad pas skur
NK076(mu)001:1361: 'debs su ma song ba'i phyir ngo bo spags te
NK076(mu)001:1363: a ni stong dang mi stong gi /
NK076(mu)001:1364: dbu ma'ang dmigs su yod ma yin /
NK076(mu)001:1366: yang 'og ma pa'i dbyer med mthar thug spyod pa'i
NK076(mu)001:1367: rigs ngor grub pa 'dod pa'i mtshan nyid gzung du
NK076(mu)001:1368: yod la / 'dir ni blo'i spyod yul dang bral
NK076(mu)001:1369: ba'i phyir mtshan nyid phyogs gcig tu med pas mtshan
NK076(mu)001:1372: de min zhen pa dgrol phyir las //
NK076(mu)001:1373: tha snyad gnyis par bsam brjod 'das //
NK076(mu)001:1375: yang 'og ma pa'i snang stong rang bzhin yod med
NK076(mu)001:1376: ris chad du song la 'dir snang stong dbyer med
NK076(mu)001:1379: snang stong dbyer med rnal 'byor mtha' //zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:1381: ci de ltar na dbyer med spyod yul dang bral
NK076(mu)001:1382: ba de thos bsam kyi gtan la dbab du yod
NK076(mu)001:1383: dam med / dang po ltar blo'i spyod yul dang bral ba nyams la /
NK076(mu)001:1384: gnyis pa ltar na rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa'i nges shes cis grub ce na /
NK076(mu)001:1385: bden mod kyi rang mtshan rtogs pa'i mthar mi ltos te /
NK076(mu)001:1386: chu brgal ba'i gru bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:1387: rtogs byed kyi shes rab su ltos pa mi 'gal gyi /
NK076(mu)001:1388: brjod byed zab mo'i sgra spyis drangs shing rgyud nas brjod bya zab mo'i don rtogs par 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:1390: dbu ma yig ge med pa'i chos rnams la //
NK076(mu)001:1391: nyan bde ston par byed pa gang //
NK076(mu)001:1392: 'gyur ba med la sgro btags nas //
NK076(mu)001:1393: nyan cing len par byed pa yin //
NK076(mu)001:1395: yang blo'i spyod yul dang bral ba la bral bar rtogs pa'i nges shes yod dam med zhes drangs /
NK076(mu)001:1396: gnyis pa ltar na de tshad mas gtan la ma phabs par thal /
NK076(mu)001:1397: nges shes med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1398: dang po ltar na nges shes de nyid 'khrul lam ma 'khrul /
NK076(mu)001:1399: gnyis pa ltar na don dang mthun par 'dzin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1400: blo'i spyod yul dang bral bar bud do //
NK076(mu)001:1401: dang po ltar na brdzun pa sgro btags su thal /
NK076(mu)001:1402: blo 'khrul ba'i yul yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1403: nam mkha' la skra bshad 'dzag snang bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:1405: nges shes yod cing ma 'khrul ba'i yul du 'jal bar 'dod do //
NK076(mu)001:1406: blo'i spyod yul du thal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:1408: gtan la 'bebs pa'i dus su ma bral bar thal zer ram /
NK076(mu)001:1409: khebs pa'i rang mtshan nyid ma bral bar thal zer /
NK076(mu)001:1410: dang po rtags ma grub la gnyis pa'i khyab pa
NK076(mu)001:1411: ma grub ste rtogs pa'i rang mtshan blo mtha' gang
NK076(mu)001:1412: gis kyang ma rig pa nyid yin no //
NK076(mu)001:1413: yang snang stong dbyer med pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:1414: snang ba skye 'gags med pa'i tshe de dang ngo
NK076(mu)001:1415: bo nyid du bdag gcig pa'i phyir stong nyid skye
NK076(mu)001:1416: 'gags byed dam mi byed ce na /
NK076(mu)001:1418: snang stong skye 'gags byed kyi ngo bo mi byed ces bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:1419: de ltar na snang stong bdag mi gcig par thal /
NK076(mu)001:1420: skye 'gags byed mi byed kyi 'gal ba'i chos yin pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:1421: de tsam du mi rtag rtog skad cig skye 'gags
NK076(mu)001:1422: byed pa'i tshe de dang bdag gcig pa'i byas chos
NK076(mu)001:1423: bum rdzas skye 'gags byed dam mi byed /
NK076(mu)001:1424: dang po ltar na da ltar bum 'dzin gyi shes
NK076(mu)001:1425: pa skad gcig gnyis pa la bum pa'i rdzas rgyun
NK076(mu)001:1428: gnyis pa ltar na mi rtag rtog bum pa'i bdag mi gcig par thal /
NK076(mu)001:1429: skye 'gags byed mi byed 'gal ba'i chos yin pa'i phyir ro zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:1430: bzhi pa lhun grub chen po'i gzhi'i bden pa gsum du nges par byed pa'i tshad ma ni /
NK076(mu)001:1433: bden pa kun rdzob don dam dang //
NK076(mu)001:1434: gnyis su med dang rnam gsum yang //
NK076(mu)001:1435: de gsum nyid du mnyam pas gsal //
NK076(mu)001:1438: de yang rnam gsum gnas tshul bzhag ces so //
NK076(mu)001:1440: gnas lugs sam rang bzhin gyi gzhi chos can /
NK076(mu)001:1441: bden pa gsum du nges te /
NK076(mu)001:1442: rnam pa ma 'dres rtog bden pa gnyis su snang zhing /
NK076(mu)001:1443: rang bzhin dbyer med yongs su rdzogs pa nyid /
NK076(mu)001:1444: sangs rgyas kyis kyang dgag par mi spyod pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1445: gtan tshigs ma grub na mkhyen pa'i ye shes rgyun chad du thal /
NK076(mu)001:1447: gnyis ka rang rgyud kyi lung gis grub pa nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:1448: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi bstan to //
NK076(mu)001:1449: gnyis pa 'khrul snang brtags pa'i gzhi la bzhis bstan te /
NK076(mu)001:1452: bye brag tu gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1456: dang po ni rje nya ri ba kha gcig na re lam pa'i blos brtags pas na brtags gazhi'o //
NK076(mu)001:1457: ces zer ba'ang mi rigs te /
NK076(mu)001:1458: sgros btags la spang bya'i rdzas ma grub te //
NK076(mu)001:1459: smig rgyu la chu rags mi dgos pa bzhin //
NK076(mu)001:1460: 'dod na lam rgyud la bstan pa don med du 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:1461: yang lam nyid kyang brtags gzhir thal /
NK076(mu)001:1462: lam pa'i blos brtags pa'i phyir zhes kyang gsungs /
NK076(mu)001:1463: yang ru gsung kha gcig na re so sor rtogs
NK076(mu)001:1464: pa'i shes rab kyis brtags dpyad bya ba'i gzhir gyur
NK076(mu)001:1465: pa'o zer ba'ang mi rigs te /
NK076(mu)001:1466: shes bya gsum char brtags gzhir thal /
NK076(mu)001:1467: shes rab kyi spyad bya yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1468: brtag khyab lung gis grub cing /
NK076(mu)001:1469: 'dod na shes bya la ma 'khrul chos mi srid par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:1470: rang lugs ni yang dag du ma grub pas las log par brtag pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:1471: lam rim 'khor dang 'das dngos zhen snang brtag ces gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1472: de ltar na'ang myang 'das log rtog tu thal /
NK076(mu)001:1474: zhen ngo la 'dod pa nyid yin la //
NK076(mu)001:1475: rang mtshan la'ang khyab pa med do //
NK076(mu)001:1478: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:1480: brtag gzhi gnyis su bstan pa'i chos //
NK076(mu)001:1483: bye brag tu 'khor ba'i chos gtan la dbab pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)001:1486: 'khrul ba'i rang bzhin chos nyid las ma g.yos par bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1489: 'khrul gzhi'i tshul ni rang bzhin gyi //
NK076(mu)001:1490: sdom 'di nges par shes par bya //
NK076(mu)001:1496: gzhi yod pa las 'khrul par smra ba kha gcig lhun grub skyon can na re /
NK076(mu)001:1497: gnas lugs kyi gzhi la 'khrul pa'i rgyu thog mar nas grub nas yod de /
NK076(mu)001:1498: de las 'khrul zer ba ni mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:1499: de ltar na 'khrul pa spang gis mi spong bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:1500: gzhi la dbyer med du grub pa'i phyir gser dang g.ya' bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:1502: sems nyid dmigs su med pa la //
NK076(mu)001:1503: dngos por rang rgyud gzhir smra ba /
NK076(mu)001:1504: de'i rigs rgyud rtag par lhung /
NK076(mu)001:1506: gnyis pa gzhi med pa las 'khrul pa smra bar kha cig na ka dag skyon can re /
NK076(mu)001:1507: gnas lugs kyi gzhi la 'khrul pa'i rgyu gtan grub pa med de glo bur ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:1509: de ltar na rgyud dag gi sangs rgyas la'ang 'khrul
NK076(mu)001:1510: pa 'byung bar thal de rgyu med kyang 'byung ba'i
NK076(mu)001:1511: phyir ro // nam mkha'i me tog bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:1513: gzhi la ye nas med ces smra //
NK076(mu)001:1514: zhes pa blo la yod do zhes //
NK076(mu)001:1515: bskur ba gang yin chad lta nyid ces so //
NK076(mu)001:1517: yod med gnyis med las 'khrul par 'dod de /
NK076(mu)001:1518: gnas lugs kyi gzhi la ma rig ye shes dbyer med kyi /
NK076(mu)001:1519: de nyid rtogs na ye shes la /
NK076(mu)001:1523: don gnyis skad cig ris med pas /
NK076(mu)001:1524: de'i rgyu rkyen rang bzhin nyid /
NK076(mu)001:1525: sman gyi phan gnod ji bzhin du //
NK076(mu)001:1526: thams cad ma lus rgyu gcig pas //
NK076(mu)001:1527: mi mthun khyad par so sor snang //
NK076(mu)001:1528: de gsungs phyir na rkyen gyi phye //
NK076(mu)001:1533: thag pa sbrul du mthong ba lta bu'o gsung /
NK076(mu)001:1534: gnyis pa ji ltar 'khrul pa'i tshul la /
NK076(mu)001:1535: dngos dang skabs 'phros kyi don no //
NK076(mu)001:1538: spyan 'grel rgyu rkyen 'bras bu 'byung ba'i dus //
NK076(mu)001:1539: tshul dang nyes pa sgrub byed pa //
NK076(mu)001:1540: nye bar mtshon pas rnam par dbye //
NK076(mu)001:1541: zhar la spyi'i dgos bshad bya //
NK076(mu)001:1542: ces pa'i don gyis brgyad du gnas pa las /
NK076(mu)001:1543: dang po rgyu ni bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:1544: rgyud mtshungs ldan cig nyer len dang //
NK076(mu)001:1546: rgyud pa'i rgyu ni sems nyid bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ste /
