NK076(mu)001:1547: de yin bzhin du ngo ma shes pas 'khrul pa'i rgyu gyur pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1549: snying po e ma ho bde gshegs snying po las /
NK076(mu)001:1550: rang gi rnam rtog las kyi sprul //
NK076(mu)001:1552: mtshungs par ldan pa'i rgyu ni lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK076(mu)001:1553: ma rig pa ste rkyen dang 'phrad na 'khrul pa
NK076(mu)001:1554: 'byung rung du gnas pa ni gser dang g.ya' bzhin
NK076(mu)001:1556: rgya mtsho kun gzhi rnam pa gnyis bral bas //
NK076(mu)001:1557: zhen pa snang bar 'gyur ma yin //
NK076(mu)001:1558: rtag tu rang mtshan snang gyur pas //
NK076(mu)001:1559: mig gis mig bzhin ma rigs pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1561: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pa te /
NK076(mu)001:1562: dge sdig gi bag chags kun gzhi las bzhag nas /
NK076(mu)001:1563: gnas mtho dman du lhan cig byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1565: snying po rgyu drug skye 'gags lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK076(mu)001:1566: gnas dang 'khrul 'khor sdug bsngal la sogs pa //
NK076(mu)001:1567: log rtog nyid las ces so //
NK076(mu)001:1568: nyer bar len pa'i rgyu ni /
NK076(mu)001:1570: brtags pa'i bag chags kun gzhi la 'dzin par byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1572: 'dus pa bdag 'dzin bdag gi rtog pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:1573: phyin ci log stobs brtson 'grus kyis //
NK076(mu)001:1574: gnas ngan len pa'i ded dpon byed //
NK076(mu)001:1576: gnyis pa rkyen ni las dang nyon mongs pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:1579: bsod nams ma yin pa'i las /
NK076(mu)001:1581: de dag kun nas slong ba po ni nyon mongs dug lnga ste /
NK076(mu)001:1583: rim gsum rkyen gnyis brten pa las gsum dang //
NK076(mu)001:1584: kun brtags ma rig nyon mongs lnga //
NK076(mu)001:1586: de ltar na rgyu dang rkyen khyad par ci yod ce na /
NK076(mu)001:1587: 'bras bu'i ngo bo bskyed par byed pa'i rgyu la /
NK076(mu)001:1588: khyad par bskyed par byed pa rkyen no //
NK076(mu)001:1589: gsum pa bskyed pa'i ngo bo 'bras bu ni /
NK076(mu)001:1590: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten gzung char snang ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:1591: nang bcud sems can 'dzin char snang zhing zhen pa'i chos sdug bsngal gyi rnam par smin pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1593: rim gsum ngo bo snod bcud 'jig rten gyi //
NK076(mu)001:1594: snang zhing zhen pa'i chos rnams so //
NK076(mu)001:1597: thog ma dang tha ma med par 'khrul zhing sdug bsngal gyi long brtags te /
NK076(mu)001:1599: rim gsum thog ma tha ma med dus nas //
NK076(mu)001:1600: yang dag don la rtog pas nyams //
NK076(mu)001:1602: 'khor tshul ni rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba bcu gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:1603: de la yang phyi nang gnyis las /
NK076(mu)001:1604: dang po la rgyu dang 'brel ba drug dang /
NK076(mu)001:1605: rkyen dang 'brel pa drug go /dang po ni sa
NK076(mu)001:1606: bon las myu gu de la rim pa bzhin du
NK076(mu)001:1614: nang rten cing 'brel pa don bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:1619: dang po ni med na mi 'byung zhing ltos pas grub pa zhig ste /
NK076(mu)001:1621: dbu ma gang la brten te gang 'byung pa //
NK076(mu)001:1622: de ni re zhig de nyid min //
NK076(mu)001:1623: de las gzhan pa'ang ma yin no //
NK076(mu)001:1626: ma rig pa la sogs bcu gnyis so //
NK076(mu)001:1627: khyad par du ma rig pa ni de kho na nyid la 'gebs pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1628: 'du byed ni yul la dmigs pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1629: rnam par shes pa ni bye brag tu shes pa ni bye brag tu 'byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1630: ming ni ming gzhi'i phung po'o //
NK076(mu)001:1631: gzugs ni mer nur mkhrang thung su 'chags pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1632: skye mched drug ni mig la sogs pa drug dod pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1633: reg pa ni gsum 'dus nas yongs su gcod pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1634: tshor ba ni nyams su myong ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:1635: sred pa ni tshor ba la chags pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1636: len pa ni bskyed pa'i rgyu rkyen la chags pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1637: srid pa ni ma'i mngal du las kyi bag chags nus pa can du gyur pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1638: skye ba ni mngal las phyir byung ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:1639: rgas pa ni lang tsho yol rgyun 'gyur ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:1640: shi ba ni srog gi dbang po rgyun chad pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1642: las nyon mongs pa sdug bsngal gsum nyid de /
NK076(mu)001:1644: mdo las dang po brgyad pa dgu nyon mongs //
NK076(mu)001:1645: gnyis dang bcu pa las yin te //
NK076(mu)001:1646: lhag ma bdun ni sdug bsngal 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:1647: zhes gsungs pa'i don bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:1648: de ltar phyi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba bcu gnyis kyi tshul du phyir 'khor zhing /
NK076(mu)001:1649: nang rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba bcu gnyis kyi tshul du nang du 'khor ba nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:1651: rten 'brel bcu gnyis tshul dag tu //
NK076(mu)001:1655: 'dod bya 'phags pa'i lam yang dag pa dang bral zhing //
NK076(mu)001:1656: spang bya sdug bsngal gyi tshol ba nyams su myong ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:1658: 'phags lam bral dang sdug bsngal myong //
NK076(mu)001:1659: nyes pa rnam pa gnyis su gsungs //
NK076(mu)001:1662: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa skad cig mas mi rtag la /
NK076(mu)001:1663: rgyun gyis rtag pa des grub par byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1665: rgyun dang bcas pa'i skad gcig mas //
NK076(mu)001:1666: las kyi byed por brjod pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1668: bdun pa'i dpe ni gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:1669: 'khor ba'i dpe zo chu khyud mo lta bu dang /
NK076(mu)001:1670: mched pa'i dpe'i rtsa sogs la me btang ba lta bu'o //
NK076(mu)001:1672: zo chu rtsa sogs me dpe bzhin //
NK076(mu)001:1676: 'khor ba'i mtshangs shes shing mya ngan las 'das pa'i lam la 'jug par 'gyur ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:1678: sdug bsngal med na nges 'byung med //
NK076(mu)001:1680: gsum pa 'khrul pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK076(mu)001:1681: de ltar 'khrul yang rang bzhin chos nyid las ma g.yos pa med de /
NK076(mu)001:1682: sgyu ma'i bslus pa'i snang ba lta bu'o //
NK076(mu)001:1684: de bzhin rigs la 'gyur med pas //
NK076(mu)001:1685: shul don rang las gzhan med phyir //
NK076(mu)001:1686: 'phrul dag'i tshul te gzhan nas min //
NK076(mu)001:1688: skabs 'phros ni de ltar na'ang 'khor ba'i dus la thog mtha' med drangs /
NK076(mu)001:1689: dang po ltar na dbyings mtha' can du 'gyur zhing
NK076(mu)001:1690: lung las kyang thog ma med dang tha ma med
NK076(mu)001:1691: dus nas / yang dag don la rtog pas nyams //
NK076(mu)001:1693: rtsom med bzhi de kun tu nyams //
NK076(mu)001:1694: ces pa spang bar mi nus la //
NK076(mu)001:1695: gnyis pa ltar na lam 'bad pa don med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:1696: stong pa'i mtha' med pa'i phyir zhes pa la /
NK076(mu)001:1697: kha gcig na re thog ma ni yod de ma rig pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1698: zhes zer ba ni ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:1699: ma rig pa ni chos nyid dang mtshungs ldan du gnas la /
NK076(mu)001:1700: de dang bdag gcig pa'i chos nyid la thog mtha' med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1701: yang kha gcig na re 'brid pa yod la gnod pa med pa'i phyir tha ma'ang yod de /
NK076(mu)001:1702: sbyang gi til bzhin zhes zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:1703: de tsam du ngas kyang 'di nas shar phyogs su
NK076(mu)001:1704: kha bltas te rings du rgyug na nam mkha'i mtha'
NK076(mu)001:1705: rnyed ces khas len pa cis dgag /rnyed rgyu'i mtha'
NK076(mu)001:1706: nyid ma grub pa ci ste rnyed par khas len
NK076(mu)001:1707: zhe na / yod rgyu'i gral gyi mtha' nyid ma
NK076(mu)001:1708: grub par ci ste mtha' yod par khas len zhes
NK076(mu)001:1709: zhe na / bya'o // 'brid pa yod la gnon mkhan med pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:1710: bgrod pa yod la bzlog mkhan med pa'i phyir zhes pa'i mgo snyoms kyis khegs pa nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:1712: ma rig 'khrul 'khor 'di la zad med 'phel ba med ces gsungs /
NK076(mu)001:1714: dbyings la dbri mnan med pa'i phyir khams gsum spyi
NK076(mu)001:1715: btsan du thog mtha' gnyis ka med la lam gyis
NK076(mu)001:1716: grol bar nus pa'i phyir gang zag sgos btsan du
NK076(mu)001:1717: tha ma ni yod ces bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:1718: de ltar na'ang spyi dpe dgos la khyab sam ma khyab /
NK076(mu)001:1719: dang po ltar na sgos btsan du'ang tha ma med par thal /
NK076(mu)001:1720: khyab byed la med pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1721: skyes bu'i mtshan dpe bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:1724: dgos la ma khyab pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1725: bye brag nyid yin no zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:1726: rnam par phye nas smra te /
NK076(mu)001:1727: rigs spyis khyab pa'i phyir zer ram /
NK076(mu)001:1728: tshogs spyis khyab pa'i phyir zer /
NK076(mu)001:1729: dang po gtan tshigs ma grub ste spyi log na
NK076(mu)001:1730: bye brag bzlog pa'i rigs don du khas ma blangs
NK076(mu)001:1731: shing / gnyis pa khyab pa ma grub ste /
NK076(mu)001:1732: tshogs pa'i spyi khegs kyang mi khegs pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:1733: shing rta zhig pa'i 'khor lo bzhin zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:1734: gal te tha ma yod pa'i phyir ltos kyi thog ma'ang yod par rigs mod ce na /
NK076(mu)001:1735: ma yin te chos nyid 'khrul ldog la mi snang
NK076(mu)001:1736: ba'i phyir sangs rgyas kyi gtsug tor bzhin no ces
NK076(mu)001:1737: bsnyad do // brtags gzhi mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:1739: rim gsum mya ngan 'das pa'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK076(mu)001:1740: nges tshig rnam grangs gang la snang //
NK076(mu)001:1741: mtshon dpe ma grub tshul don bstan //
NK076(mu)001:1742: zhes pa'i don gyis drug tu gnas pa las /
NK076(mu)001:1743: dang po ngo bo ni gzungs 'dzin dang bral ba'i ye shes kun tu snang ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:1745: ngo bo med bzhin kun snang ste //
NK076(mu)001:1746: gcig dang du ma las grol ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:1748: de la ldan pa'i mtshan nyid ni mtha' thams cad dang bral ba ste /
NK076(mu)001:1750: mtshan nyid mtha' rnams kun bral ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:1753: skye 'jigs gi chos dang bral ba te /
NK076(mu)001:1755: skye 'jigs chos rnams bral gyur pa /
NK076(mu)001:1756: mya ngan 'das pa de brjod do //
NK076(mu)001:1759: dang po phyogs ga cig pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:1761: gnyis pa mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa ni //
NK076(mu)001:1762: shes rab chen po'i 'khor ba'i mtha' la mi gnas shing //
NK076(mu)001:1763: snying rje chen pos mya ngan 'das kyi mtha' la'ang mi gnas pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1765: rnam grangs gnyis su brjod pa ste //
NK076(mu)001:1766: theg pa mtho dman bye brag gis //
NK076(mu)001:1767: phyogs pa dang mi gnas pa'i /
NK076(mu)001:1770: yul gang la snang ba ni /
NK076(mu)001:1771: dbyings ye shes gnyis med kyi rtogs pa chos kyi
NK076(mu)001:1772: sku de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la snang rjes mthun
NK076(mu)001:1773: tsam zag med kyi lam pa la'ang yod zhing /
NK076(mu)001:1774: longs sku ni dag pa'i sa la snang la /
NK076(mu)001:1775: sprul sku ni gdul bya 'khrul pa la snang ba ste /
NK076(mu)001:1777: mya ngan 'das pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK076(mu)001:1778: de bzhin gshegs la snang ba dang //
NK076(mu)001:1779: de yi sprul pa rgya cher nyid //
NK076(mu)001:1783: 'khor ba'i chu bo las brgal ba gru ltar bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:1784: gzung 'dzin gyi 'ching ba dang bral ba btson dong nas thar ba lta bu'o //
NK076(mu)001:1786: chu bo brgal ba'i gru bzhin du //
NK076(mu)001:1787: 'khor ba'i chu bo rnam par brgal //
NK076(mu)001:1788: btson rar thar pa ji bzhin du //
NK076(mu)001:1789: 'ching ba'i mdud pa las grol ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:1791: grub ma grub kyi brtag pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:1794: de la ldan pa'i khyad par gyi chos myang 'das nyid kyang yang dag tu ma grub ste /
NK076(mu)001:1796: gzhi po'i sems nyid ma grub pas //
NK076(mu)001:1797: yul snang chos kun ma nges te //
NK076(mu)001:1798: cir yang gzung du med pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1800: de dag kyang rang mtshan la rten gzhir mi byed kyi /
NK076(mu)001:1801: zhen pa sgros btags kyi blo brtag /gzhir bzhag pa yin no //
NK076(mu)001:1802: shes bya gzhi'i don bshad zin to /
NK076(mu)001:1803: gnyis pa lam rgyas par bstan pa la /
NK076(mu)001:1804: brjod bya ngo bo nyid kyi rgyud dang /
NK076(mu)001:1805: brjod byed kyi rkyen yi ge'i rgyud gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:1807: rang bzhin sngon du byed rgyu ni /
NK076(mu)001:1808: ngo bo dang ni rkyen nyid de ces so //
NK076(mu)001:1809: rkyen gyi rgyu la'ang thabs kyi de nyid rgya cher ston pa rnal 'byor pha'i rgyud dang /
NK076(mu)001:1810: shes rab kyi de nyid zab par ston pa rnal 'byor ma'i rgyud dang /
NK076(mu)001:1811: thabs shes rab zab pa dang rgya che ba gnyis
NK076(mu)001:1812: su med par ston pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud
NK076(mu)001:1815: thabs dang shes rab ma ning brgyud //
NK076(mu)001:1816: bstan pa'ang ni rkyen du gsungs //
NK076(mu)001:1818: 'dir ni phyi ma gnyis su med pa'i rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste bzhi las /
NK076(mu)001:1819: khyad par du rda rje sems dpa'i rgyud sgyu d+r+wa ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:1820: de nyid la rgyud gsang sde bcu gsum du gnas pa la'ang rtsa bshad gnyis su 'dus ste /
NK076(mu)001:1821: de gnyis khyad par gyi mtshan nyid la gzhan lugs dgag pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:1825: brjod bya brjod dar rnying mi gsal ba mun pa ltar gnas pa ni rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK076(mu)001:1826: gsal byed snang ba ltar ston pa ni bshad pa'i rgyud ces zer ba ni mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:1827: de ltar na rtsa bshad gnyis phan tshun 'gal ba nyid du 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:1828: snang mun dang mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1829: yang kha nya ri ba na re /
NK076(mu)001:1830: ston pa'i bdag nyid kyis gsungs pa rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK076(mu)001:1831: 'chad pa'i skyes bu'i gsungs pa bshad pa'i rgyud ces zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:1832: spar khab kyi dgongs pa snying po'i rgyud nyid 'chad
NK076(mu)001:1833: pa'i skyes bus gsungs par 'dod pa'i phyir zer ro
NK076(mu)001:1834: // yang kha klan ka tshol ba gcig na re
NK076(mu)001:1835: gzhung gzhan la ma ltos par gzhan bskyed par nus
NK076(mu)001:1836: pa rtsa rgyud nang gi rgyud kyi don 'grel bar
NK076(mu)001:1837: byed pa bshad rgyud zer ba'ang mi 'thad de dang
NK076(mu)001:1838: po ltar na rim gyis 'jug pa dag lam stegs
NK076(mu)001:1839: kyi theg pa gzhan la mi ltos par thal /
NK076(mu)001:1840: 'di nyid kyis bskyed nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1841: 'dod par ni rung ba ma yin te //
NK076(mu)001:1842: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK076(mu)001:1843: gsang ba'i snying po'i 'gro ba'i lam //
NK076(mu)001:1845: gnyis pa ltar na'ang snying po'i rgyud bshad rgyud du thal te /
NK076(mu)001:1847: bsgrub pa'i zhag dang tshes grangs ni //
NK076(mu)001:1848: rgyud las smos pa nyid du bshad //
NK076(mu)001:1849: ces pa'i don le'u dgu pa nyid kyi nang tshogs kyis gsal bar byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1850: rang lugs ni thog mar 'byung zhing bshad gzhir gyur
NK076(mu)001:1851: pa na rtsa rgyud rjes la 'byung zhing 'chad byed
NK076(mu)001:1852: du gyur pa'i rgyud kyi dngos po gzhan du grub
NK076(mu)001:1853: pa ni bshad pa'i rgyud ces bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:1855: thog mar bstan pa rtsa ba la //
NK076(mu)001:1856: phyis nas bstan pa bshad pa'i rgyud ces so //
NK076(mu)001:1857: rgyud kyi don gsal zhing lag tu len par byed
NK076(mu)001:1858: pa ni sgrub thabs phra mo bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK076(mu)001:1859: kyi te / 'dir dbye don rgyas par ma spros kyi gnas skabs gzhan du shes par zad do //
NK076(mu)001:1860: lam ngo bo nyid kyi rgyud la gsum /
NK076(mu)001:1862: khyad par gyi don so so nas gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1865: khyad par 'di nyid kyi lam mo //
NK076(mu)001:1866: de gnyis kyi sa mtshams ni 'jog lug tha dad do //
NK076(mu)001:1867: zab pa khyad pa la mi zab pa thun mong zhes pa'am /
NK076(mu)001:1868: don gcig la 'jug pa khyad par la /
NK076(mu)001:1869: du ma la 'jug pa thun mong zhes gzhan dag 'dod la /
NK076(mu)001:1870: bdag gi bla ma ni mdo sngags gnyis ka'i 'jug yul du gyur pas thun mong gi lam te /
NK076(mu)001:1871: dge ba'i bshes gnyen du ma la gser bum pa gang yod pa lta bu yin no //
NK076(mu)001:1872: ma ha ba nyid kyi 'jug yul du gyur pa ni khyad par gyi lam ste /
NK076(mu)001:1873: 'khor gyi gtso bo gcig la gser bum pa gang yod pa lta bu'o gsungs so //
NK076(mu)001:1874: so so nas gtan la dbab pa'i dang po thun mong gi lam la bzhi /
NK076(mu)001:1879: dang po ni gzhan sel lam mi lhung pa brtag
NK076(mu)001:1880: cing don gnyer mthar thug gi 'bras bu 'di nyid
NK076(mu)001:1881: shes par bya ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1883: snying po sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK076(mu)001:1884: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK076(mu)001:1887: thun mong gi sems lnga skyes pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1888: dbye ba la dngos kyi thun mong gi lam nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhin dang /
NK076(mu)001:1889: ltos pa'i thun mong gi lam phyi rgyud sde gsum ste /
NK076(mu)001:1891: rgya mtsho rigs kyi dbye ba lam /
NK076(mu)001:1894: ma nges phyi ma'i dbye ba ste /
NK076(mu)001:1895: bzhi ni nges 'byung thun mong lam //
NK076(mu)001:1896: de bzhin rigs gcig thun mong min //
NK076(mu)001:1897: de nyid phyi nang char snang ba //
NK076(mu)001:1898: phyi rol ltos pa'i thun mong lam //
NK076(mu)001:1901: de ltar na'ang thun mong gi lam 'di nyid khyad par du 'agro'am mi 'gro /
NK076(mu)001:1902: dang po ltar na thun mongs dang khyad par khyad med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:1903: gnyis pa ltar na thun mong gi dam bca' nyams so ce na /
NK076(mu)001:1906: khyad med du thal zhe na brtag par bya ste //
NK076(mu)001:1907: dngos kyi lam yin pa'i phyir zer ram //
NK076(mu)001:1908: brgyud pa'i lam stegs yin pa'i phyir zer //
NK076(mu)001:1909: dang po rtag ma grub la /
NK076(mu)001:1910: gnyis pa ltar na lam stegs tsam nyid kyis dngos
NK076(mu)001:1911: khams dang khyad med du 'gyur ba la ma khyab
NK076(mu)001:1912: pa ces bya'o // khyad par 'di nyid lam la'ang bzhi /
NK076(mu)001:1915: dbye ba gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1917: gzhi shes shing 'bras bu myur du thob par byed pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:1919: spar khabs shes thob rtags mi nges tshig gnyis /
NK076(mu)001:1920: rgyu rkyen thabs 'brel dgos rdzogs phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1922: yang lan grangs bzhin du bdun nyid las /
NK076(mu)001:1923: ming dang rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK076(mu)001:1925: ngo bo ni khyad par gyi sems lnga skyes pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1928: gang gis skye ba'i rgyu rkyen /
NK076(mu)001:1930: skyes pa rang gi ngo bo ye shes lnga'o //
NK076(mu)001:1932: spyan 'grel skyes pa rkyen gyis skye tshul dang //
NK076(mu)001:1933: skyes pa'i ngo bo sems rig pa //
NK076(mu)001:1936: gzhi nas so sor skye ba /
NK076(mu)001:1938: 'bras bu nas sems skye ba ste /
NK076(mu)001:1940: spyan 'grel gzhi dang skabs nas skye 'gyur ba //
NK076(mu)001:1942: dang por dang po gzhi rigs ni so skyes gsum ste /
NK076(mu)001:1949: dang po ni rang gi blo dang 'tshams pa'i theg
NK076(mu)001:1950: pa la 'jug pa'i yid bzhin du mi nur ba
NK076(mu)001:1952: 'dus pa che chung rigs pa'i blo yod phyir //
NK076(mu)001:1953: theg pa'i rims pa'ang de bzhin te //
NK076(mu)001:1954: bskul dbang che chung gnyis kyis so //
NK076(mu)001:1955: rnam pa gnyis kyi khyad par las //
NK076(mu)001:1956: 'jug pa'i yul dang de kho na //
NK076(mu)001:1958: dbyer na rigs can gsum nyan rang bo de'i mo //
NK076(mu)001:1959: gnyis pa rig chad pa la'ang gnyis las /
NK076(mu)001:1961: re zhig thar thob kyi bskal ba dang mi ldan pa te /
NK076(mu)001:1963: chos kyi dbyings kyis kun la khyab gyur kyang //
NK076(mu)001:1964: rang rig rtogs pa'i skal dang mi ldan na //
NK076(mu)001:1965: ji ltar dmus long mdun du mdog bstan bzhin //
NK076(mu)001:1966: 'di ni skal med rigs chad sa pa yin //
NK076(mu)001:1968: dbye na rang bzhin gyi rigs chad pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:1969: gnas skabs rkyen gyi rigs chad pa gnyis so //
NK076(mu)001:1970: de gnyis la gzhan gyi brtags pa'i mtha' dgag pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:1971: rang gzhung skyon med du nges pa brjod pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1973: gzhan gyis btags pa'i sbyor ba ni //
NK076(mu)001:1975: kha slas rdo rje 'od gcig na re /
NK076(mu)001:1976: gang zag gi shes rgyud chos can //
NK076(mu)001:1977: rang bzhin gyis rigs chad pa yod de /
NK076(mu)001:1978: rang rig rtogs pa'i skal pa dang mi ldan pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1979: dmus long gi kha dog bzhin zhes pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:1980: lung las kyang ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:1981: ma rig pa gnyis kyis shes rab kyis spyan ldongs
NK076(mu)001:1982: pa'i dpe ji ltar bar ye nas log pas rang
NK076(mu)001:1985: ces pa grub ces zer te /
NK076(mu)001:1987: ma nges pa'i rtag dgag pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:1988: mi mtshungs pa'i rjes 'gro dgag pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:1990: ci gang zag kyi rgyud la byang chub kyi snying
NK076(mu)001:1991: po'i sa bon tsam yang med pa'i phyir skal ba
NK076(mu)001:1993: mthun rkyen gyis cig char du rigs ma sad pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:1994: dang po ltar na rang bzhin gyi gzhi nyid kyang bzang can du thal /
NK076(mu)001:1995: byang chub kyi snying po yod na kyi mthar thug pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:1999: brgyan chos kyi dbyings ni dbyer med phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2000: rigs ni tha dad rung ma yin /
NK076(mu)001:2002: rigs yod phyir na lus can kun //
NK076(mu)001:2003: rtag tu bde gshegs snying po can //
NK076(mu)001:2005: yang 'di nyid kyi rim drug las //
NK076(mu)001:2006: chos rnams ma lus thams cad la //
NK076(mu)001:2007: byang chub snying por yod par blta //
NK076(mu)001:2008: rang bzhin ye nas 'od gsal ba //
NK076(mu)001:2009: kun bzang rdo rje sems dpa' gsungs //
NK076(mu)001:2011: lo /gnyis pa ltar na khyab pa med de /
NK076(mu)001:2012: re shig dad mos ma skyes kyang kun gzhi la
NK076(mu)001:2013: dkar po'i sa bon bzhag te nam zhig rigs sad
NK076(mu)001:2016: mdo sde phal po che las /
NK076(mu)001:2017: sems can la la zhig las kyi sgrib pas de bzhin gshegs pa la ma dad na'ang /
NK076(mu)001:2018: de dag gis mthong zhing thos pa'i dge ba'i rtsa
NK076(mu)001:2019: ba de ni yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK076(mu)001:2020: bar du don yod par 'gyur ro zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:2021: gnyis pa ni dmus long du 'gyur ba nyid sdig
NK076(mu)001:2022: to'i myong 'bras yin pa'i rang bzhin gyi dper na
NK076(mu)001:2023: mi mtshungs te / gal te de ltar na mig
NK076(mu)001:2024: mkhan gyis phye bas thams cad don med par 'gyur
NK076(mu)001:2025: mi mtshungs te / ro // gzhan yang snying po kye kye /
NK076(mu)001:2026: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK076(mu)001:2027: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK076(mu)001:2029: kun kyang smin zin bgrod pa med //
NK076(mu)001:2030: de nyid lam gyi ngo bo ste //
NK076(mu)001:2031: ces pa la sogs pa'i bka' zab mo la skur 'debs ches btab ste /
NK076(mu)001:2032: rigs lam ngan pa de nyid nges par dor bar
NK076(mu)001:2033: byos shig /rang lugs ni gnas skabs kun tu btags
NK076(mu)001:2034: pa'i rkyen gyis bag chags 'thug pos rang bzhin nyid
NK076(mu)001:2035: bsgribs te / yun ring du mthong dka' bar gyur pa'am /
NK076(mu)001:2036: log pa'i grub mthas kha khrid de yang dag pa'i gegs su gyur pa nyid la bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:2038: snying po bdag tu rmongs pa'i rtogs pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:2039: brtags pa mngon par zhen pa'i //
NK076(mu)001:2040: yang dag lam dang bral ba dag /ces pa mngon zhing /
NK076(mu)001:2041: sngar gyi lung yang rkyen gyis chad pa la dgongs pa kho na'o //
NK076(mu)001:2042: gsum pa rigs ma nges pa la'ang gnyis las /
NK076(mu)001:2043: go don ni rkyen gyi dbang gis sems gang du'ang skyer rung ste /
NK076(mu)001:2045: spyan 'grel ma nges phyi yi dbye ba las //
NK076(mu)001:2046: rigs kyi khyad par mngon par snang //
NK076(mu)001:2049: theg pa mtha' dag la zhugs shing nges shes kyi
NK076(mu)001:2050: mthar phyin mi phyin pa'i ma nges pa ngan pa
NK076(mu)001:2051: dang / chos gang bstan thogs med du go ba'i ma nges pa bzang po gnyis las /
NK076(mu)001:2052: 'dir ni sngar bstan pa ltar 'bras bu'i theg pa chen por rigs nges pa'i dbang rnon nam /
NK076(mu)001:2053: ma nges pa'i bzang po de las skye bar bzhed do //
NK076(mu)001:2054: lam nas sems skye ba ni lam rigs bzhi nas te /
NK076(mu)001:2060: lam chung la la thun mong lam rnams nas //
NK076(mu)001:2063: 'bras bu nas sems skye ba la'ang gnyis las /
NK076(mu)001:2064: go don ni thun mong gi 'bras kun tu 'od
NK076(mu)001:2065: kyi sa mngon du byas kyang gsang sngags kyi nges
NK076(mu)001:2067: rgyal ba drug pas dbang bskur chos bshad pas tha ma'i dbugs phyin te mthar thug sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2069: lam chung thun mongs pa mthar byas pa'i tshe //
NK076(mu)001:2070: yang dag sku gsung thugs bco lnga //
NK076(mu)001:2071: byin rlabs 'tshams par mos snang bas //
NK076(mu)001:2076: kha gcig na re ci rgyu'i theg pa dbu ma'i
NK076(mu)001:2077: 'bras bu nas sems skye ba ni rigs pa ma
NK076(mu)001:2078: yin te / skye ba'i rgyu ye shes rgyun chad pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2079: nam mkha'i me tog bzhin te /
NK076(mu)001:2080: 'dod na rgyu med kyi 'bras bus srid par thal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:2081: gtan tshigs lung gis grub pa nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:2082: ce na lan du bdag gi bla rog ma ni
NK076(mu)001:2083: rtog bcas kyi ye shes med pa la dgongs pa
NK076(mu)001:2084: yin gyi rtog med kyi ye shes yod pa nyid
NK076(mu)001:2086: bdag ni rgyu'i theg pa dag rang gi 'bras bu la gya nom pa'i zhen pa dgag cing /
NK076(mu)001:2087: gsang sngags su drangs pa dgongs pa yin gyi /
NK076(mu)001:2088: nges don du ye shes rgyun chad las skye bar mi rung sems te dpyad par bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:2089: gnyis pa gang gis skye ba'i rgyu rkyen ni /
NK076(mu)001:2090: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi 'brel pa bzhi dang ldan pas so //
NK076(mu)001:2092: sems nyid bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po dang ye
NK076(mu)001:2093: nas mtshungs par ldan pa ni mtshungs bya'i rgyu ste
NK076(mu)001:2094: / lam rim snying po'i rang bzhin mtshungs pa dang ces so //
NK076(mu)001:2095: 'og ma'i skyon brjod pas skyo zhing ma ha'i yon
NK076(mu)001:2096: thos pas brod de 'dun rtsol skye ba ni lhan
NK076(mu)001:2098: lam rim bshes gnyen mgon las lung gnyis thos //
NK076(mu)001:2101: rgyu'i rkyen ni gong gi rgyu gnyis po des ma har 'jug pa'i grogs su gyur pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2102: rdo rje slob dpon ni rtog pa go 'byed pa bdag po'i rkyen no //
NK076(mu)001:2103: ma ha'i don bstan pa ni dmigs pa'i rkyen no //
NK076(mu)001:2104: shes pa skad cig snga ma la long brtags nas
NK076(mu)001:2105: rdzas kyi shes pa phyi ma skye ba ni de
NK076(mu)001:2107: lam rim de dag gsang sogs dmigs pa te /
NK076(mu)001:2108: skad cig 'phel ba de ma thag /ces so //
NK076(mu)001:2109: 'brel ba bzhi ni rdo rje slob dpon dang chos nyid ngo bo nyid du 'brel /
NK076(mu)001:2110: des brtan pa'i man ngag dang snod dang bcud du
NK076(mu)001:2111: 'brel bstan bya chos nyid ma h+aa dang shes bya
NK076(mu)001:2113: ston pa kun tu bzang po dang las dang thugs rje 'brel te /
NK076(mu)001:2114: bshes gnyen rnams dang ngo bos 'brel //
NK076(mu)001:2115: de ldan bya byed snod bcud du //
NK076(mu)001:2116: chen po lung dang lung dang 'brel ba dang //
NK076(mu)001:2117: mgon dang bya byed thugs rje 'brel //
NK076(mu)001:2119: de ltar na'ang so so'i skye bo la rgyu rkyen
NK076(mu)001:2120: drug dang ldan dgos na rang rgyal ni sems skyer
NK076(mu)001:2121: mi btub ste / bla ma med pas bdag rkyen
NK076(mu)001:2122: dang lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ma tshang ba'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:2123: mi btub ste / ro zhe na / bden mod
NK076(mu)001:2124: kyi grogs por bstan nas don byed par gsungs te
NK076(mu)001:2125: mi btub ste / ro zhe na / / ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:2126: rnam snang mngon byang rang rgyal rnams la grogs po'i gzugs //
NK076(mu)001:2127: bstan nas theg chen dmigs pa 'dzud //
NK076(mu)001:2129: gsum pa skye tshul ni 'og nas 'chad la /
NK076(mu)001:2130: bzhi pa skyes pa rang gi ngo bo ni sems lnga ste /
NK076(mu)001:2132: khog gzhung 'jug ldang la sogs byang sems lnga //
NK076(mu)001:2133: nges par skye ba ngo bor 'dod //
NK076(mu)001:2140: rgyas pa 'jug dang ldang dang gnas pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:2141: smon pa byang chub sems nyid de //
NK076(mu)001:2142: g.yo dang bskyed dang ldang dang gnas //
NK076(mu)001:2144: thig le'i mgo g.yo ba'i tshe bde ba ldang bas g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems so //
NK076(mu)001:2145: bde ba snga ma 'jigs cing phyi ma la 'jug pas byang chub kyi sems so //
NK076(mu)001:2146: dga' ba skyes la ma 'gags pa la gnas pas gnas pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK076(mu)001:2147: phyi ma la dmigs shing smon pas smon pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK076(mu)001:2148: byang sems dbab pa'i thabs kyis phab nas rdo rje'i lam nas yum gyi mkhar 'gro ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:2149: bzlog pa'i thabs kyis zlog nas slar 'ong ba ni 'gro 'ong byang chub kyi sems so //
NK076(mu)001:2151: spyi nas 'dir skye tshul du brtsi ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:2152: 'di nyid kyi lam gong 'og la rtsi ba'o dang
NK076(mu)001:2153: po ni rang bzhin gyi mun pa can so so'i
NK076(mu)001:2154: skye bo dang ched du byas pa'i mun pa mu
NK076(mu)001:2155: stegs la sogs pa 'og ma nas dag nas ma
NK076(mu)001:2156: har / sems g.yo ba ni g.yo ba byang chub kyi sems /
NK076(mu)001:2157: gong ma'i yon tan la smon pas smon pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK076(mu)001:2158: don la 'jug pa ni 'jug pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK076(mu)001:2159: zhugs shing gnas pas gnas pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK076(mu)001:2160: gnas pas thob cing mthar phyin pas mthar phyin pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK076(mu)001:2161: gnyis pa 'di nyid la sbyar ba la gsum las /
NK076(mu)001:2164: spyan 'grel dang po g.yo ldang byang chub sems //
NK076(mu)001:2165: gnyis pa smon pa gsum 'jug sems //
NK076(mu)001:2166: gnas pa mthar phyin bzhi lnga pa //
NK076(mu)001:2168: lta ba rtogs nas ting nge 'dzin la ldang ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:2170: phyag rgya gcig pa la 'jug spros tshogs la gnas /
NK076(mu)001:2171: rig 'dzin bzhi la mthar phyin pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2172: zag bcas kho na la sbyar /
NK076(mu)001:2173: spyan gsum mthong nas bzhi dang ldan /
NK076(mu)001:2174: lnga pa lnga pa nyid du sbyor /
NK076(mu)001:2176: lta ba g.yo smon 'jug pa gsum mo //
NK076(mu)001:2177: de ting sgyu ma rgya gcig spros pa dag la gnas pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2178: tshogs bsgrub la sems mthar phyin pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2179: tha ma lam re re'ang sems lnga ldan gyi tshul ni /
NK076(mu)001:2180: yang na rnal 'byor gcig lnga ldan zhes pas lam rim la'ang sems lngar char sbyar ro //
NK076(mu)001:2181: gsum pa skye tshul gnyis dbye ba dang sgrub byed do //
NK076(mu)001:2182: dang po ni dbang po gnyis la ltos te rims 'jug tu skye ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:2183: gcig char du 'jug pas skye ba gnyis so //
NK076(mu)001:2184: de la yang rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon pa rims dang cig char gnyis /
NK076(mu)001:2185: sbyangs pa'i dbang rnon rims cig char gnyis te bzhi'i tshul gyi 'jug pa nyid de /
NK076(mu)001:2187: de yang dbang bzhin sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur pas nye rings phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2188: rims dang gcig char bzhi cha yin /
NK076(mu)001:2189: bye bas rnal 'byor chen por 'jug /ces so //
NK076(mu)001:2190: de la sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur pas nye rings phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2191: rim dang gcig char bzhi cha yin /
NK076(mu)001:2192: phye bas rnal 'byor chen por 'jug /ces so //
NK076(mu)001:2193: de la sbyangs pa'i dbang rnon rim kyis pa ni
NK076(mu)001:2194: tshe sngon phan chad ni lam stegs kyi theg pa
NK076(mu)001:2195: gzhan la dus ring por blo sbyongs shing 'di'i tshe
NK076(mu)001:2196: stod la'ang theg pa thun mongs la gnas pa zhig
NK076(mu)001:2199: snga ma'ang tan+t+ra'i gzhung nyid las /
NK076(mu)001:2200: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa'ang /
NK076(mu)001:2201: gsang ba'i snying por grol ba'i lam //
NK076(mu)001:2202: lam stegs sngon du rdzogs par sbyor //
NK076(mu)001:2204: sbyangs pa'i dbang rnon cig char ba ni /
NK076(mu)001:2205: snga ma phan chad sbyangs shing 'di'i tshe stod nyid nas ma har 'jug pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:2207: kha gcig dus mtha'i cig char ba //
NK076(mu)001:2208: thun mong de nyid sbyangs pa'i mthar //
NK076(mu)001:2209: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i don gzhung la'ang //
NK076(mu)001:2210: rim gyis sbyangs la cig char bgrod //
NK076(mu)001:2212: rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon rim kyis pa ni tshe
NK076(mu)001:2213: snga phan chad gzhan lam sbyangs zhing 'di'i tshe stod
NK076(mu)001:2214: la lam stegs tsam du re zhig zhugs pa'i mthar
NK076(mu)001:2217: la la dbang po rno ba dag /theg pa theg chen gnyis 'jug ste //
NK076(mu)001:2218: phye bas rgyu 'bras chen po rnams //
NK076(mu)001:2221: rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon cig char ba ni 'di'i
NK076(mu)001:2222: yang tshe stod nyid nas ma har 'jug pa ste
NK076(mu)001:2224: ma nges pa nas 'brel rgyu rkyen //
NK076(mu)001:2225: ldan pa rnal 'byor mchog sbyor ba //
NK076(mu)001:2226: mun pa'i zer tshul rtsa me ltar //
NK076(mu)001:2228: de sgrub pa la gnyis las /
NK076(mu)001:2229: sbyangs pa'i dbang rnon ni rgyu 'bras gnyis ka'i lung rigs du mas grub cing /
NK076(mu)001:2230: dngos po stobs zhugs kyi tshad mas kyang shes par nus so //
NK076(mu)001:2231: rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po sgrub pa la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:2232: med na skyon du 'gyur bas yod par bsgrub pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:2233: yod par sgrub pa'i rigs pa dngos so dang po la'ang bzhi las /
NK076(mu)001:2234: dang po ni rang bzhin gyis dbang rnon ma grub
NK076(mu)001:2235: na 'jig rten phal pa'i sems brgyad kyang skye bar
NK076(mu)001:2236: mi rigs te / sems brgyad skye ba de sbyangs pa las skye'am rang bzhin gyis skyes drangs /
NK076(mu)001:2237: sbyangs pa las skyes pa'o ce na gang la sbyangs /
NK076(mu)001:2238: snga ma la sbyangs so zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:2239: 'jig rten phal pa'i sems brgyad las snga ma'i lam ste sde snod nas bshad pa med do //
NK076(mu)001:2240: rang bzhin gyis skyes na rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon med par 'dod pa nyid nyams so //
NK076(mu)001:2241: yang gnyis pa rang bzhin gyi rnon po med pa
NK076(mu)001:2242: sbyangs pa kho na yin na sbyangs pa mnyam po
NK076(mu)001:2243: la rno rtul mi rung zhing /
NK076(mu)001:2244: 'dod na mngon sum gyis gsal lo //
NK076(mu)001:2245: de nyid snga ma la sbyangs sam ci cha zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:2246: ma sbyangs sam ci cha ste ci cha yod kyi rigs pa mi btub bo //
NK076(mu)001:2247: yang gsum pa theg pa la che chung song bar mi rigs te /
NK076(mu)001:2248: rgyu mnyam po las sbyangs pa mnyam po la rno rtul mi 'byung la /
NK076(mu)001:2249: de med na theg pa la che chung mi srid de /
NK076(mu)001:2250: theg pa che chung ni blo khyad che chung kyis skye ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:2251: bzhi pa rang bzhin gyis grub par gsungs pa'i lung thams cad dang yang 'gal lo //
NK076(mu)001:2252: gnyis pa yod par sgrub dngos la lung man ngag rig pa gsum las /
NK076(mu)001:2255: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhing khams na gnas pa'i sems
NK076(mu)001:2256: chen po 'di dag ni sems kyi rang bzhin sna
NK076(mu)001:2257: tshogs pa'i phyir shin tu zab pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:2265: gsang sngags kyi gtam rim kyis sam cig char du thob nas ces pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:2266: gzhan yang kun byed lha ma'i sems dbang po'i mi mthun pas /
NK076(mu)001:2267: la la dbang po ye nas gcig chod yod /
NK076(mu)001:2268: la las sbyangs pa'i dbang po 'phro can yod //
NK076(mu)001:2273: kha gcig thog ma nas te rigs /
NK076(mu)001:2274: kha gcig sbyangs las gyur pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2276: yang lam rim ma sbyangs sgrub pa gsum phyir kyi /
NK076(mu)001:2277: mtho brtan myur rno rgya che yang //
NK076(mu)001:2278: zab mo rgyu yi gang zag de //
NK076(mu)001:2280: gsum pa rigs pa ni mkhas pa kha gcig na re /
NK076(mu)001:2281: 'dar zhag sems can rnams kyi sems rgyud chos can /
NK076(mu)001:2282: rang bzhin gyis rno rtul du grub te /
NK076(mu)001:2283: kun gzhi la bag chags tha spyir bag chags la mod pa che ba'i rang 'dod pa /
NK076(mu)001:2284: gzhung bsags pa gtso che bar 'dod pa'i /
NK076(mu)001:2285: gzhung gnyis ka ltar 'dod pa'i gzhung dang gsum las /
NK076(mu)001:2286: dang po ni rgyu yang dag bden pa na re /
NK076(mu)001:2287: yod par min par bsags pa zhig yin na 'o
NK076(mu)001:2288: cag gis zag med mthong lam gyi bag chags ma
NK076(mu)001:2289: bzhag pas lam sbyangs kyang bden pa mi mthong bar
NK076(mu)001:2290: thal / sngar la bsags pa'i phyir ma bsags kyang
NK076(mu)001:2291: mthong na ci sto zhe na bsags pa gtso bo'i
NK076(mu)001:2293: ru mchog gi sde pa na re /
NK076(mu)001:2294: bsags pa min par rang bzhin gyis yod na sbyin
NK076(mu)001:2295: pa ma btang ba'i phyug po'i rgyud ma sbyangs pa'i
NK076(mu)001:2296: rgyud dag 'byung bar rigs te med pa'i phyir zer
NK076(mu)001:2297: ro // ru chos skyong ba'i sde pa na re gnyis ka ltar bden no zer lo /
NK076(mu)001:2301: rnon por rnam par 'jog pa'i bag chags de thos bsam gyi rgyu rkyen la ltos sam mi ltos /
NK076(mu)001:2302: dang po ltar na rang bzhin nyid nyams la /
NK076(mu)001:2303: gnyis pa ltar na rgyu rkyen la ma ltos pa'i bag chags rigs pa min te /
NK076(mu)001:2306: sems ni snga mas bzhag pa yi //
NK076(mu)001:2307: nus pa bag chags yin par 'dod //
NK076(mu)001:2310: bag chags yod pa gtso che bar mngon no zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:2312: bag chags dang kun gzhi gang snga bar grub pa zhig yin na drang /
NK076(mu)001:2313: kun gzhi snga na rang bzhin gyis grub pa nyams te /
NK076(mu)001:2315: bag chags snga na kun gzhi med pa'i bag chags gang du sog par byed /
NK076(mu)001:2316: dus mnyam na'ang gcig gcig gi gzhir mi rungs te /
NK076(mu)001:2317: glang ru g.yas g.yon bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:2318: yang rje nya ri bo kha gcig 'di skad du /
NK076(mu)001:2319: sems can rnams kyi shes rgyud chos can /
NK076(mu)001:2320: dbang po rno rtul du grub ste /
NK076(mu)001:2321: sems kyi rang bzhin sna tshogs pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2322: ces gsungs pa ni dri ma med pa'i rnal 'byor pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2323: de la gzhan gyi nye bar 'dogs pa'i skyon gsum ni /
NK076(mu)001:2324: gzhi bzang ngan can du thal /
NK076(mu)001:2325: sbyangs pa la ma ltos pa'i rgyud dag 'byung bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:2326: bdag rtag pa'i rdzas dgag mi spyod par thal zhes bum 'gyur du brjod do //
NK076(mu)001:2327: lan la gnyis gzhan lugs dgag pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:2329: dang po'i lan du slas rdo rje 'od kha gcig rnam par phye te smra ba ni /
NK076(mu)001:2330: gzhi la rno rtul tha dad du yod pa'i phyir zer ram /
NK076(mu)001:2331: ris med du yod pa'i phyir zer /
NK076(mu)001:2332: dang po'i rtags ma grub cing /
NK076(mu)001:2333: gnyis pa'i khyab pa ma grub ces zer ba ni mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:2334: ci rigs med de nyid khyab pa rang rgyud chos
NK076(mu)001:2335: nyid nyid rang bzhin gyis ngos nas brjod nas dam
NK076(mu)001:2336: / chos can rnams pa'i khyad par las brjod drang /
NK076(mu)001:2337: dang po ltar na rang bzhin gyi dbang po mi srid par thal /
NK076(mu)001:2338: rang bzhin la rno rtul gyi spu ris tsam yang rdul phran bzhin ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2339: gang rnon por 'jog pa nyid la ris can gyis khyab ste /
NK076(mu)001:2340: skyes bu'i mtshon cha bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:2341: gnyis pa ltar na sems can thams shes rgyud gcig tu thal /
NK076(mu)001:2342: rnam pa la khyad par gyi spu ris tsam yang
NK076(mu)001:2343: dus mtha' skad cig bzhin ma grub med pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:2344: ro // 'dod na don grub sangs rgyas pa'i tshe
NK076(mu)001:2345: 'khor bzlog pa stong par rigs te bzhad gad kyi
NK076(mu)001:2346: ro // sa'o // yang rang bzhin gyi rno de
NK076(mu)001:2347: nyid 'gal zla lta bu la ltos sam mi ltos
NK076(mu)001:2348: ro // sa'o // / dang po ltar na rang bzhin ma yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:2349: chos gzhan la ltos pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2350: gnyis pa ltar na rno ba'i khyad par gyi khyad chos mi 'grub bo //
NK076(mu)001:2351: rang lugs kyi rgyu bzhed lan rnam par phye te smra ba ni /
NK076(mu)001:2352: ci ngo bo bzang ngan can du thal zer ram /
NK076(mu)001:2353: ldog pa bzang ngan can du thal zer /
NK076(mu)001:2354: dang po rno rtul 'jug pa'i blos dpyad pas phyir ngo bo la /
NK076(mu)001:2356: gnyis pa ni 'dod pa kho na'o //
NK076(mu)001:2357: de ltar na'ang ldog pa de ngo bo nyid las phye ba zhig gam /
NK076(mu)001:2358: gzhan las phye ba can yin zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:2359: mgo bgreng de tsam du ngo bo bum tsam gyi
NK076(mu)001:2360: steng na byas mi rtag gi ldog pa tha dad
NK076(mu)001:2361: du gnas pa de'ang ngo bo nyid las phye ba
NK076(mu)001:2362: zhig gam / gzhan las phye ba zhig yin zhes dri ste /
NK076(mu)001:2363: gnyis pa ni snga rgol phyi rgol gnyis kas mi 'grub la /
NK076(mu)001:2364: dang po ltar na 'dir yang ngo bo nyid las phye zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:2365: gzhi yi ngo bo yang bzang ngan can du thal /
NK076(mu)001:2366: rno rtul dang rdzas dbyer mi phyed pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:2367: mtshungs te bum pa'i ngo bo yang cha gnyis dang bcas par thal /
NK076(mu)001:2368: byas mi rtag dang rdzas dbyer mi phyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:2369: 'di pa'o zhe na 'dir yang mtshungs so //
NK076(mu)001:2370: don dam spyod rigs kyis bzang ngan med par thal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:2371: 'dir yang kun rdzob spyod shes la cha gnyis med par gsal lo //
NK076(mu)001:2372: khyab pa ma grub ste byas mi rtag bum pa'i
NK076(mu)001:2373: ldog phyogs yin gyi bum pa'i ngo bo cha gnyis
NK076(mu)001:2375: ngas kyang rno rtul gzhi ldog phyogs yin gyi rno
NK076(mu)001:2376: rtul gzhi ngo bzang ngan can du mi 'gyur zhes
NK076(mu)001:2377: bya ste / srid mtha' bar du mgo 'dre ba yin no //
NK076(mu)001:2381: chos kyi dbyings ni dbyer med phyir //
NK076(mu)001:2382: rigs ni tha dad rung ma yin //
NK076(mu)001:2383: brten pa chos ldog phyogs kyi bye brag gis /
NK076(mu)001:2384: de'i dbye ba yongs su brjod /
NK076(mu)001:2386: gnyis pa'i yang khyab pa ma grub te rno rtul 'jug pa'i blo la rnam par bzhag pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2387: de ltar na'ang rang bzhin gyis dbang rno cig char
NK076(mu)001:2388: ba de rkyen thos bsam la rag las sam ma
NK076(mu)001:2389: las / dang po ltar na sbyangs pa dang khyad med du 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)001:2390: gnyis pa ltar na rgyud ma sbyangs rgyud dag grub pa nyid do ce na /
NK076(mu)001:2391: dang po la brtag pa bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:2392: ci 'og ma'i thos bsam la rag las pa'i phyir zer ram /
NK076(mu)001:2393: 'di nyid kyi thos bsam la rag las pa'i phyir zer /
NK076(mu)001:2394: dang po rtags khas ma blangs la /
NK076(mu)001:2395: gnyis pa ltar na de tsam gyis sbyangs pa dang
NK076(mu)001:2396: khyad med du mi 'gyur na ci to ste sha
NK076(mu)001:2398: dang po ltar na 'dir yang thos bsam la rag las so //
NK076(mu)001:2399: rang bzhin gyi rno bar ma yin par thal te /
NK076(mu)001:2400: thos bsam la rag las pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:2401: khyod kyi lcags rang bzhin gyis rno ba ma yin
NK076(mu)001:2402: par thal te rkyen mgar ba la rag las pa'i
NK076(mu)001:2403: phyir ro / dang po ltar na 'dir yang ma
NK076(mu)001:2404: sbyangs pa'i rgyud dag srid par thal ce na der
NK076(mu)001:2405: yang lcags ldos mtshon gyi don byed nus par thal
NK076(mu)001:2406: phyir ro / / gzhan yang rgyu lcags kyi rno
NK076(mu)001:2407: rdul dang 'bras bu'i bcud che chung rkyen la rag
NK076(mu)001:2408: las sam mi las kyi brtags pas mgo 'gre ba'ang
NK076(mu)001:2410: gsum pa'i las khyab pa ma grub ste brtag pa rkyen la ma ltos la /
NK076(mu)001:2411: 'dir de khas ma blangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:2412: de ltar na rang bzhin gyi chos gsum ldan nyid nyams so zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:2413: bden mod kyi 'dir rang bzhin gyi chos 'ga' zhig
NK076(mu)001:2414: la gzung ba nyid las chos gsum tshangs ba'i mtshan
NK076(mu)001:2415: nyid can ni ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:2416: nog dang lkog shal bod kyi ba glang la ma
NK076(mu)001:2417: tshang yang don byed nus shing mtshon byar gdags su
NK076(mu)001:2418: rung ba bzhin no zhes gsungs mod kyi /
NK076(mu)001:2419: bdag ni rnon po'i dbye ba rkyen la ltos mod
NK076(mu)001:2420: kyi ngo bo nyid la ma ltos par grub pa'i
NK076(mu)001:2421: phyir rang bzhin gyi chos su tshang ste /
NK076(mu)001:2422: rang bzhin chos dbyings kyang mngon du ma gyur bar
NK076(mu)001:2423: du sgrib pa spongs ba'i don byed mi nus pa
NK076(mu)001:2424: bzhin no snyam du sems so //
NK076(mu)001:2428: dang po thabs kyi nges pa'i don dang /
NK076(mu)001:2429: shes rab rnam par grol ba'i lam gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:2431: rim gsum dbu ma rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK076(mu)001:2432: grol lam thabs su rnam par bstan //
NK076(mu)001:2434: de gnyis khyad par ni 'dod pa tha dad de /
NK076(mu)001:2435: phyi ba kha gcig na re mngon du lta ba
NK076(mu)001:2436: rtogs nas phyi ltar nyams su len pa grol lam
NK076(mu)001:2437: / nang ltar nyams su len pa thabs zhes zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:2438: de ltar na'ang snying po'i le'u bcu gsum byang chub sems ni rdo rje'i tshogs //
NK076(mu)001:2439: dbang po yul dus rig pa rnams //
NK076(mu)001:2440: kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK076(mu)001:2441: thugs nyid chen po lhag pa yi //
NK076(mu)001:2442: thugs rje'i ye shes lnga brtas shing /
NK076(mu)001:2444: pa'i byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor de yang grol lam du thal /
NK076(mu)001:2445: 'dod na dngos su thabs lam du gsal lo //
NK076(mu)001:2446: kha cig na re theg pa 'og ma'i spyad na
NK076(mu)001:2447: 'ching ba'i nyon mongs lnga po dag 'dir spyad na
NK076(mu)001:2448: grol ba'i thabs su ston pa thabs lam /
NK076(mu)001:2449: thos bsam sgo gsum gyis shes pa'i rgyud grol bar
NK076(mu)001:2450: byed pa grol lam zhes zer ba'ang mi 'thad de
NK076(mu)001:2451: / gsang sngags mtha' dag kyang thabs lam du thal //
NK076(mu)001:2452: nyon mongs pa ma spangs par grol ba'i thabs su ston pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2453: 'dod na gsang sngags la grol lam gtan mi 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:2454: yang nyang 'od kha gcig na re /
NK076(mu)001:2455: dbang dang bde ba ston pa thabs lam /
NK076(mu)001:2456: shes rab gsum gyi sgo nas nyams su lon pa grol lam zhes zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:2457: mngon du phyung ba'i lam sgrol ba 'di thabs lam ma yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:2458: dbang dang bde ba mi ston pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2459: 'dod na ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar mi thabs ces pas thams lam du gsal /
NK076(mu)001:2462: phung po lnga po gzhig par bya //
NK076(mu)001:2463: bshig na 'byung ba'i bag la zha //
NK076(mu)001:2464: rnam shes med pas bsad byas na //
NK076(mu)001:2465: smin lam srog bcad tshul bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:2466: zhes pa'i lung gi grub bo //
NK076(mu)001:2468: gtso bor shes rab gsum gyi sgo nas rang gi rgyud grol bar byed pa ni grol lam /
NK076(mu)001:2469: gtso bor thabs kyi khyad par gyi sgo nas nyams su len pa ni thabs lam gsungs /
NK076(mu)001:2470: de ltar na'ang grol lam la thabs dang gdams ngag
NK076(mu)001:2471: mi dgos shing thabs lam la shes rab gsum dgos
NK076(mu)001:2473: rnam par phye ste gtso bor mi dgos pa nyid 'dod la /
NK076(mu)001:2474: thams cad khyab pa mi dgos pa'i khyab pa ma grub ces gsungs pa ni legs par dgongs so //
NK076(mu)001:2475: de nyid gtan la dbab pa'i dang po thabs lam la gnyis /
NK076(mu)001:2481: dang po thabs lam rim kyis pa ni steng sgo
NK076(mu)001:2482: 'khor lo drug la brten nas gtum mo ye shes
NK076(mu)001:2483: kyi me dang / thig le byang chub sems 'bar
NK076(mu)001:2484: 'dzag gi sbyor bas 'khor lo bzhir khyab brdal spyi
NK076(mu)001:2485: chen po'i man ngag sbyor ba mgrin dag pa'i /
NK076(mu)001:2487: bde chen thig le'i lte rang bzhin /
NK076(mu)001:2488: bde ba ye shes la rim kyis slob pa te /
NK076(mu)001:2490: 'khor lo gsum gnyis srog shing gsum //
NK076(mu)001:2491: me rlung 'gro bas nam mkha'i ba //
NK076(mu)001:2492: bzho bas steng du rnam par grags //
NK076(mu)001:2494: thabs lam cig char ba ni 'og sgo mkha' gsang gnyis la brten nas thig le drod babs kyi /
NK076(mu)001:2495: thabs nyid shes rab du sbyor ba /
NK076(mu)001:2496: shes rab nyid du thabs su sbyor ba /
NK076(mu)001:2497: thabs shes rab gnyis su med par sbyor ba'i /
NK076(mu)001:2498: man ngag gis gnyis shor gnyis mnyam kyi skad cig
NK076(mu)001:2499: gi bde stong gnyis med kyi ye shes nyams su
NK076(mu)001:2502: lkugs pa gsum gyis sems lnga rim //
NK076(mu)001:2503: skyes pas bcu drug sa thob pa /
NK076(mu)001:2504: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes myong nyid //
NK076(mu)001:2505: 'ching ba nyid kyi thar ba'i thabs //
NK076(mu)001:2508: dngos zhar la nyon mongs mi spongs ba'i he du'o //
NK076(mu)001:2509: dang po 'on tang na thabs lam des nyon mongs
NK076(mu)001:2510: pa lam du byed pa yin nam ma yin zhes
NK076(mu)001:2511: drangs / gnyis pa ltar na gsang sngags thabs kyi khyad par don med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:2512: nyon mongs pa nyid lam du ma slong ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2514: nyon mongs rang dang spyir bstan pa //
NK076(mu)001:2515: mtshan nyid ma nor don rtogs na //
NK076(mu)001:2516: rnam par byang ba'i lam du 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:2517: zhes pa nyid lam du gyur pa nyid du gsal lo //
NK076(mu)001:2518: dang po ltar byed na mtshan nyid dang ldan pa lam du byed do //
NK076(mu)001:2519: mi ldan pa zhig lam du byed //
NK076(mu)001:2520: gnyis pa ltar na grol lam la yang thabs lam du thal /
NK076(mu)001:2521: gtan tshigs ma grub na dam bca' bud cing //
NK076(mu)001:2522: 'dod na grol lam gyi nges tshig nyams so //
NK076(mu)001:2523: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa lam du byed na des grol lam mi grol /
NK076(mu)001:2524: dang po ltar na mtshams med byed pa'ang grol bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:2525: nyon mongs pa rang rgyud la nga bcas pa'i phyir 'dod par mi nus so //
NK076(mu)001:2526: gnyis pa ltar mi grol na ni lam du byed pa don med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:2527: grol thar mi 'byung ba'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:2529: lam du byed kyis mi mo mtshan nyid dang ldan par lam du byed do /
NK076(mu)001:2531: de ltar na mtshams med spyad pas kyang grol bar thal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:2533: yang dag pa'i thabs kyis zin nas grol bar thal lam /
NK076(mu)001:2534: ma zin kyang grol bar zer /
NK076(mu)001:2535: dang po ni 'dod pa nyid yin la /
NK076(mu)001:2536: gnyis pa ltar na thabs kyis zin pa mi grol
NK076(mu)001:2537: na ci sto te khyab pa med do ces gsung
NK076(mu)001:2538: mod kyi / bdag ni rang bzhin yongs su shes
NK076(mu)001:2539: pa'i shes rab kyis zin na gsal cha nyid lam
NK076(mu)001:2540: gyi grogs khyad par can du 'gyur ba'i phyir ched
NK076(mu)001:2541: mod kyi / du bstan la / des ma zin
NK076(mu)001:2542: na rang ka ma'i nyid kyis thar pa'i srog dang
NK076(mu)001:2545: chags pas khams 'grub ci shos kyis //
NK076(mu)001:2546: rang bzhin ye shes 'grub byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2548: des grol lam dang mtshungs par yang mi 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:2549: grol lam pa dag ched du mi bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:2550: gnyis pa mi spong ba'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK076(mu)001:2551: nyon mongs pa dug lnga 'di chos can /
NK076(mu)001:2552: gsang sngags kyi lugs kyis mi spong zhing lam du byed de /
NK076(mu)001:2553: gtan tshigs bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:2555: dang por spang bya rdzas ma grub te sems nyid kyi rang rtsal yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2556: smig rgyu la chu rags bya mi dgos te smig rgyur shes pas chog pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:2558: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug kyang //
NK076(mu)001:2559: byang chub chen po'i lam nas byung //
NK076(mu)001:2561: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo bo yin pa'i phyir yang mi spong te /
NK076(mu)001:2562: dngul rdo dang dngul gyi ngo bor gnas pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:2564: zhe sdang zhes bya rdo rje'i rigs /
NK076(mu)001:2565: ces pa la sogs pa bshad do //
NK076(mu)001:2566: phyogs gcig pa'i zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir yang mi spong te //
NK076(mu)001:2567: 'og ma bas nyon mongs pa spang bya phyogs gcig tu zhen pa la /
NK076(mu)001:2568: 'dir thabs kyis zin pas spyad na rnam byang gi lam du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2569: drang srong me byi ba'i lo rgyus lta bu'o //
NK076(mu)001:2571: mdo nyon mongs pa rnams ni spang bya med de
NK076(mu)001:2572: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug rnams ni ya ma
NK076(mu)001:2575: bka' zab mo la gus pa skye ba'i rgyur 'gyur ba'i phyir yang mi spong te /
NK076(mu)001:2576: thabs kyi che ba rmad du byung ba'i sgo nas
NK076(mu)001:2577: nyon mongs pa nyid ma bkag par sngon gyi rnam
NK076(mu)001:2579: sngags kyi nus pas dug sman du byed pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:2582: thabs chen gang dang ldan pa la //
NK076(mu)001:2583: nyon mongs byang chub yan lag 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:2585: gnyis pa grol lam gtan la dbab pa la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:2589: de bzhin gtso dang grogs kyis bsdu //
NK076(mu)001:2591: de gnyis kyi khyad par kyang shes 'jug gi dngos gzhir gyur pa ni gtso bo'i lam la /
NK076(mu)001:2592: grogs kyi yan lag tu gyur pa ni cha rkyen no //
NK076(mu)001:2594: thugs thig gtso dang yan lag rnam bcu'o //
NK076(mu)001:2595: ces pas rgyud kyi dngos po bdun nam bcu ste /
NK076(mu)001:2596: de yang lta ba ni 'og nas bstan to /
NK076(mu)001:2598: spyi'i spyod pa ni lus ngag yid gsum yongs su dag pa la bya zhing /
NK076(mu)001:2599: bye brag la brgyad de 'og nas bstan to //
NK076(mu)001:2601: ngo bo ni bkod pa lha'i 'khor la rdzogs par ldan pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2603: dkyil gtso bo la mtha' 'khor gyis bskor ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:2606: dang po ni rang bzhin dang ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)001:2615: tshom bu tshogs kyi dal lo //
NK076(mu)001:2616: gsum pa ni sin d+har tar shes pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2618: ngo bo ni rdo rje slob dpon la rags las pa'i nus pa khyad par can no //
NK076(mu)001:2621: ma dag pa dag par byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2622: dbye na zhi ba'i dbang bco brgyad khro bo'i dbang
NK076(mu)001:2623: sum cu rtsa drug go /dam tshig la gsum las
NK076(mu)001:2624: / ngo bo ni bsrung bya'i don khyad par can la sems dpa' sa bon dang bcas pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2626: don ji ltar bcas pa las mi 'da' zhe na
NK076(mu)001:2627: 'das na ngan song gi gnas su rgyud 'tshig pa'i
NK076(mu)001:2628: phyir ro // dbye na rgyas 'bring bsdus pa'i tshul lam /
NK076(mu)001:2629: yang na sum brgya drug cu'o //
NK076(mu)001:2631: ngo bo ni gtso bor gzhan don la dmigs pas byed bcas so //
NK076(mu)001:2632: nges tshig ni gdul bya dang 'tshams par don byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2633: dbye ba zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun gyis grub pa dang lnga'o //
NK076(mu)001:2635: ngo bo ni dmigs pa'i yul la 'jug pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2636: nges tshig ni 'bras bus mngon du byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:2638: 'jig rten gyi bde 'bras 'ga' zhing don du gnyer ba thun mong gi bsgrub pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:2639: myang 'das kyi bde 'bras yongs su don du gnyer ba mchog gi bsgrub pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2641: ro langs tsho dang pra sgrub dang //
NK076(mu)001:2642: lha chen po dang rgyal po bzhi //
NK076(mu)001:2643: gdug pa klu 'dul rgyal blon gyi //
NK076(mu)001:2644: chung ma dbang du bya ba gnyis //
NK076(mu)001:2645: yul khams lce spyang rkang mgyogs bsgrub //
NK076(mu)001:2649: rdo rje sems dang sman sgrub dang //
NK076(mu)001:2650: rigs bzhi bsgrub dang yum lnga sems //
NK076(mu)001:2651: byin dbab bsgrub pa rnam gnyis sogs //
NK076(mu)001:2654: ngo bo ni sems rtsa gcig pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2655: nges tshig ni ma yengs shing mi gtong ba'o /
NK076(mu)001:2656: dbye na rtog bcas lha'i rnal 'byor mtshan bcas kyi ting nge dang /
NK076(mu)001:2657: rtog med chos nyid de bzhin matsha na med kyi ting 'dzin gnyis so /
NK076(mu)001:2659: ngo bo ni dbul bya'i yul la dmig pa'o /
NK076(mu)001:2660: nges tshig ni gnas su stobs pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:2662: phyi'i mchod pa nye bar spyad pa lnga /
NK076(mu)001:2663: nang dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga /
NK076(mu)001:2664: gsang ba zab mo sbyor sgrol lo //
NK076(mu)001:2665: sngags dang phyag rgya gnyis las /
NK076(mu)001:2666: sngags kyi ngo bo ni yid shes bde myur du skyob pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2668: dug gsum gting nas 'byin pas so //
NK076(mu)001:2673: phyag rgya'i ngo bo ni lha'i ting nges so //
NK076(mu)001:2674: nges tshigs ni tha mal gyi rtog pa rgyas 'debs pa nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:2676: dam tshig /chos las zhi ba chos nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:2677: lam gyi gtso bo la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)001:2681: dang po ni grol lam rim gyis pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:2683: de gnyis khyad par la gnyis /
NK076(mu)001:2686: dang po ni kha cig rje me nyag na re /
NK076(mu)001:2687: sngon du lta ba rtogs nas ting nge 'dzin kha
NK076(mu)001:2688: spos nas nyams su len pa ni rim kyis pa
NK076(mu)001:2689: / ma spos par nyams su len pa ni cig char ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:2690: ces zer ba ni mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:2691: de ltar na phyag rgya lam du khyer ba'i cig
NK076(mu)001:2692: char ba 'di cig char ba ma yin par thal
NK076(mu)001:2693: / lta ba'i skabs su lha'i sku mi bsgom la /
NK076(mu)001:2694: ting nge 'dzin lha bsgom pa kha spos nas 'dug pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:2695: kha rag pa spang kha gcig na re sangs rgyas
NK076(mu)001:2696: kyi sa la dus myur du sbyor ba ni cig
NK076(mu)001:2697: char ba / bul bar sbyor ba ni rim kyis pa zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:2698: thod rgal ba 'di yang cig char bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:2699: rim gyis pa la ltos nas myur bar sbyor ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2700: 'dod na thod rgal nyams shing khyab pa'ang rang rgyud
NK076(mu)001:2701: la grub ste myur sbyor gyis khyad par du byas
NK076(mu)001:2705: sems lnga dus myur bar skye ba ni cig char ba /
NK076(mu)001:2706: dus bul ba las mi skye na rim gyis pa
NK076(mu)001:2707: zer ba'ang mi 'thad de skyon gong dang mtshungs so
NK076(mu)001:2708: // bdag gi bla ma rog ni /
NK076(mu)001:2709: dbyer med cig chod du rtogs cig chod du bsgom /
NK076(mu)001:2710: cig chod mthar phyin pa ni cig char ba /
NK076(mu)001:2713: rim gyis mthar phyin pa ni rim gyis pa te zhes bzhed pa nyid legs sam /
NK076(mu)001:2714: de ltar na'ang cig char ba la sems lnga skye'am mi skye drang /
NK076(mu)001:2715: gnyis pa ltar na sems lnga lam gyi ngo bo ma yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:2718: ngo bo shes rab rnam gsum gyis //
NK076(mu)001:2719: sems lnga skye bar bstan pa yin //
NK076(mu)001:2721: dang po ltar na'ang rim gyis skye'am cig char du skye /
NK076(mu)001:2722: dang po ltar na cig char bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:2724: rdo'i 'khor lo lnga 'bug pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:2725: gnyis pa ltar na grol lam shes rgyud lnga ldan du thal /
NK076(mu)001:2726: skad cig ma 'thud pa'i go rim med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:2727: khyab pa'ang rang rgyud la grub te go rim med
NK076(mu)001:2728: na sems lnga cig gi go sar mtshungs par bsgyur
NK076(mu)001:2732: lan la gnyis las so sor gdab pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:2733: skye ni skye mod kyi skye lugs yod de thod
NK076(mu)001:2734: rgal lam rim gyis la ltos nas shin tu myur
NK076(mu)001:2737: ut+pala gyi 'dab ma lnga mda' cig gis dus cig du phug pa'i tshe rim gyis rdol lam /
NK076(mu)001:2739: gnyis pa ltar na 'dir yang sems lnga cig char du skye'o //
NK076(mu)001:2740: 'gro la shes rgyud lnga ldan du thal lo zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:2741: ut+pala lnga yang 'gogs pa cig gnas par thal //
NK076(mu)001:2742: rim gyis rdol lo zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:2743: 'dir yang sems lnga rim gyis skye'o //
NK076(mu)001:2744: rim pas skye ba'i phyir cig char ba ma yin par thal lo /
NK076(mu)001:2747: dus cig tu phug par thal lo //
NK076(mu)001:2748: 'dod par ni gnyis kas kyang mi nus shing khyab pa'ang rang rgyud la mtshungs par grub bo //
NK076(mu)001:2749: lam gcig char ba gtan la dbab pa la drug ste /
NK076(mu)001:2754: mtshan nyid gsum dang sbyor ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:2756: srid pa bardzusa skyes su chos mthun pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2758: dbang po yang rab kyis 'bras bu thob pa'i thabs su gyur ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:2759: ngo bo ni dbyer med cig chod du bsgom pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:2760: nges tshig ni sangs rgyas kyi sar myur du sbyor ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:2762: mtshan bcas lha bsgom pa'i cig char ba ni cho
NK076(mu)001:2763: ga'i yan lag la ma ltos par skad cig dran
NK076(mu)001:2764: rdzogs su bskyed cing gsal ba ste /
NK076(mu)001:2767: snying por brjod pas 'khor lor shar //
NK076(mu)001:2769: mtshan med de bzhin nyid bsgoms pa'i cig char ba
NK076(mu)001:2770: ni sgom zhi gnas lhag mthong dbyer med yongs rdzogs
NK076(mu)001:2773: thig le chen po'i rang bzhin las //
NK076(mu)001:2774: bsgom pa rnam gsum dus cig rdzogs //
NK076(mu)001:2776: mtshan nyid gsum dang sbyar ba ni /
NK076(mu)001:2777: dbyer med cig cod du lta rtogs pa rgyu shes pa lta ba /
NK076(mu)001:2778: cig chod du goms pa rkyen 'jug pa ting nge /
NK076(mu)001:2779: cig chod du mngon du gyur pa 'bras bu'o //
NK076(mu)001:2780: rim gyis pa gtan la dbab pa la zag bcas
NK076(mu)001:2781: zag med dam lta ba dang ting nge gnyis su'ang
NK076(mu)001:2782: cig du rung mod kyi 'dir re zhig /mtshan nyid
NK076(mu)001:2784: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba /
NK076(mu)001:2785: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge /
NK076(mu)001:2786: lam du gyur pa'i 'bras bu rig 'dzin no //
NK076(mu)001:2788: snying po shes 'jug mtshan nyid 'byor ba'i gzungs /
NK076(mu)001:2789: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK076(mu)001:2790: nus mthu can du gang gyur pa //
NK076(mu)001:2791: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK076(mu)001:2795: lam rim gzhi dang gtan tshigs grub pa'i don /
NK076(mu)001:2796: ces pa'i tshul gyis chos gsum gyi sgo nas rtogs par bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:2798: de gtan la pheb pa'i gtan tshigs /
NK076(mu)001:2799: des gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha' 'o //
NK076(mu)001:2802: de shes rab gang gi yul yin pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:2803: skabs 'phros kyi dgos pa gsal ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:2805: dang po ni 'khor ba'i chos gzung 'dzin rang rgyud du zhen pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:2806: myang 'das sku dang ye shes sam lam gyi gnyen rten la zhen cing 'dzin pa dag ste /
NK076(mu)001:2808: lam rim 'khor dang 'das pa'i zhen snang brtag ces gsung pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:2809: gnyis pa de shes rab gang gis yul yin na
NK076(mu)001:2810: yid kun brtags pa'i rtog pa de nyid shes rab
NK076(mu)001:2811: dang po'i rkyen gyis bar ma bsam pa'i shes rab
NK076(mu)001:2812: du gnas 'gyur ba'i spyod yul te /
NK076(mu)001:2814: rnam bkod brjod pa'i dngos po spyod yul la //
NK076(mu)001:2815: so sor rtog pa'i gtan tshigs rkyen /
NK076(mu)001:2817: lam rim gzhan yang kun brtags shes pa bar mar 'gyur /
NK076(mu)001:2818: zhes pa'ang bar ma'i yul phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2820: gsum pa de gtan tshig kyi mtha' dag par bya zhing dogs pa gsal ba la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:2821: gzhal bya med pa'i dogs pa bsal ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:2822: gzhal gyis mi lang ba'i dogs pa bsal ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:2823: dang po ni yid gnas su 'gyur gyi bsam shes
NK076(mu)001:2824: des myang 'das la 'jal lam 'khor ba la mjal
NK076(mu)001:2826: dang por myang 'das rang gi mtshan nyid la gzhal
NK076(mu)001:2827: bar mi rung ste las dang po la mos spyod
NK076(mu)001:2828: kyi rigs shes la lkog tu 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2830: rnam bkod 'das pa spyod gyur ma gyur phyir //
NK076(mu)001:2831: gzhal ba'i yul du ji ltar rigs //
NK076(mu)001:2832: gal te 'das pa'i snang ba la //
NK076(mu)001:2833: mjal na dang po'i lkog du 'gyur zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:2834: gzhan du rang mtshan la sgro 'dogs med pa'i phyir yang gzhal mi dgos te /
NK076(mu)001:2835: dung dkar snang ba bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:2837: rim gsum mtshan nyid mtha' rnams kun bral ba /
NK076(mu)001:2839: gal te mya ngan 'das su zhen pa sgro btags kyi rnam pa la 'jal lo zhes na'ang /
NK076(mu)001:2840: yul du ma gyur par zhen du mi rung zhing /
NK076(mu)001:2841: zhen pa nyid myang 'das ma yin pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:2843: rnam bkod sems la mya ngan 'das zhen pa /
NK076(mu)001:2844: de nyid 'das par shes rab gsum te ma byas par rung ma yin /
NK076(mu)001:2846: gnyis pa 'khor ba rang gi mtshan nyid snang tsam
NK076(mu)001:2847: nyid kyang gzhal byar mi rigs te rang snang ba'i
NK076(mu)001:2849: snang ba rang gi mtshan nyid ni //
NK076(mu)001:2850: brjod bya min te rigs snang phyir //
NK076(mu)001:2851: gzhal bya min te skye ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:2852: yul min grub pa'i mtha' dang snang //
NK076(mu)001:2854: gzhan du snang tsam lam gyi dgag bya'ang ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:2855: kun rdzob bden shes bya'i gnas lugs nyid la /
NK076(mu)001:2856: rigs pas dgag par mi nus shing //
NK076(mu)001:2857: bkag na skyon du 'gyur ste lam du bsod nams kyi tshogs bkag par 'gyur ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:2858: 'bras bu ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes rgyun chad par 'gyur /
NK076(mu)001:2862: snang ba'i ngo bo gang yin pa //
NK076(mu)001:2863: dgag par nus pa ma yin te //
NK076(mu)001:2864: gzhan du sdug bsngal rgyur gyur pa'i //
NK076(mu)001:2865: bden par zhen pa bzlog bya yin //
NK076(mu)001:2867: 'dir yang kha slan cig ni 'khor ba'i rang mtshan
NK076(mu)001:2868: skad cig ma la 'dod pa ni rigs pa min
NK076(mu)001:2869: te / de nyid la 'phags pa'i shes yul las gzhan du ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2870: 'khor ba la 'khor ba'i rang mtshan mi nges shing 'phags pa nyid 'khrul bar 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:2871: gal te zhen pa sgros btags kyi shes pa la 'jal lo zhe skyon gsum ste na /
NK076(mu)001:2872: sgros dang por btags dngos med yin pa'i phyir dgag bya rjes su ma grub ste /
NK076(mu)001:2874: rnam bkod brtags pa nang la spyad do zhes /
NK076(mu)001:2875: spyad pa'i gzhi ru grub ma yin /
NK076(mu)001:2877: shes pa nyid skad cig gnyis par mi sdod par 'jal bya 'jal byed tshogs pa'ang med pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2879: log rtog spros pa'i skad cig ma //
NK076(mu)001:2881: de la brten nas brtags mi rigs //
NK076(mu)001:2883: gzhan gsum pa yang kun brtags nyid bsam shes su
NK076(mu)001:2884: gnas 'gyur ba'i phyir de nyid kyis de nyid la
NK076(mu)001:2886: ral gri de nyid kyis de nyid la mi chod pa'am /
NK076(mu)001:2887: mdzum mo nyid kyis nyid la reg tu med pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:2889: lam rim kun brtags shes pa bar mar 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:2890: spyi yul lus med grib ma bzhin //
NK076(mu)001:2891: med pas mi btub rang nyid la //
NK076(mu)001:2892: mi gtub mdzum mo bzhin dgos pas //
NK076(mu)001:2894: zhe na bden mod kyi 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i rang mtshan nyid la mi 'jal gyi /
NK076(mu)001:2895: 'khor ba snod bcud dam sku dang myang 'das ye
NK076(mu)001:2896: shes su zhen pa sgros btags kyi yul la 'jal
NK076(mu)001:2897: te / da dung kun brtags rtsa ba nas spong
NK076(mu)001:2898: ba'i gnyen po bsgom pa'i shes rab rgyud la brten
NK076(mu)001:2899: pa med pa'i phyir bsam shes de nyid kyi rjes
NK076(mu)001:2900: su kun brtags skyes rung du gnas pa'i zhen yul
NK076(mu)001:2901: la 'di ni 'adi'o snyam 'jal bar bsam te /
NK076(mu)001:2903: rnam bkod de nyid shes pa skad gcig ma //
NK076(mu)001:2904: de yang rang thad rang thad dpyad //
NK076(mu)001:2906: 'on tang na shes pa skad cig gsum gyi snga ma'i zhen snang la 'jal lam /
NK076(mu)001:2909: dang po gnyis ni mi rung ste /
NK076(mu)001:2910: 'das pa 'gags shing ma 'ongs pa yul du ma skyes pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2913: snga ma 'das shing mi dmigs la //
NK076(mu)001:2914: phyi ma ma 'ongs brtags tu med //
NK076(mu)001:2916: da lta la 'jal lo zhe na'ang //
NK076(mu)001:2917: yul dang shes pa 'tshogs nas 'jal lam /
NK076(mu)001:2919: gnyis su ltar na long bas kyang gzugs mthong bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:2920: gang du yul shes ma 'tshogs pa nyid mngon gsum
NK076(mu)001:2921: gyi gzhal bya ma yin pas khyab pas don lkogs
NK076(mu)001:2923: dang po ltar na 'gro la shes rgyud gnyis ldan du thal /
NK076(mu)001:2924: shes rgyud skad cig gis 'jal bya 'jal byed mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:2925: gang du 'gal ba tshogs pa la ngo bo'i rdzas
NK076(mu)001:2926: tha dad pas khyab te tsha reg dang grang reg
NK076(mu)001:2927: bzhin no // 'dod par ni mi nus te /
NK076(mu)001:2930: rtogs gnyis cig char 'jug pa med ces pas gsal lo //
NK076(mu)001:2931: gal te ngo bo'i rdzas tha dad par yang khas blangs du mi rung ste /
NK076(mu)001:2933: lam rim de yang yongs su brtags bzhin ni //
NK076(mu)001:2934: dbang pos yul du snang ba kun //
NK076(mu)001:2935: yul na yod pa ma yin te //
NK076(mu)001:2936: yul min grub pa'i mtha' ltar snang //
NK076(mu)001:2941: dang po kha cig kyi na re /
NK076(mu)001:2942: zhen pa ni shes pa spyi yi yul yin la /
NK076(mu)001:2943: rang mtshan skad cig ma gnas 'gyur ba so so'i
NK076(mu)001:2944: rtogs pa'i shes rab yin pas yul shes ma 'dres
NK076(mu)001:2945: pa'i phyir gzhal bya yod cing /
NK076(mu)001:2946: shes rgyud gnyis ldan gyi nyes pa yang med ces zer ba ni mi rigs te /
NK076(mu)001:2947: zhen pa'i rgyud de rang mtshan skad cig ma la ltos sam mi ltos /
NK076(mu)001:2948: gnyis pa ltar na rgyu de dngos po med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:2949: rtsom byed kyi rdzas la ma ltos pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2950: gang phra ba'i skad cig mas ma brtsam pa la
NK076(mu)001:2951: rags pa'i rgyun mi srid pas khyab te ming tshig
NK076(mu)001:2952: yi ge la ma brten par rab tu byed pa
NK076(mu)001:2954: 'dod na dus mtha'i shes pa skad cig nyid du shes ces pas gsal lo //
NK076(mu)001:2955: dang po ltar na lho nas skad cig pa skad cig la bsam shes su gnas 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2956: zhen yul rgyun chad du thal /
NK076(mu)001:2957: gang du rdzas gnas 'gyur ba la rdzas rgyun yang gnas 'gyur bas khyab te /
NK076(mu)001:2958: ma ning gi dbang po bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:2959: 'dod na zhen yul gzhal bya 'dod pa'i dam bca' bud ces bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:2960: yang kha klan ka tshol ba cig na re yid so sor rtog shes su gnas 'gyur kyang /
NK076(mu)001:2961: zhen pa kun gzhi'i rnam shes yod pa'i nyid gzhal bya yin no //
NK076(mu)001:2962: ces zer ba'ang mi rigs te /
NK076(mu)001:2963: kun gzhi'i rang ldog ni mdo las rnam par mi rtog spyod dang bral /
NK076(mu)001:2964: so so'i ris kyi ltar mi snang ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:2965: ces rtog bral 'dus ma byas yin pas kun tu
NK076(mu)001:2966: brtags pa'i dmigs rnams kyi zhen yul du rgya ma
NK076(mu)001:2967: chad cing de la sogs pa'i bag chags ni tshogs
NK076(mu)001:2969: bye brag tu dbang shes lnga ni kun tu mi 'chos rang bzhin srun /
NK076(mu)001:2970: gang yang ma yin te dbu ma ces rtog med
NK076(mu)001:2971: snang tsam las zhen yul du mi 'dzin cing mi
NK076(mu)001:2972: gnas la / nyon yid ni der 'dzin de nyid de la blta /
NK076(mu)001:2973: ma nges phyir 'gro gnyis mi dmigs ces /
NK076(mu)001:2974: kun gzhi'i la nang lha'i shes pa yin pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:2975: phyi rol gyi yul la kun tu mi rtog mod
NK076(mu)001:2976: / gal lte de nyid gzhal bya yin du'ang mi rung ste /
NK076(mu)001:2978: lam rim 'jig rten 'di na ci yod pa'i //
NK076(mu)001:2979: ming dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa rnams //
NK076(mu)001:2980: log tog so so rang spyi mtshan //
NK076(mu)001:2981: ji ltar gnas pa spyad par bya //
NK076(mu)001:2982: ces gzhal bya nyid kun brtags kyi shes pa nyid la bshad pa dang 'gal lo //
NK076(mu)001:2983: de'i phyir kun brtags kyi shes pa las log pa'i kun gzhi la sogs kyi tshogs bdun chos can /
NK076(mu)001:2984: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis gzhal bya ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:2985: dmigs pa dang rnam pa'i khyad par cir yang ma zhen pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2986: mtshan ma'i yul du ma gyur pa'i nam mkha' bzhin
NK076(mu)001:2987: zhes mi dmigs pa'i rtags kyi kheg pa nyid do
NK076(mu)001:2988: // yang so sor rtog pa'i bsam shing dpe tshogs
NK076(mu)001:2989: gzhan gyi zhen snang bzhin du yid shes nyid kyis
NK076(mu)001:2991: gnyis pa ltar na gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha' de nyid che ba'i lta bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:2992: zhen snang phyogs gcig ma khegs pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:2993: gang spros pa phyogs ga cig la mchod pa la
NK076(mu)001:2994: nyi tshe ba'i grub mtha' khyab ste ka ba dang
NK076(mu)001:2995: bum pa bzhin / 'dod na rnam pa kun ldan
NK076(mu)001:2996: gyi stong pa mthong dgos par gsungs par gsal lo
NK076(mu)001:2997: bum pa bzhin / // dang po ltar na spang gnyen 'tshogs pas spong ngam ma tshogs kyang spong /
NK076(mu)001:2998: dang po ltar na skyon snga so na gnas la /
NK076(mu)001:2999: phyi ma ltar na yid shes gnyen po med par log par thal /
NK076(mu)001:3000: gnyen po dang tshogs pa med pa'i phyir zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:3001: yang bdag gi bla ma rog ni /
NK076(mu)001:3002: yid kun brtags gnas skabs su so sor rtog pa'i
NK076(mu)001:3003: shes rab du gnas 'gyur kyang da dung bsgom pa'i
NK076(mu)001:3004: shes rab rgyud la ma brten pa'i phyir de nyid
NK076(mu)001:3005: la kun brtags skyer rung ngam /
NK076(mu)001:3006: zhen snang 'byung rung yod pa'i skad cig de nyid la rang thad rang thad du 'jal te /
NK076(mu)001:3007: ngo bo cig la ldog pa tha dad par shes
NK076(mu)001:3008: rgyud gnyis ldan du mi 'gyur ba ni chu bo
NK076(mu)001:3009: chen po'i rgyun la lag pa 'khrul ba'am /
NK076(mu)001:3010: skyes bu me long gi bzhin la blta ba bzhin ces gsungs pa la /
NK076(mu)001:3011: mi rigs te sngar gyi 'tshogs pa dang ma tshogs
NK076(mu)001:3012: pa brtag pas khegs pa la dpe skyon can la'ang
NK076(mu)001:3013: don mi gnas te lag pa dang chu rgyun nam
NK076(mu)001:3014: bzhin dang me long gnyis dngos po tha dad pa
NK076(mu)001:3016: 'jal byed gnyis kyang dngos rdzas tha dad thal /
NK076(mu)001:3017: des don mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:3018: khyad rang rgyud la grub la /
NK076(mu)001:3019: 'dod na lam rim yul min grub pa'i mtha' ltar snang zhes pas gsal lo //
NK076(mu)001:3020: rang lugs ni yid kun brtags kyi shes pa de
NK076(mu)001:3021: nyid shes rab dang po'i rkyen gyis yang dag spyod
NK076(mu)001:3022: pa'i bsam pa'i shes rab ci rigs pas skad cig
NK076(mu)001:3024: da dung mthong lam rgyud la ma brten pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:3025: de nyid la kun brtags skyer rung du yod de
NK076(mu)001:3026: / de yang shes rgyud skad cig gi steng du
NK076(mu)001:3027: mngon gyur dus gcig du 'tshog nas 'jal ba ni
NK076(mu)001:3028: / ma yin gyi / gcig mngon du gyur pa'i
NK076(mu)001:3029: gcig bag la nyal du gnas pa'i phyir snga ma
NK076(mu)001:3030: dang phyi ma da lta 'phrad pa'i tshul gyis 'jal
NK076(mu)001:3031: / ma yin gyi / te / da lta skad
NK076(mu)001:3032: cig dang po la phrad tsam /gnyis pa la mgo
NK076(mu)001:3033: / ma yin gyi / te / gnon / gsum
NK076(mu)001:3034: pa bsam shes kyi sbyor ba rdzogs par skyes pa'i
NK076(mu)001:3035: tshe snga ma kun brtags kyi sngon 'gyur ci rigs
NK076(mu)001:3036: / ma yin gyi / te / gnon / su
NK076(mu)001:3037: 'gal cing / rkyen gzhan gyis de'i rgyun brjed pa'i
NK076(mu)001:3038: skad cig phyi ma la kun brtags skye bzhin pa
NK076(mu)001:3039: ste yul shes ma 'dres pa'i phyir shes rgyud gnyis
NK076(mu)001:3040: kyi gnod med du sgro 'dogs sel bar ni /
NK076(mu)001:3042: rnam bkod zhen pa shes pa'i spyi yul yin //
NK076(mu)001:3043: skad cig gnas 'gyur de nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:3044: de bas yul shes ma 'dres phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3045: zhen snang 'jal la skyon pa med //
NK076(mu)001:3047: gzhan yang lam rim gnyen po med pas dag min zhing /
NK076(mu)001:3048: gra ma'i yul phyir nges tshig 'grub /
NK076(mu)001:3050: yang rnam bkod phyi rol med la yod ltar snang /
NK076(mu)001:3051: zhen dang lta ba gnyis pas brten //
NK076(mu)001:3052: de shes shes pa skad cig ma //
NK076(mu)001:3053: de yang rang thad rang thad spyad //
NK076(mu)001:3055: de ltar na'ang brtsad pa zhen snang dag pa'i shul du bsam shes skye'am /
NK076(mu)001:3057: dang po ltar na bsam shes don med du thal te /
NK076(mu)001:3058: de'i tshe zhen snang mi zhen pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3059: gnyis pa ltar na skyon snga so na gnas so
NK076(mu)001:3060: ce na brtsad spong ma yin te phyi ma gnyen
NK076(mu)001:3061: po'i nus pa dang phrad tsam gyis snga ma spang
NK076(mu)001:3062: bya'i mngon gyur 'gal ba la phyogs pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:3063: lhan cig ring du mi gnas pa'i 'gal ba yin pa'i phyir zhes pa ni dngos po'i lan no //
NK076(mu)001:3065: de tsam du snang bas mun pa spong ba'i tshe mun pa dag pa'i shul du snang ba skye'am /
NK076(mu)001:3066: ma dag pa la skye zhes dri'o //
NK076(mu)001:3067: dang po ltar na 'dir yang zhen dag pa'i shul du bsam shes skye'o //
NK076(mu)001:3069: mi gnas pa'i phyir bsam shes don med du thal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:3070: der yang mun pa mi gnas pa'i phyir snang ba don med du thal lo //
NK076(mu)001:3071: gnyis pa ltar na zhen snang ma dag pa la bsam shes skye zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:3072: de'i tshe shes rgyud skad cig gi steng du gzhal
NK076(mu)001:3073: bya 'jal byed mtshungs pa'i phyir shes rgyud gnyis ldan
NK076(mu)001:3075: der yang de'i tshe snang mun mtshungs pa'i phyir mngon
NK076(mu)001:3076: 'gyur gyi dngos po gcig la sgrib ma sgrib cha
NK076(mu)001:3077: gnyis su gcig la ldan par thal lo /
NK076(mu)001:3078: khyab pa ma grub ce na'ang mtshungs pa nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:3079: gang du gzhal bya 'jal byed dus mtshungs pa la shes rgyud gnyis ldan gyis khyab te /
NK076(mu)001:3080: skyes bu dang skyes bu sa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:3082: der yang gang du snang mun dus mtshungs pa la rdzas cha gnyis dang ldan pas khyab te /
NK076(mu)001:3083: khri mun dang mthong mun bzhin zhes pa'i bar du
NK076(mu)001:3084: 'jam dbyangs kyis kyang dgag mi yod par 'gro bar
NK076(mu)001:3085: 'gyur ro // gal lte snang mun rdzas tha dad pa'o zhes kyang brjod par mi nus te /
NK076(mu)001:3086: snang bas mun pa logs su dor ba med cing ldog pa snang bar shar ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:3088: blo gsal ba dag gis da dung lug rigs du
NK076(mu)001:3089: mas ma 'khrul ba'i don spyad par gyis shig /gnyis
NK076(mu)001:3090: pa gzhal gyis mi langs pa'i dogs bsal ni /
NK076(mu)001:3091: 'o na 'khor 'das kyi zhen snang bsam gyis mi
NK076(mu)001:3092: khyab pa yod pa'i phyir gzhal gyis mi lang ngo
NK076(mu)001:3093: zhe na / da ltar gyi snod bcud log pa'i zhen snang 'di nyid la spyi grub pas /
NK076(mu)001:3094: yul dus rang bzhin gyis ma bskal ba'i chos can
NK076(mu)001:3095: chos bum pa lta bu gcig la sgro 'dogs chod
NK076(mu)001:3096: pas rigs kyi bye brag kun kyang de ltar shes
NK076(mu)001:3097: te / 'dam bu cig khog stong na kun kyang khog stong pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:3100: gzugs kyi de bzhin nyid shes na //
NK076(mu)001:3101: chos thams cad kyi mdo dang rgyas pa shes par 'gyur zhes pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:3102: 'di nyid las kyang lam rim dngos gnyis zhen dngos dus gsum chos //
NK076(mu)001:3103: skad cig cig la kun rdzob phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3104: de dngos mthong pa yang dag par //
NK076(mu)001:3105: rig phyir kun kyang de ltar shes //
NK076(mu)001:3107: bzhi pa rtsod pa spang ba ni /
NK076(mu)001:3108: de ltar la'ang so sor rtog pa'i shes rab de nyid ma 'khrul ba dri med zhig yin tam /
NK076(mu)001:3109: 'khrul pa'i dri ba bcas zhig yin /
NK076(mu)001:3111: 'bad med du grol thor 'byung bar thal 'khrul pa'i nyes pa zad pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3115: de nyid kyis ma nor don gyi bden pa gtan la pheb sam mi phebs /
NK076(mu)001:3116: dang po ltar na dung ser 'dzin gyi 'khrul shes kyi 'khrul dang spong nus par thar /
NK076(mu)001:3117: bsam shes nyid 'khrul pa'i khyab pa rang rgyud /
NK076(mu)001:3119: gnyis pa ltar na sems shes skyes pa don med du 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:3120: lan ma 'khrul ba dri med du 'dod do //
NK076(mu)001:3121: 'bad med du grol bar thal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:3122: dbang po ya rab la ltos nas 'dod pa nyid la /
NK076(mu)001:3123: 'bring man chad la ltos nas rtags ldan gyi rjes dpag gam /
NK076(mu)001:3124: yid ches pa'i lung rigs kyi sgra spyi'i rjes su
NK076(mu)001:3125: don spyi sgro 'dogs sel ba'i phyir khyab pa med
NK076(mu)001:3126: ces gca' bya'o // yang zhen snang yul du byed
NK076(mu)001:3127: mkhan gyi shes pa des zhen snang de yul du
NK076(mu)001:3130: dang po ltar na so sor rtog pa'i shes rab de nyid 'khrul bar thar /
NK076(mu)001:3131: kun brtags rdzun pa de nyid yul du byed pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3133: gnyis pa ltar na gzhal bya la sgro 'dogs ma chad par thal /
NK076(mu)001:3134: yul du ma gyur pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3136: ces dang lan ni yul du byed do //
NK076(mu)001:3137: 'khrul bar thal zhe na brtag par bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:3138: rang rgyud par yul du byas pa'i phyir zer ram
NK076(mu)001:3139: rang bzhin med sgrub kyi phyir zer ram rang bzhin
NK076(mu)001:3140: med sgrub kyi phyir gzhir yul du byed pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:3141: zer / dang po'i rtags khas ma blangs shing //
NK076(mu)001:3142: gnyis pa ltar na khyab pa ma grub pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:3143: de ltar gzhal bya nyid so sor rtog shes kyi
NK076(mu)001:3144: rgyus skad cig gnyis pa la mi dmigs pa'i shes
NK076(mu)001:3148: rang gis ngo bos gnas skabs kyang //
NK076(mu)001:3149: rgyu 'bras yin phyir cig shes la //
NK076(mu)001:3150: de nyid dngos lnga tshul dang tshig ces pas gsung ngo //
NK076(mu)001:3151: gnyis pa de gtan la 'bebs pa'i gtan tshigs la gnyis //
NK076(mu)001:3154: dang po ni bsgrub bya'i don yang dag par shes pa'i thabs rtsod gzhi la bkod pa ste //
NK076(mu)001:3156: gtan tshigs gtan tshigs brjod pa rnams //
NK076(mu)001:3157: bsgrub bya gang yin shes don la //
NK076(mu)001:3158: ngo bo nges tshig mtshan nyid stsogs //
NK076(mu)001:3159: gang nas phabs kyang rgyas par byos //
NK076(mu)001:3162: sngon 'byung dngos po lnga'i gtan tshigs /rjes 'jug tshul lnga'i gtan tshigs /tshig lnga'i gtan tshigs so //
NK076(mu)001:3165: zhar la rtsod pa spang ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:3167: sngon 'byung du ston pa sku lnga dngos kyi 'khor
NK076(mu)001:3168: lnga dngos la ston pa chos kyi skus 'khor ye
NK076(mu)001:3169: shes rgya mtsho la skye med don kyi gsung gis
NK076(mu)001:3170: // longs skus smin pa rgya mtsho la gong brda de gsung gis //
NK076(mu)001:3171: mngon byang gis rgyal ba rgyal mtsho la rig pa
NK076(mu)001:3172: byin rlabs kyi gsung gis sprul skus mos pa rgya
NK076(mu)001:3173: mtsho la brjod pa tshig gi gsung gis rdo rje'i
NK076(mu)001:3174: skus dbyer med rdo rje'i 'khor la rdo rje'i skus
NK076(mu)001:3175: dbyer med rdo rje'i 'khor la rdo rje'i gsung gis
NK076(mu)001:3176: te / gsung lnga'i sgo nas chos nyid kyi don
NK076(mu)001:3177: dngos su gtan la 'bebs pa gang yin pa ste
NK076(mu)001:3179: yang dag rdzogs sangs rgyas ston pa //
NK076(mu)001:3181: gsung lnga bstan pa de kho na //
