NK076(mu)001:3186: dngos lnga he du dang gzhal bya la 'brel ba yod dam med drang /
NK076(mu)001:3187: gnyis pa ltar na gtan tshigs don med du 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:3188: gzhal bya la 'brel ba med pa'i phyir mig gis sgra mi thos pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:3189: dang po ltar na 'dra gcig pa'am /
NK076(mu)001:3192: dang po ltar na gtan tshigs kyis gzhal bya'i zhe na snang mi spong bar thar //
NK076(mu)001:3193: ngo bo dbyer med pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3194: gser dang ser khyab po bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:3196: gzhal bya la he du 'byung ngam he du la gzhal bya 'byung /
NK076(mu)001:3197: gnyis pa ltar na sku lnga 'khrul bcas su thal /
NK076(mu)001:3198: dngos lnga'i gtan tshigs la 'khrul pa'i rgyu ma zad pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3199: gser dang ser po bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:3200: gang du rgyu ma zad pa la 'bras bu skyer rung gis khyab te sbyang gi til bzhin /
NK076(mu)001:3201: dang po ltar na he du nyid go byed gzhan rkyen la ma ltos par thal /
NK076(mu)001:3202: gzhal bya nyid la skye ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3203: 'dod na gsung lnga la dgos pa med par thar lo /
NK076(mu)001:3204: gsum pa ltar na sangs rgyas kyi zhen snang bden pa nyid yul du byed par thal /
NK076(mu)001:3205: yul don mthun par 'dzin pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3206: sngo 'dzin sngon po las mi 'khrul ba bzhin /
NK076(mu)001:3207: 'dod na sangs rgyas 'khrul ldan du 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:3211: dang po ni blo na shag mgon kha cig na
NK076(mu)001:3212: re 'brel ba ni yod kyi ngo bo dbyer med
NK076(mu)001:3213: kyi / de kho na nyid la 'jal bas zhen
NK076(mu)001:3214: 'khrul du mi 'gyur ces zer ba ni mi 'thad
NK076(mu)001:3215: kyi / de / de nyid rtog na gtan tshigs kyis ci zhig bya /
NK076(mu)001:3216: ma rtogs kyi bar du zhen 'khrul gyi skyon snga son gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:3217: yang kha brtsang cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:3218: 'di brtags gzhi min te gtan tshigs 'byung ba'i gzhi yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3219: zhen snang dang 'brel pa med dam ces zer ba'ang mi 'thad do //
NK076(mu)001:3220: dngos su gsung lnga nyid kyis brda sprad par gsungs shing /
NK076(mu)001:3221: gzhal bya dang 'brel pa med pa'i he du la don med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:3222: yang kha cig na re nya tshal ba zhen snang mtshan nyid la med kyi /
NK076(mu)001:3223: go bye ba'i 'khor gyi ched du brtags su bcas
NK076(mu)001:3224: tsam zhig yong ba ltar brtan nas gtan la 'bebs
NK076(mu)001:3226: ston pa'i ngos nas brtags pa zhig gam /
NK076(mu)001:3227: 'khor gyi ngos nas brtags pa zhig drangs /
NK076(mu)001:3228: dang po la ni rang rgyud kyis bsdus pa'i 'khrul
NK076(mu)001:3229: rtog gi ming tsam yang mi gnas pa lta zhog
NK076(mu)001:3230: /phal che ba sku bzhi'i 'khor la 'ang rang rgyud
NK076(mu)001:3231: du zhen pa med de rjes thob du'ang yul rnams
NK076(mu)001:3232: sgyu ma ltar bur gzigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:3233: ji skad du don bsdus rang gi mtshan nyid mngon sum du //
NK076(mu)001:3234: gsal bar mthong ba'i dbugs phyin te //
NK076(mu)001:3236: zag gsum zag rigs 'di la med //
NK076(mu)001:3239: 'khor gyi ngo la ltos nas gzhal bya 'jal byed
NK076(mu)001:3240: kyi 'brel pa tsam gnas kyi gtan tshigs kyis gzhal
NK076(mu)001:3242: gzhal byas gtan tshigs la ma khyab pas 'khrul bar mi 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:3243: snang yang rang rgyud du ma zhen pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3244: skyes bu mngon shes can gyi gzhan 'khrul gyi rmi lam shes pa lta bu'o //
NK076(mu)001:3246: mdo mkhyen pa'i ye shes cig nyid kyis //
NK076(mu)001:3247: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor kun khyab cing //
NK076(mu)001:3249: de ltar na'ang nyid sangs rgyas nyid 'khrul ldan du thal te /
NK076(mu)001:3250: khyab bya la zhen snang ma dor ba'i phyir zhe na //
NK076(mu)001:3251: de tsam du 'byung la nam mkhas khyab sam ma khyab //
NK076(mu)001:3252: gnyis pa ltar na chos nyid kyi dper yang bya bar mi rung la /
NK076(mu)001:3253: dang po ltar na nam mkha' dngos so thal te /
NK076(mu)001:3254: khyab bya la dngos rdzas ma dor phyir zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:3255: yang sngon 'byung sku lnga'i 'khor lnga la zhen snang yod dam med drang /
NK076(mu)001:3256: gnyis pa ltar na 'jal byed gtan tshigs don med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:3259: dang po ltar na mi rigs te sku lnga'i 'khor
NK076(mu)001:3260: byed par nus pa ni mthong lam yan chad kyi
NK076(mu)001:3262: mthong lam la zhen snang dag pa khyab pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3263: 'dod pa ni mi nus te mthong lam zhen snang dngos 'gal du bshad pa cis spong zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:3264: lan du kha cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:3265: dngos po lnga'i gtan tshigs kyis skabs su gzhal bya
NK076(mu)001:3266: nas phyag na rdo rje snyan cha lnga dang ldan
NK076(mu)001:3267: pa ni zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:3268: de ltar na'ang phyag na rdo rje la zhen snang yod dam med /
NK076(mu)001:3269: dang po ltar na'ang rgyu'i theg pa las kyang sa bcu'i dbang phyug du bshad la /
NK076(mu)001:3270: gsang sngags su sangs rgyas kun gyi mes por gsungs
NK076(mu)001:3271: pa dang 'gal te da dung zhen snang med pa'i
NK076(mu)001:3272: phyir ro // gal te zhen snang med pa nyid
NK076(mu)001:3273: la gtan tshigs kyi rtags bkod pa don med de
NK076(mu)001:3274: rang mtshan kun brtags kyis ma bsgribs pa'i phyir ro
NK076(mu)001:3275: phyir ro // // bdag gi bla ma rog ni
NK076(mu)001:3276: sku bzhi'i 'khor la zhen snang rang rgyud pa med
NK076(mu)001:3277: phyir ro // // gsung / de ltar na gzhal bya med pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3278: gtan tshigs don med du thal zhes pa'i lan du /
NK076(mu)001:3279: sngon 'byung don med du thal zer ram /
NK076(mu)001:3280: rjes 'jug don med du thal zer /
NK076(mu)001:3282: gnyis pa ltar na sngon 'byung du don med kyang
NK076(mu)001:3283: rjes 'jug go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched du zhen
NK076(mu)001:3284: snang yod pa ltar bstan nas gtan la phab pas
NK076(mu)001:3285: don du 'gyur ba ni ci sto ste khyab pa
NK076(mu)001:3286: ma grub ces gsung pa'ang legs par ma rtogs te
NK076(mu)001:3287: / dang po ltar na mthong lam yan chad kyi rgyud la zhen rtog mi srid par thal /
NK076(mu)001:3288: gtan tshigs don med pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3289: 'dod par mi nus te bzang rtog gnyen po'i zhen yul shes sgrib yod par gsal /
NK076(mu)001:3290: gang du zhen snang cung zad kyang med pa la
NK076(mu)001:3291: 'jal byed don med pas khyab te sangs rgyas bzhin
NK076(mu)001:3292: no // gnyis pa rjes 'jug ltar na sngon 'byung
NK076(mu)001:3293: dag pa'i rgyud la gnas pa rnams la zhen snang
NK076(mu)001:3294: yod pa ltar bstan pas rjes 'jug gi don du
NK076(mu)001:3295: no // mi 'gyur te / zhen snang thug med
NK076(mu)001:3296: du dgos pa'i log rtog mi khegs pa'i phyir ro
NK076(mu)001:3297: no // mi 'gyur te / // rang lugs ni
NK076(mu)001:3298: ston pa sku bzhi'i 'khor la'ang zhen snang phra ba
NK076(mu)001:3299: ci rigs yod par khas len te /
NK076(mu)001:3300: de lta min na sku lnga'i 'khor bya don med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:3302: spyir na zhen snang gi gong ba shes bya ni
NK076(mu)001:3303: de kho na nyid don gyi gnas lugs la blo
NK076(mu)001:3304: yi dri mas bzang ngan du sgro 'dogs pa la
NK076(mu)001:3306: de yang yongs su brtags pa'i gzhir //
NK076(mu)001:3307: dbang po yul du snang ba kun //
NK076(mu)001:3308: yul na yod pa ma yin te //
NK076(mu)001:3309: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa nyid //
NK076(mu)001:3310: dngos po sna tshogs par snang bas /
NK076(mu)001:3313: de'i yang ngan rtog phra rags gnyis rim gyis pa bzhin du mthong bsgom gyis spong zhing /
NK076(mu)001:3314: gnyen po la kun tu brten pa bzang rtog gi
NK076(mu)001:3315: shes bya'i sgrib pa shin tu phra ba ni mthar
NK076(mu)001:3317: da dung mnyam pa la bzhag 'jog pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:3318: ji skad du mi mthun mtshan ma gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3319: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK076(mu)001:3320: bdag rtog mtshan ma kun bcom nas //
NK076(mu)001:3321: mnyam bzhag ye shes dbang bskur zhing //
NK076(mu)001:3322: don du gnyer ba'i smon lam mthus //
NK076(mu)001:3324: de nyid kyi sgrib pa'i zhen snang ma yin na
NK076(mu)001:3325: ni rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin skyes pa don
NK076(mu)001:3326: med du thal / spang bya med pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3330: sa bcu rgyun mthar byang chub snying por rdo rje gdan dang bzhugs pa na //
NK076(mu)001:3331: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug dang //
NK076(mu)001:3332: gzhan yang dri ma rnam mang ngo //
NK076(mu)001:3333: khyed kyi ye shes me yis bsregs //
NK076(mu)001:3335: 'di nyid las kyang lam rim bag la nyal ba 'jom byed cing /
NK076(mu)001:3337: gang du yang bya ba med pa la gnyan po
NK076(mu)001:3338: don med pa'i khyab ste nyin bar gyi mar me
NK076(mu)001:3339: bzhin ces bya ba ni rigs par smras pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:3340: de ltar na'ang mthong lam skyes pa don med du thal te /
NK076(mu)001:3341: da dung zhen snang yod pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:3342: de'i rags pa'ang yod pa'i phyir zer ram /
NK076(mu)001:3343: phra ba tsam yod pa'i phyir zer //
NK076(mu)001:3344: dang po'i rtags khas ma blangs shing //
NK076(mu)001:3345: gnyis pa ltar na khyab pa ma grub te sangs
NK076(mu)001:3346: rgyas kyi ye shes mngon du ma gyur gyi ring
NK076(mu)001:3347: la zhen sgrib phra ba yod pas na /
NK076(mu)001:3348: 'das pa'i zhen snang ces pa'ang phyogs 'ga' zhig las brtags par zad do //
NK076(mu)001:3349: yang dngos lnga'i gtan tshigs la rjes 'jug gi spyad
NK076(mu)001:3350: du yod dam med dang po ltar lam rim na
NK076(mu)001:3351: bzhi rjes mi spyod ga cig rjes spyod //
NK076(mu)001:3352: ces spyad du med par dang 'gal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:3353: gnyis pa ltar na lam rim brda spros rjes 'jug bstan pa'ang //
NK076(mu)001:3354: bsregs bcad brdar ba'i gser bzhin du //
NK076(mu)001:3355: dngos po lngas legs par brtags te dbab ces spyad
NK076(mu)001:3356: du yod par bshad pa ji ltar drang she na
NK076(mu)001:3357: / lan du dbang po rtul po la ltos nas
NK076(mu)001:3358: spyad du med de tshig gi yul du ma gyur
NK076(mu)001:3359: / pa'i phyir / ji skad du lam rim tshigs dang yi ges mtshon du med /
NK076(mu)001:3361: dbang rnon la ltos na spyad du yod de brjod
NK076(mu)001:3362: pa la mi ltos par don rtogs par 'gyur pa'i
NK076(mu)001:3364: ji skad du lam rim brjod dang 'dra bar brda sprod pas //
NK076(mu)001:3365: ngo bo nyid kyi bshad pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3366: ma 'ongs don du gtan tshigs nges //
NK076(mu)001:3368: rjes 'jug gi gtan tshigs ni tshul dang tshig gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:3369: de nyid kyi khyad par ni /
NK076(mu)001:3370: kha cig zur pa na re /
NK076(mu)001:3371: sku lnga dngos min yang sku lnga dang tshul mthun par don rtogs su gyur pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:3373: tshig gis go rtags su gyur pa tshig gi gtan tshigs so ces zer mod kyi /
NK076(mu)001:3374: d+aa ki ru rog ni sngon 'byung gtan la phab pa'i tshul du go la gyi gtan tshigs la /
NK076(mu)001:3375: de tshigs su brjod pa ni tshig gi gtan tshigs so gsung ngo //
NK076(mu)001:3376: gnyis pa tshul gyi gtan tshigs la lnga ste /
NK076(mu)001:3377: chos sku'i gsung dang mthun pa skye med don gyi
NK076(mu)001:3378: he du skye med mtshan nam mkha' lta bu dang
NK076(mu)001:3379: // mngon byang gi gsung dang tshul mthun pa rang
NK076(mu)001:3380: rig mngon gsal gyi he dum rtog med rang gsal
NK076(mu)001:3381: nyi ma'i snying po lta bu dang /
NK076(mu)001:3382: longs sku'i gsung dang tshul mthun pa dgongs pa brda
NK076(mu)001:3383: yi he du sgrib pa ngos 'don pa me long
NK076(mu)001:3384: gi gzugs brnyan lta bu dang /
NK076(mu)001:3385: rdo rje'i sku'i gsung dang tshul mthun pa dbyer med
NK076(mu)001:3386: rdo rje'i he du grag stong gnyis med brag cha
NK076(mu)001:3387: lta bu dang / sprul sku'i gsung tshul dang mthun
NK076(mu)001:3388: pa brjod pa tshig gi he du kun yid 'jug
NK076(mu)001:3389: lta bu dang / pa / tshangs pa'i dbyangs lta bu'o //
NK076(mu)001:3390: de dag he du de dag gis dbang po yang
NK076(mu)001:3391: rab du gyur pa la snang grags 'di nyid kyis
NK076(mu)001:3392: mtshon nas sku lnga'i tshul du gtan la phebs par
NK076(mu)001:3394: lam rim rtogs dang ldan pa'i blo rnams la //
NK076(mu)001:3395: dngos po sna tshogs sems gsang sngags //
NK076(mu)001:3396: dpe lung yin phyir chos tshul ston //
NK076(mu)001:3397: brjod dang 'dra bar brda sprod pas //
NK076(mu)001:3398: ngo bo nyid kyi bshad pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3399: ma 'ong don du gtan tshigs nges //
NK076(mu)001:3401: gnyams pa tshig gi gtan tshigs dbye ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:3403: dang po ni sngar kyis tshul lnga nyid tshig dngos tu brjod pa lnga'o //
NK076(mu)001:3404: bsdu na spyad du med pas go ba sku bzhi'i he du dang /
NK076(mu)001:3405: spyad du yod pa go ba sprul pa sku'i he du gnyis su 'dus te /
NK076(mu)001:3406: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni dngos su tshig tu ma gsungs pas spyad du med pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:3407: dngos tshigs su spyad du med pa ni spyad du yod pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:3408: ces bdag gi bla mas gsungs mod kyi /
NK076(mu)001:3409: bdag ni don car phog du ston pas spyad du med pa /
NK076(mu)001:3410: don la rgyud nas ston pas spyad du yod par
NK076(mu)001:3411: ces mkhas slas pa'i skye bo gzhan gyis 'dod pa'i
NK076(mu)001:3412: rjes su 'brangs nas legs par som te /
NK076(mu)001:3414: de ltar mod kyang bsdu na gnyis //
NK076(mu)001:3415: bzhi rjes mi spyod gcig rjes spyod //
NK076(mu)001:3416: rnam gnyis tshul gyis don byed pa //
NK076(mu)001:3417: dbang po rnams dang mthun sbyor ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:3419: dang po spyad du med pas go ba la bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:3421: ma spyad pa'i go ba dpe /
NK076(mu)001:3423: dang po ni dbang po rnon po la chos nyid
NK076(mu)001:3424: kyi don cig char du snang bar byas te rtags
NK076(mu)001:3428: de la ji bzhin nyid dbab pa //
NK076(mu)001:3429: ji bzhin brjod pa'i tshig rnams kyis //
NK076(mu)001:3430: dkar pos dkar po mtshon pa bzhin //
NK076(mu)001:3431: bsam brjod 'das pa de nyid mtshon //
NK076(mu)001:3434: spyad pa las rtog pa 'byung bar 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:3436: spyad pa zhug na rtog pa'i gzhi //
NK076(mu)001:3437: dmigs pa zhugs na 'dzin pa'i gzungs //
NK076(mu)001:3441: gser blta bar 'dod pa la gser nyid bstan pa lta bu ste /
NK076(mu)001:3443: de bas gser blta gser bzhin du //
NK076(mu)001:3444: bdag phyir bya byed ma dmigs pas //
NK076(mu)001:3445: rtog dpyod dmigs 'dzin mi tshol ba'i //
NK076(mu)001:3446: de brjod nyid kyis de nyid mtshon //
NK076(mu)001:3449: dang po na de nyid so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyi yul ma yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:3450: dpyad du med pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:3451: de tsam du rtog ge'i dbang shes sbyangs yul nye bar mi 'dzin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:3456: gzhal bya 'jal byed du gsal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:3457: yul dang yul can du gsal lo //
NK076(mu)001:3458: gang dpyad du med pa la shes yul ma yin
NK076(mu)001:3459: pas khyab ste mig shes dang sgra bzhin ce na
NK076(mu)001:3460: / gong rtog pa med pa la yul mi 'dzin
NK076(mu)001:3461: pa'i khyab te 'gog pa'i snyoms 'jug bzhin zhes bya'o
NK076(mu)001:3462: / // dngos por na brtags dpyad lam brten par
NK076(mu)001:3463: rtogs pa nyid shes rab kyi phul du gyur pa
NK076(mu)001:3465: so sor gang la'ang rtog med par //
NK076(mu)001:3466: so sor snang ba kun rtog phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3467: so sor rtogs pa'i mchog yin te //
NK076(mu)001:3468: brtags pa med pa'i bla dwags yin //
NK076(mu)001:3470: yang gtan tshigs ni rjes dpag kyis mtshon byed yin gyi /
NK076(mu)001:3471: 'dir mngon gyur ma ci zhig bya zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:3472: ma yin te mngon gyur mtshon pa'i ngag la dgongs pa ni lung bsdams grub bo //
NK076(mu)001:3473: yang ma dpyad par go ba la rkyen dgos sam mi dgos ce na /
NK076(mu)001:3474: rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon gyi mgo bsgre /
NK076(mu)001:3475: dpyad mtshungs pa nyid yin no //
NK076(mu)001:3476: yang gtan tshigs de'i zlog pa nas gzhal bya dang ldan nam mi ldan /
NK076(mu)001:3478: dpyad du yod pa dang khyad med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:3479: gnyis pa ltar he du'i sgra mi 'jug ce na /
NK076(mu)001:3480: gzhal bya tsam zhig yod kyi 'jal tshul go ba myur bul gyis 'dir khyad par du byas te /
NK076(mu)001:3481: rta pa dang rkang 'gros bzhin zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:3482: gnyis pa spyad du yod pas go ba la gnyis ste /
NK076(mu)001:3485: dang po dbang po rtul po la brtags dpyad la
NK076(mu)001:3486: brten nas chos nyid kyis gtan la 'bebs pa ste
NK076(mu)001:3488: ye shes kun mnyam lha grangs dgu /thos bsam so sor rtog bsgom dang //
NK076(mu)001:3489: rnal 'byor rim pa'i rgyu las skyes //
NK076(mu)001:3491: dbye na sgrub bya'i don dang he du'i tshig mi mthun pa'i don dang /
NK076(mu)001:3492: mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK076(mu)001:3493: bsgrub bya'i don dang he du'i tshig mthun pa don dang mthun pa'i gtan tshigs gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:3495: brjod pa'i dngos po spyad yul la //
NK076(mu)001:3496: so sor rtog pa'i gtan tshigs rkyen //
NK076(mu)001:3497: don dang mthun dang mi mthun pa //
NK076(mu)001:3499: dang po dpyad du yod pa mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs la bzhi /
NK076(mu)001:3503: dang po ni tshad mas gzhal rung gi zhen snang ngo //
NK076(mu)001:3505: spyir na log rtog bsam yas kyang //
NK076(mu)001:3506: ye nas yod pa ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:3508: gnyis pa gtan tshigs rang gi ngo bo ni //
NK076(mu)001:3509: shes byed kyi rtags go bzlog nas ston pa ste //
NK076(mu)001:3511: de mtshon ci yang yin pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3512: de phyir ma yin kun yin pas //
NK076(mu)001:3514: gsum pa dpe ni rtog ge ba'i 'bras rtags kyis
NK076(mu)001:3515: lam ldan du bsgrub pa khyab pas mtshon pa lta
NK076(mu)001:3517: phyi ma mi mthun mtshon byed ltar /
NK076(mu)001:3519: bzhi pa dgos pa ni phyogs gcig tu 'dzin pa'i
NK076(mu)001:3520: zhen pa dgrol zhing phyogs med kyi don rtogs par
NK076(mu)001:3523: phyi ma mi mthun mtshon byed ltar //
NK076(mu)001:3525: bzhi pa dgos pa ni phyogs gcig tu 'dzin pa'i
NK076(mu)001:3526: zhen pa dgrol zhing phyogs med kyi don rtogs par
NK076(mu)001:3531: ngo bos phebs par rgyas par 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:3533: gnyis pa tshig don mthun pa'i he du la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:3534: spyir dbye ba'i khyad par dang /
NK076(mu)001:3535: bye brag so so nas gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:3537: tshig don gnyis ka gzhung 'di nyid las khyad par
NK076(mu)001:3538: du grags pa ltar gtan la 'bebs pa tshad ma
NK076(mu)001:3539: bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs dang /
NK076(mu)001:3540: tshig mdo sngags thun mong du grangs shing don 'di
NK076(mu)001:3541: nyid ltar gtan la 'bebs pa sgra mthun don spags
NK076(mu)001:3543: so so nas gtan la dbab po'i dang po tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs la bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:3544: dag pa mnyam pa rtogs pa /
NK076(mu)001:3545: bdag gi chen po'i gtan tshigs so //
NK076(mu)001:3549: dang po ni 'di ltar snang ba phyi nang gi chos rnams chos can /
NK076(mu)001:3550: ye nas sku dang ye shes kyi ngo bor sangs rgyas yin te /
NK076(mu)001:3551: dag pa gsum mam bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:3552: gsum ni snod 'byung ba lnga yum lngar dag /bcud
NK076(mu)001:3553: phung po lnga yab lngar dag /rgyud rnams par shes
NK076(mu)001:3554: pa'i tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar dag ste /
NK076(mu)001:3555: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing /
NK076(mu)001:3557: bzhi ni don dam chos nyid dmigs med du dag
NK076(mu)001:3558: /kun rdzob chos can sgyu mar dag /rgyu ni 'byung
NK076(mu)001:3559: ba lngar dag / 'bras bu dam rdzas bdud rtsi lngar dag ste /
NK076(mu)001:3560: rnam bzhi'i tshul gyis dag rtogs mngon /
NK076(mu)001:3562: dgos ched ni 'og ma bas dag ma dag gnyis
NK076(mu)001:3563: su lta ba'i phyogs 'dzin dgag pa'i 'bras bu rang
NK076(mu)001:3564: nyid las 'byung bar shes par 'gyur ba ste /
NK076(mu)001:3566: gsum bzhi bzhi brjod dgos ched ni //
NK076(mu)001:3567: rmongs pa gsum bzhi dag ma dag /
NK076(mu)001:3568: 'dzin pa'i lta ngan bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3569: rnam grangs brjod kyi ngo bo gcig /ces so //
NK076(mu)001:3571: dag pa'i he dus da ltar gyi snang ba rang ga ma 'di spang sam mi spang /
NK076(mu)001:3573: ye nas dag pa nyid ma yin par thal //
NK076(mu)001:3575: gal te dag kyang spong na thugs med du 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:3576: gnyis pa ltar na so skye rnams bden mthong du thal te /
NK076(mu)001:3577: dag pa yul du byed pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3578: 'dod na 'bad med du grol bar rigs ce na /
NK076(mu)001:3580: snang tsam ma spang shing rang kar mi ldan pa ni rnyog ma dwangs pa'i chu lta bu ste /
NK076(mu)001:3582: chu khams gser dang nam mkha' ltar //
NK076(mu)001:3583: dag pa bzhin du dag par 'dod //
NK076(mu)001:3585: mnyam pa'i gtan tshigs la'ang gsum ste /
NK076(mu)001:3591: lhag pa chos kyi sku chen por ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK076(mu)001:3592: mnyam pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:3594: don dam skye med du mnyam /
NK076(mu)001:3596: bden pa dbyer med du mnyam /
NK076(mu)001:3597: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral bar mnyam te /
NK076(mu)001:3598: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK076(mu)001:3599: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK076(mu)001:3602: 'khor 'das bzang ngan du zhen pa zlog cing mnyam pa'i don la nges shes bskyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:3603: ji skad du kun kyang mnyam pa nyid yin pas //
NK076(mu)001:3605: so sor lta ba brjod par bya //
NK076(mu)001:3606: dgag cing blang bar med ces so //
NK076(mu)001:3608: de ltar na'ang thun mong gi theg pa mnyam pa
NK076(mu)001:3609: gnyis po 'di sgra mthun don spags kyi gtan tshigs
NK076(mu)001:3610: su thal te / 'og ma dang ming mi mthun pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:3611: ma yin te lhag pa'i bden gnyis kyi ltos pa
NK076(mu)001:3612: ngos bzung tsam yin gyi bsgrub byed dngos ma yin
NK076(mu)001:3613: pa'i phyir nyes pa med de zhes /
NK076(mu)001:3614: gsungs pa'ang re zhig spyod do //
NK076(mu)001:3615: rtogs pa'i gtan tshigs la'ang dngos /
NK076(mu)001:3619: lus ngag yid kyis bsdus pa'i sems can gyi khams rnams chos can /
NK076(mu)001:3620: ye nas sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bor sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK076(mu)001:3621: rtogs pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:3623: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad don sems nyid du rgyu ga cig rtags yig 'bru gsum du gsal /
NK076(mu)001:3624: byin rlabs sku gsung thugs su nyams su blangs pas //
NK076(mu)001:3625: 'bras bu mngon sum par sangs rgyas pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3627: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK076(mu)001:3628: byin gyis rlabs dang mngon sum pa //
NK076(mu)001:3629: rab tu rtogs pa rnam bzhi yis //
NK076(mu)001:3630: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal po che //
NK076(mu)001:3632: de ltar bzhi po de yang gang zag ga cig
NK076(mu)001:3633: gi rgyu la sbyor ba skor ba gcig yin te
NK076(mu)001:3634: rjes dpag gi tshul gsum gyis la la me sgrub
NK076(mu)001:3637: sems can gyi lus ngag yid gsum gyi rang bzhin
NK076(mu)001:3638: gcig pa'i sku gsung thugs sngon du shes par bya
NK076(mu)001:3639: ba'i phyir ro // ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:3640: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med pas //
NK076(mu)001:3641: sku gsung thugs kyi yi ge gsum //
NK076(mu)001:3644: de ltar grub mtha' dang khyad med du 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:3645: ma yin te go byed kyi ngos nas gtan tshigs
NK076(mu)001:3646: su 'gro la grub mtha' ni rtogs pa'i don nyid
NK076(mu)001:3647: do // bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs la'ang gsum ste /
NK076(mu)001:3648: dngos dgos ched rtsod spong ngo //
NK076(mu)001:3650: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams snang lugs du mar snang
NK076(mu)001:3651: na'ang sems nyid skye ba med pa rang byung gi
NK076(mu)001:3652: ye shes chen po gcig gi bdag nyid du ye
NK076(mu)001:3653: nas gnas pa gtan la phebs pa de /
NK076(mu)001:3654: de la rang rgyud gsum dang /
NK076(mu)001:3657: skye ba can mi bden pa'i phyir skye med bden /
NK076(mu)001:3658: gzhan 'byung mi bden pa'i phyir rang 'byung bden /
NK076(mu)001:3659: glo bur mi bden pa'i phyir ye nas gnas pa bden zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:3661: skye med mi bden pa'i skye ba can de bden par thal /
NK076(mu)001:3662: 'dod na rang las skye'am gzhan las skye ces pas
NK076(mu)001:3663: dgag go /rang byung mi bden pa'i phyir gzhan byung
NK076(mu)001:3664: bden par thal / 'dod na rgyu gcig las byung ngam //
NK076(mu)001:3665: du ma las byung ces pas dgag go /ye nas
NK076(mu)001:3666: gnas pa mi bden pa'i glo bur ba bden pa
NK076(mu)001:3667: thal / 'dod na glo bur ba la rgyu yod dam med /
NK076(mu)001:3668: dang po ltar na glo bur ba nyams la //
NK076(mu)001:3669: gnyis pa ltar na med pa'i chos bzhi srid par thal //
NK076(mu)001:3672: spyod yul yongs su dag par shes par bya ba'i phyir te /
NK076(mu)001:3674: bdag nyid chen po'i rkyen tshig gis //
NK076(mu)001:3675: log rtog rgyu 'bras bdag gzhan phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3676: snang ba 'di kun rang rang gi /rang bzhin med pa'i rnam shes nyid //
NK076(mu)001:3677: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK076(mu)001:3678: rang byung spyod yul bral bas dag /ces so //
NK076(mu)001:3680: de ltar na'ang phyi ma 'di nyid sgra mthun don spags su 'gyur zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:3681: ma yin te 'og ma dag pa nyid rang byung gi ye shes su mi ston pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:3682: gnyis pa sgra mthun don spags kyi gtan tshigs la bzhi /
NK076(mu)001:3686: mtshon pa dpe'i gtan tshigs so //
NK076(mu)001:3688: thun mong pa dag nyon mongs pa spyi'i mtshan nyid
NK076(mu)001:3689: ni sems rab tu ma zhi ba'i rnam pa can
NK076(mu)001:3690: yin la / rang gi mtshan nyid kun nas mnar
NK076(mu)001:3691: sems pa la sogs pa lnga la 'dod mod kyi
NK076(mu)001:3692: yin la / / 'dir khyad par kyi lugs kyis
NK076(mu)001:3693: nyon mongs pa spyi'i mtshan nyid ni rigs su spros
NK076(mu)001:3694: pa dang bral bar mtshon la /
NK076(mu)001:3695: rang gi mtshan nyid rig pa sgyu ma'i rtsal so sor snang ba ste /
NK076(mu)001:3697: yang dag par ma grub ste /
NK076(mu)001:3698: nyon mongs pa rnams rang rang gi ngo bos stong pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3700: la la rang rig thabs chen du //
NK076(mu)001:3701: ma 'gags snang ba rang snang ste //
NK076(mu)001:3702: dngos kun rnam par byang ba dang //
NK076(mu)001:3703: mtshan nyid yin te spyi ru 'dod //
NK076(mu)001:3706: thun mong gi gzhung gis spyi dang //
NK076(mu)001:3707: rang gi mtshan nyid du phye nas 'khor ba'i lam du brtags te spong sbyong byed la /
NK076(mu)001:3708: 'dir spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid du phye nas myang 'das kyi lam du brtags te /
NK076(mu)001:3709: spong sbyong ba'i khyad par yang yod do //
NK076(mu)001:3711: nyon mongs rang dag spyir bstan pa //
NK076(mu)001:3712: mtshan nyid ma nor don rtogs na //
NK076(mu)001:3713: rnam du byang ba'i lam du 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:3714: de phyir rang spyi'i mtshan nyid gces //
NK076(mu)001:3716: mtha' dang bral ba'i gtan tshigs ni //
NK076(mu)001:3717: rang gzhan rig pa'i yul thams cad chos can //
NK076(mu)001:3718: spros pa'i mtha' cir yang ma grub ste //
NK076(mu)001:3719: yang dag gi gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3721: mtha' dang dbus med du mar bral //
NK076(mu)001:3722: gang yang ma yin de bzhin nyid //
NK076(mu)001:3723: dbyer med tshul du don rtogs phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3724: mtha' dang bral ba'ang de bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:3727: thun mong gi gcig dang du bral rnam gcod la
NK076(mu)001:3728: bkag pa'i yongs gcod la gcig du bral du bsgrub
NK076(mu)001:3729: la / 'dir gcig dang du ma'i snang ba ma
NK076(mu)001:3730: spangs shing mthar zhen pa la ma rig pa khyad
NK076(mu)001:3731: la / par yod de / ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:3732: phyogs 'dzin lta ngan dgrol ba dang //
NK076(mu)001:3734: mtha' dang bral zhes brjod mod kyi //
NK076(mu)001:3735: mtha' kun rang rig rang snang phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3736: 'di la bral dang ma bral dang //
NK076(mu)001:3737: grol dang ma grol phyogs zhen med //
NK076(mu)001:3739: rnam par dbye ba'i gtan tshigs ni //
NK076(mu)001:3740: phyi nang gi chos rnam chos can //
NK076(mu)001:3741: rang bzhin du nges pa ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:3742: 'byung ba la sogs pa re re'ang du ma'i chos dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3745: rnam par dbye ba'ang phung po dang //
NK076(mu)001:3746: 'byung ba la sogs dngos kun la //
NK076(mu)001:3747: dngos snang re re'ang bye brag ni //
NK076(mu)001:3748: brtsi bar ril por zhen grol ba //
NK076(mu)001:3751: thun mong gi mtshon bya mtshon byed tha snyad nges pa can du 'dod la /
NK076(mu)001:3752: 'dir mtshon byed yi ge mum gyis mtshon bya chos
NK076(mu)001:3753: kyi dbyings su mthar nges pa med par gtan la
NK076(mu)001:3757: rang bzhin med par gzhig bya'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3758: gcig la lnga lngar dbye bya zhing //
NK076(mu)001:3759: yum gyi dbyings su bstim par bya //
NK076(mu)001:3760: mun nyid smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK076(mu)001:3762: mtshon pa dpe'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK076(mu)001:3763: don 'ga' zhig dngos su bstan par ma nus pa
NK076(mu)001:3764: la nye bar 'jal ba'i dpe mtshon nas rdzogs par
NK076(mu)001:3765: byed do // sems kyi de kho na nyid nam mkha' skrun pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:3767: nam mkha' bzung du med par ltar //
NK076(mu)001:3768: snang srid thams cad de dang 'dra /
NK076(mu)001:3770: 'thad pa ni thun mong 'di dpe don tha dad du gtan la 'bebs pa la /
NK076(mu)001:3771: 'dir ni dpe don rang bzhin tha mi dad du mtshon pas khyad par yod de /
NK076(mu)001:3773: snang ba rang rgyud med pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3774: rang rig rang snang spyod yul med //
NK076(mu)001:3775: kun la de ltar 'byor bar gyis zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:3776: gtan tshigs de dag kyang ga cig gam tha dad ce na /
NK076(mu)001:3777: ngo bo 'am gtan tshigs la dbab bya'i don dbyer
NK076(mu)001:3778: med kyis mtshon tshul gyis ldog phyogs tha dad pa
NK076(mu)001:3780: de dag dbye ba mtshon gyi rnam grangs blo'i phyir bshad kyis /
NK076(mu)001:3781: de grangs su ngos bzung med /
NK076(mu)001:3782: de bas ngo bo gcig par bden //
NK076(mu)001:3784: gsum pa gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha' la gnyis
NK076(mu)001:3785: te gzhan sel nor ba don gyi lta ba 'og
NK076(mu)001:3786: ma'i grub mtha' dmigs kyis bskor ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:3787: don gnyer ma nor don gyi lta ba 'di nyid kyi grub mtha' dmigs kyis blangs pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:3789: de ltar ldan pa'i spyan 'tshol tshe //
NK076(mu)001:3790: gtan tshigs rnams kyis smal bya ste //
NK076(mu)001:3791: nor bas shes rab dmigs bsal nas //
NK076(mu)001:3792: ma nor dmigs nas bslang bar bya //
NK076(mu)001:3796: gol tshul bye brag tu bstan pa /
NK076(mu)001:3798: chos nyid du la bzla ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:3799: dang po ni chos nyid phyogs med chen po la //
NK076(mu)001:3800: rang rang gi blos phyogs ris su zhen pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:3801: nam mkha' ris su bcad pa lta bu ste /
NK076(mu)001:3803: spyi ni log rtog bsam yas pa //
NK076(mu)001:3804: ye nas yod pa ma yin te //
NK076(mu)001:3805: so so'i 'dzin rtogs bag chags kyis //
NK076(mu)001:3806: gzung 'dzin d+r+wa bas sgrib gyur te //
NK076(mu)001:3807: ci yang med las cir yang snang //
NK076(mu)001:3808: byang chub snying po'i gzhi la gol //
NK076(mu)001:3810: bye brag tu bstan pa la bcu ste //
NK076(mu)001:3811: 'jig rten pa'i lta ba lnga dang 'das pa'i lta ba lnga'o //
NK076(mu)001:3812: dang po'i dang po ni dngos po'i de nyid mi
NK076(mu)001:3813: shes pa'i dug lnga rang rgyud par spyad pas lam
NK076(mu)001:3815: de bas mnyam nyid mi rtogs pas //
NK076(mu)001:3818: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid ma rtogs pa'i dbang gis
NK076(mu)001:3819: zag pa dang bcas pa'i dge bcu khyad du spyad
NK076(mu)001:3820: pas 'dod khams kyi lha mir gol te /
NK076(mu)001:3821: dge bcu dag la gtsor len cing //
NK076(mu)001:3822: dge dang mi dge mi mnyam pas //
NK076(mu)001:3823: lha dang mi yi skye gnas te //
NK076(mu)001:3826: gzugs kyi 'dod chags ma bral zhing rtog dpyod ting
NK076(mu)001:3827: nge 'dzin ro la chags pas gzugs khams su gol
NK076(mu)001:3828: te / tshad med bzhi dang bsam gtan bzhi //
NK076(mu)001:3829: rim pas so sor bdag 'dzin cing //
NK076(mu)001:3830: gzungs khams kun la bdag tu rtog /
NK076(mu)001:3831: 'di ni tshangs gnas rim par skye //
NK076(mu)001:3833: lhag mthong gi shes rab kyis dben pa'i ming bzhi
NK076(mu)001:3834: la ldan pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gcig tu gzung
NK076(mu)001:3835: pas gzugs med kyi lhar gol te /
NK076(mu)001:3836: mnyam dang gzugs med ma rtogs pas //
NK076(mu)001:3837: ming bzhi med par ma shes te //
NK076(mu)001:3838: skye mched bzhi la gnas gyur na //
NK076(mu)001:3839: srid pa rtse mo'i sa ru skye /
NK076(mu)001:3841: chos nyid mtha' dang bral ba la sgro bskur gyi mthar zhen pas mu stegs su gol te /
NK076(mu)001:3842: rtag chad gnyis ka gang gi blo zhen pa //
NK076(mu)001:3843: don gyi snying po nyid las grol bar gsung //
NK076(mu)001:3845: 'das pa'i lta ba lnga'i dang po ni //
NK076(mu)001:3846: chos kyi bdag gzung 'dzin don dam du lta zhing
NK076(mu)001:3847: 'khor 'das bden bzhi'i rgyu 'bras la spang len byed
NK076(mu)001:3848: pas ni nyan thos su gol te /
NK076(mu)001:3849: gnyis med ma rtog thams cad la //
NK076(mu)001:3850: bden bzhi'i dngos por yod lta zhing //
NK076(mu)001:3851: spong dang mi spong byed gyur na //
NK076(mu)001:3852: 'di ni nyan thos sa pa yin //
NK076(mu)001:3854: shes pa skad cig don dam du lta zhing 'khor
NK076(mu)001:3855: 'das rgyu 'bras du 'dzin pas na rang rgyal du
NK076(mu)001:3856: gol ste / las dang nyon mongs thams cad la //
NK076(mu)001:3857: mnyam pa'i don du mi shes shing //
NK076(mu)001:3859: 'di ni rang sangs rgyas kyi sa //
NK076(mu)001:3861: bdag med gnyis kyi rtogs pa ci rigs par ldan
NK076(mu)001:3862: zhing bden gnyis bzang ngan blang dor du byed pas
NK076(mu)001:3863: ni byang chub sems par gol te /
NK076(mu)001:3864: mnyam pa'i don nyid mi shes shing //
NK076(mu)001:3865: kun rdzob don dam gnyis 'byed la //
NK076(mu)001:3866: chos dang gang zag bdag med na //
NK076(mu)001:3867: 'di ni byang chub sa pa yin //
NK076(mu)001:3869: don dam par mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i dag par
NK076(mu)001:3870: rtogs pa kun rdzob tu dngos grub gzhan du re
NK076(mu)001:3871: zhing rtsol bas kri yar gol te /
NK076(mu)001:3872: gnyis med mnyam par ma shes pas //
NK076(mu)001:3873: don dam dag pa chos nyid rtsam //
NK076(mu)001:3874: ye shes bzhi yon kun rdzob lha //
NK076(mu)001:3875: res bsgom bya ba las kyi sa //
NK076(mu)001:3877: don dam par mtshan ma med pa'i chos nyid kyi
NK076(mu)001:3878: byin rlabs kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi char lhar
NK076(mu)001:3879: brtags pa bzang ngan blang dor byed pa ni yo
NK076(mu)001:3880: gar gol te / lhun grub mnyam pa ma mthong pas //
NK076(mu)001:3881: chos kun rnam dag ye shes kyi //
NK076(mu)001:3882: byin rlabs rdo rje dbyings sprul pas //
NK076(mu)001:3883: blang dor byed pa las kyi sa //
NK076(mu)001:3886: 'dzin pa rnams duhkha'i btson rar tshud cing bde ba'i lam dang bral la /
NK076(mu)001:3887: 'das pa rnams rang rang gi lta spyod kyis rgyud bcings te //
NK076(mu)001:3888: mthar thug 'bras bu'i gegs su 'gyur ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:3890: bden min ma grol bcings pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:3892: 'phags lam bral zhing btson rar chud //
NK076(mu)001:3896: de dag ji ltar snang zhing gang ltar 'jig rten
NK076(mu)001:3897: na'ang rang bzhin chos nyid las nyams pa med de
NK076(mu)001:3898: / gser gyi bzo khyad bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:3900: theg pa mtho dman thams cad dang //
NK076(mu)001:3901: 'jig rten lta ba thams cad kun //
NK076(mu)001:3902: ye shes chen por rab brtags nas //
NK076(mu)001:3903: rang bzhin med las cir yang 'grub //
NK076(mu)001:3904: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa na //
NK076(mu)001:3906: sa dgu dag pa'i ye shes ni //
NK076(mu)001:3907: sa dgu ma spang ngang du bcom //
NK076(mu)001:3909: don gnyer ma nor don gyi lta ba 'di nyid
NK076(mu)001:3910: kyi grub mtha' dmigs kyis blangs ba la lnga ste
NK076(mu)001:3915: rtogs ma rtogs kyi skyon yon no //
NK076(mu)001:3916: dang po ni bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ste //
NK076(mu)001:3918: lhag pa'i mnyam nyid dbyer med don //
NK076(mu)001:3919: ming grangs cir yang bstan mod kyi //
NK076(mu)001:3920: don du smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK076(mu)001:3922: rnam grangs pa la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:3926: zag bcas kyi lha grangs ni bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:3928: mngon byas rim pa rtog gom rim //
NK076(mu)001:3929: rnam bzhi lam dang sgo bzhi dang //
NK076(mu)001:3930: bsnyen bsgrub lam grangs mnyam g.yo thob //
NK076(mu)001:3931: gom brtan mthar phyin rim par 'phar //
NK076(mu)001:3933: gnyis pa lam kun gyi lha grangs ni dgu ste //
NK076(mu)001:3935: mnyam nyid ngang las mi skrag pa //
NK076(mu)001:3936: mngon bya nges pa'i shes rab dang //
NK076(mu)001:3937: rnam pa kun ldan stong chen mthong //
NK076(mu)001:3938: rang rang snying rje ye shes gzigs //
NK076(mu)001:3939: phyag rgya gcig sku 'bras bu lta //
NK076(mu)001:3940: thams cad gsal ba'i lta ba dang //
NK076(mu)001:3941: bar chad med pa'i tshogs chen mthong //
NK076(mu)001:3942: dbang bsgyur mnyam nyiid mi g.yo ba //
NK076(mu)001:3943: ye shes kun mkhyen lha grangs dgu zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:3944: gsum pa rgyud don lha grangs bcu ni //
NK076(mu)001:3945: rgyud kyi dngos po re la lta ba re re'o //
NK076(mu)001:3946: ming gi rnam grangs ni rnam shes tshogs drug gi lta ba drug ste //
NK076(mu)001:3948: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gsal stong bzugs //
NK076(mu)001:3949: lha dang lta ba byar med par //
NK076(mu)001:3950: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams cad mthong //
NK076(mu)001:3951: gang du'ang ma mthong spyan gyi mchog /ces pa la sogs pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:3952: lta ba'i btsal thabs ni dri ma med pa'i shes
NK076(mu)001:3953: rab rnams gsum gyis yod med la sogs mtha' dang
NK076(mu)001:3954: bral ba las / btsal bar bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:3956: yod las btsal na sgro btags te //
NK076(mu)001:3957: sgro btags brgyad du ltung bar 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:3958: med las btsal na skur btab te //
NK076(mu)001:3959: bskur pa bcu yi gnas su ltung //
NK076(mu)001:3960: yod med gnyis las btsal byas na'ang //
NK076(mu)001:3961: de snyed lung ma bstan du 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:3962: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas la //
NK076(mu)001:3963: de min lta ba zlog pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:3964: mtha' bral 'das dang grol sogs su /
NK076(mu)001:3965: bla dwags tsam du brjod pa yin ces so //
NK076(mu)001:3966: rtogs pa'i tshad ni bden pa dbyer med skor cig
NK076(mu)001:3967: lhun gyis grub pa rang gi mtshan nyid du rtogs
NK076(mu)001:3968: nas rig pa yul med du gsal ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:3970: rang rig mngon sum dmigs bral bas //
NK076(mu)001:3971: rang gsal gsum bral mi 'gul bar //
NK076(mu)001:3972: nges par gdeng du gang byas pa //
NK076(mu)001:3973: thos bsam brtan pa'i lta mthar phyin /
NK076(mu)001:3975: de yang lam cig char ba'i skabs su gsal ba chig chod skyed dbyung du med par rtogs shing /
NK076(mu)001:3976: thod rgal ba'i skabs su de bas mi gsal bar rtogs la /
NK076(mu)001:3977: rim gyis pa'i skabs su na nga nas mi gsal bar rtogs lo //
NK076(mu)001:3978: 'o na rim ca ga char gnyis lta ba'i ngo bo la khyad yod dam med /
NK076(mu)001:3979: ce na kha cig rtogs tshab che chung yod ces zer ba ni 'thad pa ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:3980: myur bul tsam las rtogs pa rang gi ngo bo
NK076(mu)001:3981: la ni khyad par cung zad med do gsung ngo
NK076(mu)001:3982: // de ltar na'ang lam zag bcas kyi lta ba rang gi mtshan nyid mthong ngam mi mthong /
NK076(mu)001:3983: dang po ltar na zag med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:3984: rang mtshan mngon du byas pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:3988: de dag zag bcas bsam gtan te //
NK076(mu)001:3989: gnyis med yul dral de mthong yin //
NK076(mu)001:3992: spyi min rang gi mtshan nyid du /
NK076(mu)001:3993: rang rig mngon sum dmigs gnyis su bral bas /
NK076(mu)001:3994: rang gsal mtha' rgyud las grol /
NK076(mu)001:3996: sgra rten yid la byed min par //
NK076(mu)001:3997: rang rig mngon sum dmigs bral ba /
NK076(mu)001:4000: nus pa thob dang ma thob pa'i //
NK076(mu)001:4001: mthong lam gnyis su gyur pa yin /
NK076(mu)001:4002: zhes rang mtshan du mthong bar gsungs pa'i lung rnams ji ltar drang ngo zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4006: dang po kha sngags ram pa cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:4007: chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid zag bcas kyi skabs
NK076(mu)001:4008: su lta zhog gi /zag med kyi lam gsum du'ang
NK076(mu)001:4009: ma mthong ste / sangs rgyas nyag gcig gi spyod yul lo //
NK076(mu)001:4011: de ni rgyud dag pa kho na'i spyod yul brgyad
NK076(mu)001:4012: gyur du gyur gyi gangs dang sa la gnas pa
NK076(mu)001:4013: rnams kyis ni ma yin no //
NK076(mu)001:4015: zer ba ni mi rigs te /
NK076(mu)001:4016: legs pa'i lam gsum chos can //
NK076(mu)001:4018: nyon mongs sgrib pa ma spangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:4019: gang du chos nyid rang mtshan ma mthong pa la nyon sgribs ma spangs pas khyab cing /
NK076(mu)001:4020: nyon mongs pa dang bcas pa la 'khor bar bzlog pas khyab ste /
NK076(mu)001:4021: so so'i skye bo bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:4023: zag kun thad pa'i rigs can 'di //
NK076(mu)001:4024: ji ltar byas kyang bzlog pa med //
NK076(mu)001:4026: gong du mthong bar bshad pa'i lung du mas kyang gnod cing /
NK076(mu)001:4027: khyed nyid kyi lung yang lam du chos nyid rang
NK076(mu)001:4028: mtshan mi mthong pa la dgongs pa ma yin gyi
NK076(mu)001:4029: dus bzhi mnyam sbyor du ma gyur pa la dgongs
NK076(mu)001:4030: pa yin no // yang kha skyo cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:4031: zag bcas kyi ma rtogs na phar zhog /rtogs pa
NK076(mu)001:4032: re re shes na rang mtshan skyed du byar med
NK076(mu)001:4033: par mthong zhes zer ba ni shin tu'ang mi rigs
NK076(mu)001:4034: te / zag bcas kyi lam mtshon /
NK076(mu)001:4035: zag med mthong lam dang khyad med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:4036: rang mtshan skyed med du mthong ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4037: tshes gsum gyi zla ba bzhin 'dod na gsal lo //
NK076(mu)001:4038: yang nya ri ba kha cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:4039: zag bcas kyi skabs su dum bu bar mthong zag med kyi skabs su rgyun du mthong ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:4040: ces zer ba'ang mi rigs te /
NK076(mu)001:4041: dang po mthong lam la rang mtshan rtogs pa'i nges shes yod dam med /
NK076(mu)001:4043: bden mthong gyi byed chos ma grub la /
NK076(mu)001:4046: rang mtshan la nges shes skyes pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4047: sa dang po'i bden pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:4048: 'dod na dum bu ba'i khyad par bud de /
NK076(mu)001:4050: rang gsal gsum bral mi sgul bas //
NK076(mu)001:4051: nges par steng du gang byas par //
NK076(mu)001:4052: thos bsam brten pa'i lta mthar phyin //
NK076(mu)001:4053: ces nges shes yod cing rkyen dbang du mi 'gyur bar bshad pa dang 'gal lo //
NK076(mu)001:4054: zag med mthong lam nyid du'ang rgyun du mthong zhes kyang brjod par mi nus te /
NK076(mu)001:4055: ngang du bsgom pa'i lam gyis da gzod rgyun bsring
NK076(mu)001:4056: zhing mnyam rjes gnyis med du slob dgos pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:4058: gsang thos gsang rigs bsgom sbyor bas //
NK076(mu)001:4059: dkyus sar phyin pa'i cang shes bzhin //
NK076(mu)001:4060: kun tu 'gro ba bdag po'i don //
NK076(mu)001:4062: yang kha 'dar nag cig na re //
NK076(mu)001:4063: zag bcas kyi skabs su rang gi mtshan nyid rang rig pa'i mngon sum du mthong zhing /
NK076(mu)001:4064: zag med du rnal 'byor gyi mngon sum du mthong ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:4065: zhes zer na'ang re zhig 'thad 'thad 'dra na'ang rigs pa ni ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:4067: rgyu 'bras dus gcig rdzogs pa yi //
NK076(mu)001:4068: rang rang nyid du dbang thob ste //
NK076(mu)001:4069: don mthong 'jug pa mthar phyin lam //
NK076(mu)001:4070: mthong ba'i chos la mya ngan 'das //
NK076(mu)001:4071: ces tshe dbang gi bden pa rang rig gi mngon
NK076(mu)001:4072: gsum du mthong bar gsungs pa nyid spangs bar mi
NK076(mu)001:4073: nus so // bdag gi bla ma rog ni zag bcas kyi skabs su /
NK076(mu)001:4074: rang gi mtshan nyid du mthong ni mthong la /
NK076(mu)001:4075: mthong lugs kyi khyad par yod de /
NK076(mu)001:4076: zag med mthong lam la ltos nas mi gsal ba'am /
NK076(mu)001:4077: nus pa mthong pa'i tshul du mthong gsung /
NK076(mu)001:4078: de ltar na'ang zag med dang khyad med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:4079: rang mtshan mthong ba'i phyir ro zhes pa'am /
NK076(mu)001:4081: mthong ba tsam gyi phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:4082: nus thob du mthong pa'i phyir zer /
NK076(mu)001:4083: dang po khyab pa med cing /
NK076(mu)001:4084: gnyis pa'i rtags ma grub ces gsungs pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:4085: bla ma'i gsung la gces spras byas pa tsam yin legs pa dkar yang mi sems te /
NK076(mu)001:4086: lta ba zag bcas dang chos nyid rang rang mtshan
NK076(mu)001:4087: gnyis mngon 'gyur 'gal chos su gnas pa'i phyir ro
NK076(mu)001:4088: // rang lugs kyi lan ni rnam par dbyer phye nas 'debs te /
NK076(mu)001:4089: spyir lta ba'i skabs su chos nyid rang mtshan du mthong ngam ma mthong zer ram /
NK076(mu)001:4090: bye brag du zag bcas lta ba'i skabs su mthong
NK076(mu)001:4091: ngam ma mthong zer dang po ltar na mthong ba'ang
NK076(mu)001:4092: yod de dbang po rnon po'i yang rab de nyid
NK076(mu)001:4093: thos bsam gyi lta thog nas grol ba dgag mi
NK076(mu)001:4096: ye nas dbyings su ro cig pas //
NK076(mu)001:4097: rkyen gyi rdul gyi ga la 'go /de la nga
NK076(mu)001:4098: dang bdag mi rtog /shes rab mchog gi de ltar
NK076(mu)001:4100: gzhan yang lta ba ni zag bcas kho nar rnam par bcas pa min pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4101: 'ga' zhig du rang mtshan mthong ba mi 'gal te /
NK076(mu)001:4103: lta ba lta bar gtsor brjod mod //
NK076(mu)001:4104: don du shes rab kun mnyam nyid //
NK076(mu)001:4105: ded dpon rin chen ji bzhin du //
NK076(mu)001:4106: gdod mtha'i bar du 'di shes dgos //
NK076(mu)001:4108: gnyis pa ltar na ni ma mthong ste /
NK076(mu)001:4109: dbang po rab kyi 'bring man chad kyis zag bcas
NK076(mu)001:4110: kyi skabs su thos pa'i sgra spyi la brten nas
NK076(mu)001:4111: bsam shes kyis lta ba don spyir rtogs te /
NK076(mu)001:4112: zag bcas zhi gnas kyi ting nge la 'dris par
NK076(mu)001:4113: bslabs pas zag med du rang mtshan nyid ngo bo
NK076(mu)001:4114: bskyed du byar med par mthong la /
NK076(mu)001:4115: de nas sangs rgyas kyi sa'i bar du phra ba'i
NK076(mu)001:4116: sgrib pa rim gyis spangs te gsal ba'i khyad par
NK076(mu)001:4117: bskyed du byas shing mkhyen pa'i ye shes dus bzhi
NK076(mu)001:4118: mnyam sbyor bskyed du byar med pa mngon du gyur
NK076(mu)001:4119: pa nyid do // ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:4121: nye ring drung bzhin stobs 'phel ba //
NK076(mu)001:4123: gsal ba'i bye brag rim par 'gro //
NK076(mu)001:4124: de chas skabs min brjod dngos gcig ces gsungs shing /
NK076(mu)001:4125: dbyer med chig chod du rtogs par ma nus pas
NK076(mu)001:4126: lta ba'i rnam grangs tha dad kyis lam rang rang
NK076(mu)001:4127: gi skabs su spros pa gcod pa nyid de /
NK076(mu)001:4129: ye shes kun mkhyen lha grangs dgu /rnal 'byor rim pa'i rgyud las skyes //
NK076(mu)001:4130: de bas shes rab gsum la 'bod //
NK076(mu)001:4131: rgyud don gzungs kyis zin pa yin //
NK076(mu)001:4133: de bas na zag bcas kyi lam skabs 'di chos can /
NK076(mu)001:4134: chos nyid rang mtshan du mthong ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:4135: kun brtags spangs pa'i gnyen po mthong lam chen po nyid rgyud la ma brten pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4136: thun mongs kyi sbyor lam bzhin ces 'bras rtags zlog khyab kyis khegs pa yin no //
NK076(mu)001:4137: de ltar na'ang sngar gyi spyi des dgos la khyab bam ma khyab /
NK076(mu)001:4138: gnyis pa ltar na lta ba la rigs spyi khegs par 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)001:4139: dang po ltar na zag bcas su'ang rang mtshan rtogs par mi 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4140: ma yin te 'dir rigs kyi bye brag khegs pas spyi mi dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:4142: rtogs ma rtogs kyi skyon yon ni 'khor bar zlog mi zlog khyad par du byed de /
NK076(mu)001:4144: spyan bzang lam zhugs ji bzhin phyir //
NK076(mu)001:4145: che kun zag cing 'ching ba'i rgyu //
NK076(mu)001:4149: dngos grub mchog gi snying po ste /
NK076(mu)001:4150: chu srin phyag rgya ji bzhin du //
NK076(mu)001:4151: dang po'i mthar rtogs don mi mthong zhes gsungs so //
NK076(mu)001:4152: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin la gnyis ste /
NK076(mu)001:4154: nges pa yongs rdzogs su bsgom pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:4159: dang po ni mos pa yul du byed yid shes pa bzang rtog gi rnam pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:4161: lam kun skad cig chas bsgoms nas //
NK076(mu)001:4162: spros pa'i 'khor lo mos bsgom zhing //
NK076(mu)001:4164: bslab tshul ni thun gcig gi nang du ya tha
NK076(mu)001:4165: bsrung 'khor nas ma tha go bgo lus bsrung yan
NK076(mu)001:4166: mos pa tsam re rdzogs par lag tu len pa
NK076(mu)001:4168: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la //
NK076(mu)001:4169: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK076(mu)001:4170: phyogs dus kun nas bder gshegs yi //
NK076(mu)001:4171: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rab du rdzogs //
NK076(mu)001:4172: nye bar gyur pa'i dam tshig mchog /ces so //
NK076(mu)001:4174: rang don du bsod nams kyi tshogs khyad par can
NK076(mu)001:4175: rdzogs par 'gyur ba'i nus pas rgyud nas nges pa
NK076(mu)001:4176: yongs rdzogs kyi lam rgyud la skye zhing /
NK076(mu)001:4177: gzhan don 'phrin las kyi nus pa'i mi bslu bar 'byung ste /
NK076(mu)001:4179: nus pa'i byin ldan rdzogs par byed /
NK076(mu)001:4182: skabs 'di nyid du skyed rim lha'i rnam pa don spyi yul du byed pas sgom mam /
NK076(mu)001:4183: rang mtshan yul du byed pa'i tshul gyis bsgom /
NK076(mu)001:4184: dang po ltar na lam bsgoms pa don med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:4185: don spyi'i mtshan nyid ni mi gsal don byed mi nus pa'i bsgro btags dngos med yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4186: dga' ldan gyi lo rgyus thos pa'i yid shes bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:4187: gnyis pa ltar na nges pa yongs rdzogs dang khyad par med par 'gyur zhing /
NK076(mu)001:4188: bskyed tsam gyis lha'i zhal mthong ba yang thal te /
NK076(mu)001:4189: rang mtshan gyi mtshan nyid gsal la don byed nus pa'i dngos po can yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:4190: mig gis gzugs mngon sum du mthong pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:4192: lan ni 'dir rtogs pa kho na bas lha'i don spyi yul du byed do //
NK076(mu)001:4193: don byed mi nus pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4194: bsgoms pa don med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:4196: de'i mthong ba nyid kyi don byed mi nus pa'i phyir zer tam /
NK076(mu)001:4197: mthong bar byed pa'i don byed mi nus pa'i phyir zer /
NK076(mu)001:4198: dang po'i rtags ma grub cing /
NK076(mu)001:4199: gnyis yi khyab pa ma grub ces bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:4200: nges pa yongs rdzogs la gsum ste //
NK076(mu)001:4204: so sor dbye ba'i don no //
NK076(mu)001:4205: dang po ni lam po ting nge mthar phyin pa'i slob pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:4207: de bzhin nyid du mthong goms na //
NK076(mu)001:4208: rnam rtog mtshan mar yongs mi 'dzin //
NK076(mu)001:4209: bde dang mi bde gnyis med pas //
NK076(mu)001:4210: thams cad dbyer med ye shes yin ces pa'i don no //
NK076(mu)001:4211: blo rim ni de ting lta bu la mthar phyin
NK076(mu)001:4212: pa'i nyams skyes skyes su bsgoms nas mthar phyin pa
NK076(mu)001:4213: dang / lam phyi ma ye shes sgyu ma la sbyor te de nas rim pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:4215: sngon du gtong goms rnal 'byor pas 'di nyid rgyu thar sngon bya zhing /
NK076(mu)001:4217: skye tshul brten gyi khyad par ni /
NK076(mu)001:4218: rim pa ma spangs par sangs rgyas kyi sa la bgrod pa thar chags pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4219: rim pa spangs te sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'gro ba thod rgal ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:4220: so so'i dang por thar chags zag bcas kyi lam la lnga ste /
NK076(mu)001:4221: stong pa chen po'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK076(mu)001:4225: bar chad med pa'i lam du tshogs bsgrub pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:4226: dang por de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la chos brgyad //
NK076(mu)001:4227: zhar la 'byung ba gnyis te bcu'o //
NK076(mu)001:4231: bya ba'i spyod pa ci byed pa //
NK076(mu)001:4232: sgom bya'i ngo bo gang yin pa //
NK076(mu)001:4233: mtshan nyid theg pa'i sa lam dang sbyar ba /
NK076(mu)001:4236: rang gi 'bras bu dang brgyad do //
NK076(mu)001:4237: gnyis pa ni dogs pa bsal ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:4239: dang por gzhi gang dang sbyar na shi ba'i 'od gsal dang chos mthun te /
NK076(mu)001:4240: lam rim shi ba don dam bden pa ste zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:4241: khyad par gyi dgos pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:4242: mtshan nyid kyi rtog pa dag par byed pa'i chos
NK076(mu)001:4243: kyi sku'i rtog pa rgyu mthun du sgrub pa ste
NK076(mu)001:4244: / mun lam rim snang 'gyur ba'i tshul bzhin du //
NK076(mu)001:4246: don du gnyer ba'i rnam grangs kun //
NK076(mu)001:4250: mi dmigs pa'i spyod pa byed de //
NK076(mu)001:4251: bya ba med las byar med byas //
NK076(mu)001:4253: bsgom pa'i ngo bo ni mi rtog pa la blo gnas pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:4254: lam rim de yang 'du shes kun bral ting nge 'dzin mchog ces so //
NK076(mu)001:4255: mtshan nyid theg pa'i sa lam dang sbyar na /
NK076(mu)001:4256: lam gyi dang po tshogs lam /
NK076(mu)001:4257: de las kyang chung ngur dran pa nyer bzhag bzhi dang mo tshod 'thun te /
NK076(mu)001:4258: lam rim de yang ma 'gag mi 'dzin tshogs gnyis ldan zhes so /
NK076(mu)001:4260: lam rim ngo bo bzhin tu grangs 'jug ste /
NK076(mu)001:4266: ma bcos lhun grub de bzhin nyid ces sam /
NK076(mu)001:4267: ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid /
NK076(mu)001:4268: lhun gyis grub pa'i de bzhin nyid /
NK076(mu)001:4269: mnyam pa nyid kyi de bzhin nyid do /
NK076(mu)001:4270: khungs ni dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pas /
NK076(mu)001:4271: rtog pa smra bsam yul las 'das ces so //
NK076(mu)001:4272: 'bras bu ni brgyud nas chos sku thob ste /
NK076(mu)001:4273: sngon byas pa'i chos skur sbyor zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:4274: log rtog bsal ba la gnyis las /
NK076(mu)001:4275: bsgom bya'i ngo bo la log par rtog pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:4276: kha cig de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge'i skabs 'dir
NK076(mu)001:4277: dbyer lam rim med sgom zer ba ni mi 'thad
NK076(mu)001:4279: lam rim don dam kun gyi rgyu yin phyir //
NK076(mu)001:4280: ltag pa'i rgyu de dang por bsgom //
NK076(mu)001:4282: man rgyud nas ngag las kyang /
NK076(mu)001:4283: rnam pa kun du stong chen mthong /
NK076(mu)001:4286: de ting gi skabs su dbyer med bsgoms nas dbyer
NK076(mu)001:4287: med la nyams mthar phyin par slob bam mi slob
NK076(mu)001:4289: g.yo ldan smin 'jug mthar phyir pa //
NK076(mu)001:4290: lnga yis yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:4292: dang po ltar na snying rje sgyu ma don du med tha la /
NK076(mu)001:4293: de stong nyid du dbyer med mthar phyin par slob nus pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4294: phyag rgya gcig pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:4295: don med kyang sgom na lam pa nyid 'khrul par 'gyur zhing /
NK076(mu)001:4296: don med kyang mi bsgom na gzhung dang 'gal ba nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:4297: gnyis pa 'bras bu la log par rtogs pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:4298: kha cig nges par 'di nyid kyis chos sku thob ces zer ba ni mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:4299: snying rje sgyu ma man chad bsgoms pas don med du 'gyur zhing /
NK076(mu)001:4300: lung las phyogs mthun brjod kyi ris ma yin /
NK076(mu)001:4304: spyi lam 'og ma bas gong ma bzang ba ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:4305: de ltar na'ang lta ba las de bzhin nyid ngan du gyur par thal /
NK076(mu)001:4306: sngar dbyer med du rtogs kyang 'dir don dam brkyang pa las mngon du mi byed pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4307: 'bras chang dor nas chu nyug la spyod pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:4308: 'dod na gong ma bzang ba nyid nyams pa ma yin tam zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4309: de'i skyon med de lta ba'i dus su dbyer med rtog pa'i gams pa rgyud la /
NK076(mu)001:4311: 'dir khyad par du bden pa chig chod du goms
NK076(mu)001:4312: ma nus pas kha khral nas bsgoms pa yin zhes
NK076(mu)001:4313: bdag gi bla ma gsung la /
NK076(mu)001:4314: bdag ni rims kyis dbang btsan du lta ba don
NK076(mu)001:4315: spyir rtogs pa de nyid rang mtshan rtogs par byed
NK076(mu)001:4316: pa'i thab ting nge 'dzin la rims kyis zhugs pa
NK076(mu)001:4317: nyid yar lngan snyams sems so //
NK076(mu)001:4318: yang gnyis pa de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge'i skabs su 'bras bu don dam bsgom mam mi bsgom /
NK076(mu)001:4319: dang po ltar na stong ldog rkyang pa nyid bsgom mam /
NK076(mu)001:4321: dang po ltar na phyogs gcig pa'i myang 'das su 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)001:4322: gnyis pa ltar na phyag rgya gcig pa dang khyad med du thal te /
NK076(mu)001:4323: dbyer me du bsgom pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:4324: gnyis pa ltar na mi bsgom na'ang gsang sngags 'bras
NK076(mu)001:4325: bu la lam du byed pa ma yin par 'gyur
NK076(mu)001:4326: zhing / lung las kyang mdun dang gsum phyir don
NK076(mu)001:4327: dam las tsas bsgom par gsungs pa dang 'gal zhe
NK076(mu)001:4328: zhing / na / lan ni 'bras bu don dam
NK076(mu)001:4329: nyid bsgom zhing 'dir skabs don du stong pa gtso
NK076(mu)001:4330: bo'i dmigs yul du bsgom mod kyi /
NK076(mu)001:4331: des phyogs gcig pa'i myang 'das nyid lam du byed par yang mi 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:4332: 'dir rnam pa kun ldan gyi stong pa nyid sgom pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:4333: yang gsum pa 'dir gsang sngags pa 'bras bu lam du byed de /
NK076(mu)001:4334: smin nas kyang lam du byed pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4335: 'dod na gsang sngags nyid de ring lam du thal /
NK076(mu)001:4336: khyab pa ni mthar bskyed du med phyi mtha'o zhes so /
NK076(mu)001:4337: thug lam gyi 'bras bur bshad pa'i rang rgyud kyi lung gi grub bo //
NK076(mu)001:4338: gnyis pa ltar na 'bras bu ma yin par thal te //
NK076(mu)001:4339: ma smin pa'i phyir 'dod na rang tshig nyams na
NK076(mu)001:4340: gang ma smin pa la mthar thug gi 'bras bu
NK076(mu)001:4341: ma yin pas khyab ste myu gu sngon po bzhin
NK076(mu)001:4342: zhe na / lan ni thob bya don gyi ngo bo rang la gnas kyang //
NK076(mu)001:4343: de nyid mi gsal gsal ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:4344: mngon du ma gyur pa gyur pa rtsam la lam du byed ces 'dogs pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:4346: de lam rim ltar ye shes rang gnas dang //
NK076(mu)001:4347: lam dang 'bras bu kun ngo bo //
NK076(mu)001:4348: 'brel pa bdag phyir thabs chen pos //
NK076(mu)001:4349: mngon byed rang las 'byung bar zad //
NK076(mu)001:4351: de ltar na'ang lam gyis mngon du byas thos pa'i
NK076(mu)001:4352: tshe sngar gyi 'bras bu la bskyed byung ngam ma
NK076(mu)001:4353: byung zhe na / de rtsam du dngul rdo la
NK076(mu)001:4354: bzhu brtul byas pa'i tshe sngar gyi dngul de las
NK076(mu)001:4355: bskyed byung ngam ma byung zhes dri /
NK076(mu)001:4356: ngo bo la bskyed du byar med kyis mngon gsal
NK076(mu)001:4357: khyad par dngul gyi rang mdog du gyur pas bskyed
NK076(mu)001:4359: 'dir yang ngo bo la bskyed du byar med kyis
NK076(mu)001:4360: mngon gsal gyi khyad par 'bras bu'i rang mtshan mngon
NK076(mu)001:4361: du gyur pas bskyed du byas pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:4362: de ltar na ngo bo la bltos nas lam gyi 'bad pa don med du thal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:4363: mngon gsal la ltos na 'bras bu rgyu med las skyes par thal lo zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4364: der yang ngo bo la ltos nas gzhu brtul gi 'bad pa don med du thal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:4365: mngon gsal la ltos na dngul 'bras rgyu med las
NK076(mu)001:4366: thal zhes mtshungs pa nyid du mgo 'dre bar 'gyur
NK076(mu)001:4367: ro // snying rje sgyu ma las chos bcu las /
NK076(mu)001:4368: dang por gzhi gang dang sbyar na //
NK076(mu)001:4369: srid pa bar ma do dang chos mthun te //
NK076(mu)001:4370: lam rim skye ba bar ma kun rdzob yin zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:4371: khyad par gyi dgos pa ni //
NK076(mu)001:4372: chos bdag gam stong 'dzin gyi 'chings ba las dgrol ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:4373: bden pa phyogs gcig par mi btang zhing rgya gcig gi rgyur bya ba'i phyir te //
NK076(mu)001:4374: lam rim bdag nyid dri ma bsal ba dang //
NK076(mu)001:4375: stong pa'i mdud pa gzhig pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:4376: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rgyur bya zhing //
NK076(mu)001:4378: bden pa ris su mi btang phyir //
NK076(mu)001:4380: bya ba'i spyod pa ni shes rab dang mthun pa'i spyod pa byed de /
NK076(mu)001:4381: lam rim snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK076(mu)001:4382: srid gsum sgyu ma 'dra bar ni //
NK076(mu)001:4384: bsgom bya'i ngo bo ni ye shes sgyu ma'i snying rje bskyed pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:4385: lam rim rang rig ye shes snying rje gzig sa ces so //
NK076(mu)001:4386: mtshan nyid theg pa'i sa lam dang sbyar nas tshogs
NK076(mu)001:4387: lam 'bring po yang dag par spong ba dang lam
NK076(mu)001:4388: tshod snyam mo // ting 'dzin dpyad dbye na drug ste /
NK076(mu)001:4390: sgyu ma mig yor sprul pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:4391: smis rgyu 'ja' tshon chu zla bzhin /
NK076(mu)001:4395: dngos po sgyu ma gsum ni 'khor ba'i chos la ltos nas phye /
NK076(mu)001:4396: thabs sgyu ma phyag rgya sgyu ma /
NK076(mu)001:4397: ye shes sgyu ma gsum ni 'das pa'i chos la ltos nas phye ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:4399: snying po stong pa nyid du rab gsal bas //
NK076(mu)001:4400: snying rje'i yul ni bsgom par bya zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:4401: 'bras bu ni brgyud nas longs sku thob pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:4402: lam 'dir cha rkyen rdzogs bsgrub na //
NK076(mu)001:4403: mtshan dang dpe byad kun dang ldan //
NK076(mu)001:4404: dbang phyug chen po'i gnas nyid du //
NK076(mu)001:4405: sngon du 'byung par the tshom med ces so //
NK076(mu)001:4406: log rtog bsal ba la gnyis las /
NK076(mu)001:4407: ngo bo la log par rtog pa ni kha cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:4408: snying rje sgyu ma'i skabs su dbyer med bsgom zer ba ni mi 'thad de //
NK076(mu)001:4411: thams cad sgyu ma mig yor dang //
NK076(mu)001:4412: sprul pa'i tshul du bsgom par bya //
NK076(mu)001:4414: man ngag las lam rim kyang /
NK076(mu)001:4415: skye ba bar ma kun rdzob yin //
NK076(mu)001:4417: rigs pa'i 'gal ba yang gong dang mtshungs so //
NK076(mu)001:4418: gnyis pa 'bras bu la log par rtogs pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:4419: 'dir dngos su longs sku 'thob zer ba ni mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:4420: phyag rgya ga cig pa man chad bsgoms pa don med du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4421: 'dir yang chos mthun brtsis pa'am brgyud pa'i rgyu yin gsung /
NK076(mu)001:4422: brtsod pa spang pa la bzhi las /
NK076(mu)001:4423: dang po ni snying rje sgyu ma'i skabs su spyi
NK076(mu)001:4424: lugs kyis lam 'og ma bas gong ma bzang ba
NK076(mu)001:4425: min te / min na lam gong du bgrod pa don med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:4426: gong ma bzang ba yin na don dam pas kyang kun rdzob bzang bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:4427: gong ma kun rdzob snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor 'di yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:4428: 'dod na sam b+h+ri ta'i sgra las drangs nas ngan pa'am bslu ba'i chos can du gsal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4429: lan ni kun rdzob rtsam po bzang por thal zer ram //
NK076(mu)001:4430: lhag pa'i kun rdzob bzang por thal zer /
NK076(mu)001:4431: dang po'i rtags ma grub cing /
NK076(mu)001:4432: gnyis pa ni 'dod pa kho na'o //
NK076(mu)001:4433: de lta na'ang theg pa spyi lugs dang 'gal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4434: ma yin te theg pa spyi lugs kyis sems can
NK076(mu)001:4435: rnams bdag tu 'dzin pa'i dngos po la zhen pa
NK076(mu)001:4436: spang pa'i gnyen po don dam stong nyid yin pas
NK076(mu)001:4438: 'dir stong nyid snying po phyogs gcig pa'i rten rtogs
NK076(mu)001:4439: 'jig par byed pa lhag pa'i kun rdzob yin pa'i
NK076(mu)001:4440: phyir de bas kyang bzang po nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:4441: yang lam gong ma'i don rnams kyang brgyud la ldan na /
NK076(mu)001:4442: de'i steng du'ang lhag pa'i kun rdzob bsgom nus pas yon tan yar ldan yin te /
NK076(mu)001:4444: snga ma snga ma rgyud ldan pas //
NK076(mu)001:4445: phyi ma phyi ma gsal bar byed //
NK076(mu)001:4447: yang gnyis pa 'dir sgyu ma'i chos drug las /
NK076(mu)001:4448: log rtog dang rten 'brel sgyu ma bsgom mam mi bsgom /
NK076(mu)001:4449: gnyis pa ltar na sgyu ma'i chos drug bsgom par gsungs pa dang 'gal zhing //
NK076(mu)001:4450: snying rje sgyu ma'i khyab bya yang ma yin par 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)001:4451: dang po ltar na nges grol lam mi grol /
NK076(mu)001:4452: mi grol na bsgoms pa don med du thal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:4453: grol na sems can thams cad 'bad med du grol bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:4454: log rtog dang rten 'brel bsgom pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4455: len du kha cig na re de gnyis ni shes nas spang bar bya ba yin gyi /
NK076(mu)001:4456: ting nge yul du bsgrub par bya ba ma yin
NK076(mu)001:4457: pa'i phyir khyab pa ma grub ces zer mod kyi
NK076(mu)001:4458: / bdag ni log rtog rten 'brel rang brgyud pa bsgom pa'i phyir zer ram /
NK076(mu)001:4459: sgyu mar bsgom pa'i phyir zer /
NK076(mu)001:4460: dang po'i rtags ma grub cing gnyis pa'i khyab pa med do //
NK076(mu)001:4461: yang 3kun du snang gi ting nge 'dir sngar gyi
NK076(mu)001:4462: de ting dang ldan nam mi ldan dang po ltar
NK076(mu)001:4463: na 'di nyid du dbyer med bsgom nus par thal
NK076(mu)001:4464: / rgyud ga cig la ting nge 'dzin gnyis char mtshungs pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4465: chu dang 'o ma 'dres pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:4466: gnyis pa ltar na snying rje chen po ma yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:4467: de bzhin nyid kyi rtogs pas spangs pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4468: byams pa'i snying rje bzhin zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4469: len du de bzhin nyid spang pa ni ma yin gyi /
NK076(mu)001:4470: gtso bor snying rje sgyu ma la dmigs nas slob par byed de /
NK076(mu)001:4471: de bzhin nyid phal par gnas pas dngos shugs kyis
NK076(mu)001:4472: goms pa las mngon gyur dbyer med du rtogs pa
NK076(mu)001:4473: med cing / de tsam gyis phyag rgya gcig pa dang khyad par med par yang mi 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:4474: da dung rtog pa ltar ma bskyed pa'i phyir ro zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:4475: yang 4 sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor 'dir rtog tshogs ltar bsgom mam mi bsgom /
NK076(mu)001:4476: dang po ltar na gcig spros dang khyad med du 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)001:4477: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag kun //
NK076(mu)001:4478: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lngar grags rtsog ces pa /
NK076(mu)001:4479: gnyis pa ltar na lhag pa'i kun rdzob 'di'i 'jug yul ma yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:4481: khyab pa ma grub na dam bca' nyams pa nyid ma yin nam zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4482: bden mod kyi spyi'i 'jug yul du bsgom mi bsgom zer ram /
NK076(mu)001:4483: khyad par du bskyed nas bsgom mam mi bsgom zer /
NK076(mu)001:4485: lam rim bzhi rdzogs phyag rgya ma 'dres gsal zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:4486: des gcig spros dang khyad med du'ang mi 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:4487: bskyed thabs kyis mngon du ma byas pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:4488: gnyis pa ltar mi bsgom ste ting nge phyi ma dag la ltos pas so //
NK076(mu)001:4489: de ltar na'ang snga ltar gsal ba la ltos nas
NK076(mu)001:4490: phyi ma khyad par du bskyed pa don med du
NK076(mu)001:4492: ma yin te rtog tshogs rags pa ci rigs su bsgyur kyang /
NK076(mu)001:4493: mngal dang rdzas te skye ba'i bag chags 'phra mo
NK076(mu)001:4494: sbyang pa'i phyir don yod dam snyam du sems te
NK076(mu)001:4495: dngul legs par dpyad dgos so //
NK076(mu)001:4496: phyag rgya gcig pa la chos bcu las /
NK076(mu)001:4497: dang po gzhi gang dang sbyar na /
NK076(mu)001:4498: rim pa dang cig char gyis lus grub cing skyes pa dang sbyar te /
NK076(mu)001:4499: skyes pa'i rim gsum gnyis med don zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:4500: khyad par gyi dgos pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:4501: bden gnyis tha dad du zhen pa dgag cing /
NK076(mu)001:4502: dbyer med du bya ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:4503: rang gzhan gyi don du rtog tshogs ltar bsgyur zhing spros pa'i rgyur bya ba'i phyir te /
NK076(mu)001:4504: 'bras bu yongs su rdzogs bya zhing //
NK076(mu)001:4505: spros pa'i rgyu yis thob pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:4506: rgyu stong zhen dbang du bya dang //
NK076(mu)001:4507: rtog pa'i phung stsogs gnas bsgyur zhing //
NK076(mu)001:4508: gzhan dag smin par bya ba'i phyir zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:4510: bya ba spangs pa rnal 'byor gyi spyod pa byed ste /
NK076(mu)001:4511: bya min las kun dor bya ste zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:4512: sgoms bya'i ngo bo ni lha'i sku snang stong dbyer med dam /
NK076(mu)001:4513: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa //
NK076(mu)001:4514: h+aum las skyes pa'i ye shes gzugs //
NK076(mu)001:4516: mtshan nyid theg pa'i sa lam dang sbyar na tshogs
NK076(mu)001:4517: lam chen po'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang
NK076(mu)001:4519: ting nge'i dbye ba la gnyis las /
NK076(mu)001:4520: don gyi phyag rgya ga cig pa ni bden pa dbyer med rang gi mtshan nyid du rtogs pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:4521: rtags kyi phyag rgya gcig pa ni lha'i sku phyag rgya gcig du bsgoms pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:4522: zhi ba rgyan gcig pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4523: khro bo rgyan ga cig pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:4525: mkha' dkyil dag pa'i dbyings nyi zla //
NK076(mu)001:4526: ye shes rgyal ba stangs dpyal bsgom //
NK076(mu)001:4528: 'bras bu ni brgyud nas yi ge 'khor lo sprul pa'i sku thob ste /
NK076(mu)001:4529: rnal 'byor las su rung rnams kyis //
NK076(mu)001:4530: phyag rgya chen po rdzogs 'gyur zhing //
NK076(mu)001:4531: gsal la yid gnyis med pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:4535: 'bras bu log rtog bsal ba gong dang 'dra //
NK076(mu)001:4537: rtsod pa spang pa ni gsum las //
NK076(mu)001:4538: dang po ni phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs su lhag pa'i lha dgu bsgom mam mi bsgom /
NK076(mu)001:4540: spyi mgrin tsi ta'i gnas gsum du /
NK076(mu)001:4541: byin brlabs rdo rje gsum bsgom bya ces pa dang 'gal lo //
NK076(mu)001:4542: dang po ltar na phyag rgya ga cig pa ma yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:4543: lha nyid dgu dang bcu sgom pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4544: lan du yan lag gi lha bsgom /
NK076(mu)001:4545: phyag rgya ga cig pa ma yin par thal lo //
NK076(mu)001:4546: lha du ma bsgoms pa'i phyir zhe na //
NK076(mu)001:4547: rtsa ba'i lha du ma bsgom pa'i phyir zer ram /
NK076(mu)001:4548: yan lag gi lha du ma bsgom pa'i phyir zer /
NK076(mu)001:4549: dang po ltar na gtan tshigs ma grub la /
NK076(mu)001:4550: gnyis pa ltar na yan lag gi lha du ma
NK076(mu)001:4551: bsgoms kyang rtsa ba'i lha gcig las mi bsgom pas
NK076(mu)001:4552: phyag rgya gcig par 'gro na ci ste khyab pa
NK076(mu)001:4553: med do // shing gi sdong po bzhin zhes gsung ngo //
NK076(mu)001:4554: yang chos gcig gi de bzhin nyid shes na chos
NK076(mu)001:4555: thams cad kyi mdo dang rgyas pa shes pa ma
NK076(mu)001:4556: yin nam / min na gzugs kyang bzhin nyid shes
NK076(mu)001:4557: na chos thams cad kyi mdo dang rgyas pa shes
NK076(mu)001:4559: yang rig spyir kun kyang de ltar shes ces pa dang 'gal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:4561: phyag rgya gcig pas lha'i sku snang stong gnyis med
NK076(mu)001:4562: du shes pas lha gzhan gyis shes sam mi shes
NK076(mu)001:4563: / mi shes na ga cig shes pas kun shes pa bud la /
NK076(mu)001:4564: shes na spros bcas sgom pa don med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:4567: lha gcig gi mtshan nyid nges pas lha kun gyi mtshan nges pa'i blos shes so //
NK076(mu)001:4568: spros pa sgom pa don med du thal te /
NK076(mu)001:4570: mtshan nyid nges pa'i blos shes kyang tshad la goms pas ma khyab pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:4571: dngos po nges pa'i blos sgom na ci te khyab pa med do //
NK076(mu)001:4572: 'o na mtshan nyid shes kyang dngos po nges pas mi shes pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4573: de na sgros 'dogs spyi sgrubs la gcod pa dang
NK076(mu)001:4574: bye brag la gcod pa'i khyad par te gser gyi
NK076(mu)001:4575: rang bzhin dang / bzo'i bye brag bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:4576: yang lha'i sku phyag rgya ga cig pa de snang pa bsgom mam /
NK076(mu)001:4577: snang ba rang bzhin med pa bsgom la /
NK076(mu)001:4578: dang po ltar na kun rdzob dang khyad par med du 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)001:4579: gnyis pa ltar na ye gdod ma nas 'jug pa'i cig char ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:4581: snang stong gnyis med sgom pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4582: lan mi nyag kha cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:4583: khyab pa med te cig char ba'i brten med kyi dbyer me sgom la /
NK076(mu)001:4584: 'dir ni rten can gyi dbyer med bsgom pas so ces zer mod kyi /
NK076(mu)001:4586: 'dir ting nge 'dzin gzhan la sngon du slob la /
NK076(mu)001:4587: cig char ba gzhan la spyi slob pa khyad par che'o gsung /
NK076(mu)001:4588: phyag rgya spros pa la'ang bcu las /
NK076(mu)001:4589: dang por gzhi gang dang sbyar na lus rgyas rkang
NK076(mu)001:4590: rdzong nas bu tsha 'dab rgyas pa dang sbyar te
NK076(mu)001:4591: / rkyen ldan bu sogs rgyas pa des //
NK076(mu)001:4592: rigs la sogs pa rgyas par byed //
NK076(mu)001:4594: khyad par gyi dgos pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:4595: lha gcig du zhen pa dgrol zhing du mar bsgoms pas bye brag gi rtog pa bzlog pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4596: spros pa nyid mthar phyin pas tshogs sgrub kyi rgyur
NK076(mu)001:4597: 'gyur zhing dngos grub gnyis 'grub par byed pa ste
NK076(mu)001:4598: / bsod nams yongs su rdzogs bya zhing //
NK076(mu)001:4599: spyod yul byin gyis brlabs pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:4600: 'khor lo sa mthar dbyung pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:4601: tshogs la dus kyi bsgrub pa'i phyir zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:4602: bya ba'i spyod pa ni spros bcas kyi spyod pa byed de /
NK076(mu)001:4603: spyod yul mthong thos thams cad kun //
NK076(mu)001:4606: ma nyams pa yi dbyings na gnas //
NK076(mu)001:4607: shes rab mchog gis rtag tu dpyad //
NK076(mu)001:4610: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i lha du ma bsgom pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:4611: de phyir bden gnyis dbye ba med //
NK076(mu)001:4612: phyi nang snod bcud ye nas dag /ces so //
NK076(mu)001:4613: mtshan nyid theg pa'i lam dang sbyar na /
NK076(mu)001:4614: sbyor lam chung ngu drod bzod rtse dpyad /
NK076(mu)001:4615: gnyis dang mo tshong mnyam mo //
NK076(mu)001:4617: rang bzhin phyag rgya spros pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4618: lam phyag rgya spros pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4620: dang po ni rtog tshogs lha'i dal du ye nas gnas pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:4621: phyi ma ni 'og min gyi gnas na yi ge
NK076(mu)001:4622: 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa sangs rgyas du ma
NK076(mu)001:4623: snyed gnas so // bar ma lam phyag rgya spros pa la gnyis ste //
NK076(mu)001:4625: dang po la 'khor lo tshom bu zhal phyag ces pa bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:4634: dang po la rigs lnga yab yum bcu dang /
NK076(mu)001:4635: sgo ba yab yum brgyad ste lha tshogs bco brgyad do //
NK076(mu)001:4636: 'bring po la rigs lnga yab yum bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4637: sems dpa' sems ma bcu drug /sgo ba yab yum brgyad /
NK076(mu)001:4638: kun bzang yab yum gnyis thub pa drug ste bzhi bcu zhe gnyis so //
NK076(mu)001:4640: dbus na rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyis gtso
NK076(mu)001:4641: bo byas nas rigs chung ni sems dpa' yab yum
NK076(mu)001:4643: shar rnam snang gi gtso bo byas pa bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4644: lho rin 'byung gis gtso bo byas pa bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4645: nub snang mtha' yis gtso bo byas pa bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4646: byang don grub kyis gtso bo byas pa bcu ste lnga bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4647: sems dpa' yab yum bcu drug /sgo ba yab yum brgyad /
NK076(mu)001:4648: thub pa drug ste brgyad bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4649: kun bzang yab yum gnyis te brgyad bcu rtsa gnyis so //
NK076(mu)001:4650: tshom bu spros pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK076(mu)001:4654: dang po la lha grangs bac+wa brgyad de /
NK076(mu)001:4655: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum la rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad kyis bskor ba bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4656: sgo ba yab yum brgyad do //
NK076(mu)001:4657: dal bsdus pa dang gnyis lha grangs la khyad par med kyang lhang ngo la khyad par yod do //
NK076(mu)001:4658: gsum pa la lha du yod na ngag 'bras bu'i gtan tshigs su shar nas /
NK076(mu)001:4659: slob dpon rnams dgongs pa ma mthun te /
NK076(mu)001:4660: mngon rtogs nas dbus rdo rje sems dpa' la rigs chung gis bskor ba bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4662: nub snang mtha' la bcu ste sum cu /
NK076(mu)001:4663: sgo ba yab yum brgyad de so brgyad du bshad /
NK076(mu)001:4664: spar khab nas gong gi steng du khro bo bcu bsnan pas zhe brgyad du bshad do //
NK076(mu)001:4665: lnga pa lha grangs bdun bcu ste /
NK076(mu)001:4666: sngar gyi steng du lho rin 'byung la bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4667: byang don grub la bcu ste lnga bcu'o //
NK076(mu)001:4668: khro bo khro mo nyi shu ste bdun bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4669: rnam grangs spros pa la bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:4670: gtso bo la bkod pa sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor /
NK076(mu)001:4671: kha ni thog mar yum gyi skye mched la gtso
NK076(mu)001:4672: bo yab yum na spyir stims pa'i lha thabs kyi
NK076(mu)001:4673: lha bzhi ste / yab kyi gtso bo rnam snang //
NK076(mu)001:4675: thugs kar rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK076(mu)001:4678: mig gi nang rtsar sa snying /
NK076(mu)001:4680: rna ba'i nang rtsar spyan ras /
NK076(mu)001:4685: phyi rtsar 'jal dpal la sogs phyag g.yas gshin rje /
NK076(mu)001:4693: gsang bar yi dwags rkang mthil dmyal thub po thugs kar kun bzang /
NK076(mu)001:4694: de bzhin du yum la yum rnams dgod par sbyar te thabs kyi lha 'dzin bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4695: de re re'i thugs kar shes rab kyi lha ye shes sems dpa' re re ste bzhi bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4696: thabs kyi gnas gsum du bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK076(mu)001:4697: lha sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum ste bzhi bcu
NK076(mu)001:4698: phrag gsum / sngar gyi dang log pas nyis rgya
NK076(mu)001:4699: bdag po rigs kyi lha dbu rgyan lnga lnga bkon
NK076(mu)001:4700: pas dbu rgyan gyi lha stong phrag khrigs bcad do
NK076(mu)001:4701: phrag gsum / // sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor
NK076(mu)001:4702: yang ri rab til 'bru'i tshul bzhin du ces so
NK076(mu)001:4703: phrag gsum / // // ka dbu rgyan kho na'i nyi khri stong dus gcig gsal /
NK076(mu)001:4705: dbang du nyi khri bzhi stong /
NK076(mu)001:4706: de bzhin rnam snang la sogs par yab yum zung
NK076(mu)001:4707: bcu bdun thub pa drug ste nyer gsum la stong
NK076(mu)001:4708: stong brtsi pas sngar gyi dang log pas stong phrag
NK076(mu)001:4709: nyi shu rtsags ste lam rim dang mthun par brtsis
NK076(mu)001:4710: nang / rnam grangs byung tshogs su nyi khri brgyad stong brgyad brgya /
NK076(mu)001:4711: sbyang gzhi rtog tshogs la ltos nas bsam yas lhun grub bo //
NK076(mu)001:4713: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4715: khro bo phyag rgya spros pa la yang bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:4720: dang po la gsum las bsdus pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:4722: gnas yul gyi lha mo bcu drug /sgo ma bzhi /
NK076(mu)001:4723: dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad de lnga bcu rtsa brgyad do //
NK076(mu)001:4724: 'bring po ni de'i steng du khro bo bcu dang
NK076(mu)001:4725: khro mo bcu bsnan pas bdun bcu rtsa brgyad do
NK076(mu)001:4726: // rgyas pa ni rigs lnga'i khrag 'thung yab yum
NK076(mu)001:4727: zung re la rigs chung gi khrag 'thung brgyad brgyad
NK076(mu)001:4728: kyis bskor bar lnga bcu'i steng du sngar gyi 'khor
NK076(mu)001:4729: byin po rtsa brgyad bsnan pas brgya dang bco brgyad
NK076(mu)001:4730: // do // tshom bu spros pa la yang gsum las /
NK076(mu)001:4731: gcig pa la lha grangs bdun bcu rtsa brgyad de /
NK076(mu)001:4732: badz+ra he ru ka yab yum la rigs chung yab yum brgyad kyis bskor ba bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4734: khro bo khro mo nyi shu /
NK076(mu)001:4735: dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK076(mu)001:4736: gong gi b+hu d+ha he ru ka dang bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4737: nub du pad ma he ru ka la bcu ste dgu bcu rtsa brgyad do //
NK076(mu)001:4738: tshom bu lnga pa la lha brgyad dang brgyad brgyad de /
NK076(mu)001:4739: sngar gyi steng du lhor rat+na he ru ka la bcu /
NK076(mu)001:4740: byang du karma he ru ka la bcu ste brgya dang bac+wo brgyad do //
NK076(mu)001:4742: gtso bo la skye mched kyi lha /
NK076(mu)001:4744: de re re la dbu rgyan rigs lnga lngas brgyan pas nyis brgya dgu bcu'o //
NK076(mu)001:4745: yang na zhi ba dang mthun par sbyar ro //
NK076(mu)001:4747: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4748: zhal gsum phyag drug pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4749: dbu dgu phyag bac+wo brgyad pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4750: dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig phyag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4755: yan lag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ldan //
NK076(mu)001:4756: de nyid yan lag spros bdag ste //
NK076(mu)001:4758: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog gis /
NK076(mu)001:4760: log rtog bsal ba la gnyis las /
NK076(mu)001:4761: ngo bor log par rtog pa ni kha cig na re 'di nyid du dkyil 'khor /
NK076(mu)001:4764: zhal phyag spros pa rnams mthar phyin par bsgom zhes zer ba ni mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:4765: de ltar na rigs 'dzin gsum las spros bcas bzang par thal /
NK076(mu)001:4766: dngos su spros bcas bsgom nus pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4767: 'dod na lam gong 'og gi khyad par gyis bsal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:4768: grangs la mthar thal 'gyur zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:4770: 'dir phyag rgya spros pa'i skabs nyid du dngos su gsal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis yin gyi //
NK076(mu)001:4771: gzhan rnams mos pa'i yul du bsgom mo //
NK076(mu)001:4772: de nas lam gong ma rnams su rim pa bzhin mngon du 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)001:4773: mthar lam du bsam yas lhun grub dngos su gsal
NK076(mu)001:4774: zhing zhal phyag gi rnam grangs kyang de ltar rim
NK076(mu)001:4775: pa bzhin te / ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:4776: rim brjod bstan pa'i spyod yul ni /
NK076(mu)001:4777: nyi shu gcig dang dgu brgyad dang //
NK076(mu)001:4778: grangs med mthar lam rim par bsgom //
NK076(mu)001:4780: 'bras bu'i log rtogs spangs pa sngar bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:4781: brtsad pa spang pa dang bcas pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:4782: de ltar na'ang tshom bu dang dkyil 'khor gnyis la khyad par yod dam med drang /
NK076(mu)001:4783: med na gnyis su phye ba nyid la dgos pa med par 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)001:4784: yod na gang yin zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4785: lan ni 'dod pa tha dad de /
NK076(mu)001:4786: kha cig zur chung na re /
NK076(mu)001:4787: mi grangs nges pa can gyis lha grangs nges pa can bsgom pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:4789: mi grangs nges pa can med pa'i lha grangs nges
NK076(mu)001:4790: pa med pa bsgom pa ni dkyil 'khor zhes zer
NK076(mu)001:4792: de ltar na tshom bu ga cig pa la brtan pa thob nas gsum pa bsgom pa na /
NK076(mu)001:4793: tshom bu ma yin par thal /
