NK076(mu)001:4794: mi grangs mang du ma song la lha grangs mang du song bas phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:4795: yang kha cig skyos na re gnas skabs su gtso bo nges pa ni dkyil 'khor la /
NK076(mu)001:4796: gtso bo ma nges pa ni tshom bu zhes zer ba ni mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:4797: de ltar na tshom bu ga cig pa nyid dkyil 'khor du thal /
NK076(mu)001:4798: gnas skabs su gtso bo nges pa kho nar rdo rje rigs kyis byed pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:4801: rnam grangs byung tshogs su ston pa dkyil 'khor /
NK076(mu)001:4802: gtso bo phri brnan du ston pa'i tshom bu ste /
NK076(mu)001:4803: gtso bo gcig na tshom bu /
NK076(mu)001:4805: gtso bo gsum na tshom bu gsum zer ba yang zer yang 'thad sems /
NK076(mu)001:4807: de ltar na dkyil 'khor gyis tshom bu la ma khyab par thal /
NK076(mu)001:4808: rnam grangs byung tshogs kho na dkyil 'khor yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4809: 'dod na tshom bu rtags kyi dkyil 'khor zhes gsungs pa dang 'gal zhes gsung rung ngo //
NK076(mu)001:4810: bla ma ni ngo bo gcig la zlog pa tha
NK076(mu)001:4811: dad pas khyab che chung du gyur pa nyid do
NK076(mu)001:4812: // dal gyi tshom bu la khyab cing tshom bus dal la khyab cing gsung mod kyi /
NK076(mu)001:4813: bdag ni rigs tha dad kyi gtso bo gcig du gyur pa ni dkyil 'khor /
NK076(mu)001:4814: rigs tha mi dad kyi gtso bo so sos byed
NK076(mu)001:4815: pa ni tshom bu zhes bsnyad na legs par sems
NK076(mu)001:4816: te / dang bo ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs
NK076(mu)001:4817: rnams snang la sogs pa yang gtso bor rdo rje
NK076(mu)001:4819: gnyis pa ni rang gi rigs che chung gis bye brag du bskor ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:4820: de ltar na'ang dal rgyas pa 'di tshom bur thal te /
NK076(mu)001:4821: rang rang gi rigs chung gis bye brag du bskor ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:4823: khyab pa ma grub ste spyi'i gtso bo ga cig gis byed pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4826: rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil nyid de //
NK076(mu)001:4827: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mos 'khor //
NK076(mu)001:4829: yang 'dir lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bsgom pas spros par brtags pa ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:4830: yin na spros pa chen po yang spros par thal /
NK076(mu)001:4831: gzhan don gyi phrin las su lha du ma bsgom pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:4832: 'dod na stong chen ma yin par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:4833: mi bsgom na spros pa'i dkyil 'khor mos bsgom zhes gsungs pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:4834: lan ni dngos su bsgom pa'i phyir zer ram /
NK076(mu)001:4835: mos pa bsgom pa' phyir zer /
NK076(mu)001:4836: dang po ltar na rtags ma grub la /
NK076(mu)001:4837: gnyis pa ltar na mos pa tsam sgom yang dngos
NK076(mu)001:4838: su bsgom mi nus pas khyad par yod na ci
NK076(mu)001:4839: sto ste khyab pa med ces bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:4840: bar chad med pa'i lam du tshogs bsgrub pa la don bcu las /
NK076(mu)001:4841: dang por gzhi gang dang sbyar na spyad ris dang
NK076(mu)001:4842: khe grags la sogs pa byed pa dang mthun te
NK076(mu)001:4843: / yul lha zas nor dbang byed pa //
NK076(mu)001:4844: cha gnyis la sogs 'jug par byed //
NK076(mu)001:4846: khyad par gyi dgos pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:4847: 'khor bar bzlog pa'i nyes pa dor nas zag med
NK076(mu)001:4848: kyi bden pa chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid mthong
NK076(mu)001:4849: ba la dngos su sbyor bar byed pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:4850: rnal 'byor tshogs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyis nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa grub /
NK076(mu)001:4852: bya ba'i spyod pa ni yo byad lnga la blang
NK076(mu)001:4853: dor med pa rmad du byung ba'i spyod pa byed
NK076(mu)001:4854: de / spyod lam yo byad lnga spyod cing zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:4856: snang stong lha'i dkyil 'khor du ngo bo dngos su gsal zhing blo gnas pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:4857: de ltar na spros pa dang khyad ci yod snyam na /
NK076(mu)001:4858: spros pa ni gsal zhing nye ba tsam yin la /
NK076(mu)001:4859: 'dir ni shin du gsal brtan du gyur zhing nye ba yin te /
NK076(mu)001:4861: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK076(mu)001:4862: dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i ting nge 'dzin zhes pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4864: de yang mthu bzhi nus pa yis //
NK076(mu)001:4865: lta spyod 'brel bas brtan pa yin //
NK076(mu)001:4867: mtshan nyid theg pa'i sa lam dang sbyar na /
NK076(mu)001:4868: rnal 'byor sbyor lam chen po bzod pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:4869: chos mchog dang po tshod mnyam mo //
NK076(mu)001:4870: ting nge 'dzin gyi dbye ba la gnyis ste /
NK076(mu)001:4871: zhi ba'i tshogs bsgrub pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4873: 'di yang nyams su len pa'i dus su /
NK076(mu)001:4874: phun sum 'tshogs pa bzhis bsgrub pa'i gzhi bzung pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4875: bsnyen bsgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4876: rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i dus gsum du 'ching bar byed de /
NK076(mu)001:4878: de la snga ma gnas dang dus /
NK076(mu)001:4880: bsgrub thabs phun gsum tshogs pa'i //
NK076(mu)001:4881: gzhi dang sbyar bas gzhung rdzogs bya //
NK076(mu)001:4883: bsnyen bsgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK076(mu)001:4885: de las lam bsgrub sbyor ba yis //
NK076(mu)001:4887: lam dus kyi bsnyen bsgrub bzhi dang /
NK076(mu)001:4888: sgrub pa dus kyi bsnyen bsgrub bzhi dang /
NK076(mu)001:4889: rnal 'byor ba dus kyi bsnyen bsgrub bzhi'o //
NK076(mu)001:4890: dang po ni de ting dang sgyu ma gnyis ni bsnyen pa /
NK076(mu)001:4891: phyag rgya gcig spros ni nye bsnyen /
NK076(mu)001:4892: bar chad med pa'i lam ni bsgrub pa /
NK076(mu)001:4893: rig 'dzin bzhi ni bsgrub pa chen po ste /
NK076(mu)001:4895: rtsa ba'i dang po bsnyen pa ni //
NK076(mu)001:4896: bya ba sems rtogs 'grub pa ste //
NK076(mu)001:4897: phyag rgya gsal ba nye bsnyen pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:4898: de phyir gcig dang spros pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:4899: bsgrub pa nyid ni bar chad med //
NK076(mu)001:4900: dus kyi tshogs mtha' bsgrub chen len //
NK076(mu)001:4902: sbyor pa dus kyi bsnyen bsgrub bzhi ni /
NK076(mu)001:4903: yum mtshan dang ldan pa ni bsnyen pa /
NK076(mu)001:4904: de la khrus byas te rgyan 'dog pa ni nye bsnyen /
NK076(mu)001:4905: mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs nas snyoms par zhugs pa ni bsgrub pa /
NK076(mu)001:4906: bya ba kyi sems btang ste bde ba nyams su myong ba ni bsgrub pa chen po ste /
NK076(mu)001:4908: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK076(mu)001:4909: dabye'am yang na mi dbye bar //
NK076(mu)001:4910: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen pa //
NK076(mu)001:4911: bsgrub pa dang ni bsgrub chen po //
NK076(mu)001:4912: yum gyi pad ma'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK076(mu)001:4913: bde ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor spro zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:4914: bsgrub pa dus kyi bsnyen sgrub bzhi ni //
NK076(mu)001:4915: yo byad 'tshogs te bsgrub pa byed pa la ma thogs pa ni bsnyen pa /
NK076(mu)001:4916: bsgrub pa la zhugs te zhag du byed pa'i phyed yan chad nye bsnyen /
NK076(mu)001:4918: nub tha ma la dngos grub blangs pa ni bsgrub pa chen po ste /
NK076(mu)001:4920: zla phyed phyed zhag nye bsnyen pa //
NK076(mu)001:4922: bco lnga phyed ma sgrub pa ste //
NK076(mu)001:4924: zhag grangs tshang nas rtags byung na //
NK076(mu)001:4925: dngos grub bzlas blang bsgrub chen po //
NK076(mu)001:4927: bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu grub pa'i dus ni /
NK076(mu)001:4928: rab kyis zla ba drug gam gnyis //
NK076(mu)001:4930: tha mas bcu drug gam drug na /
NK076(mu)001:4932: tha mas rnam smin las sbyor te /
NK076(mu)001:4934: zhag gi sum bcu phrag drug gam //
NK076(mu)001:4935: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK076(mu)001:4936: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK076(mu)001:4938: yang zhag ni sum bcu phrag drug gam /drug bcu'am dgu bcu rtsa drug du //
NK076(mu)001:4939: sde dang bcas pa'i bsam pa yis //
NK076(mu)001:4940: re ba med par bsgrub par bya //
NK076(mu)001:4943: snying po yan lag ma nyams yo byad ldan //
NK076(mu)001:4944: cho ga rdzogs par shes pa yi //
NK076(mu)001:4946: nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK076(mu)001:4948: 'bras bu ni gong dang mtshungs so //
NK076(mu)001:4950: gzhan la med kyis nges tshig cung zad yod de /
NK076(mu)001:4951: 'di kha cig na re zag bcas nas zag med
NK076(mu)001:4952: du sbyor ba la bar gzhan gyis ma chod pas
NK076(mu)001:4954: gsung yang kha slas cig phal che bas dbang du lam gzhan gyis bar du ma chod pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:4955: gsung yang kha cig nya ri gis ngan song du 'gro bar chad med pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:4956: gsung bdag gis bla ma ni spros pa man chod la dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes pas /
NK076(mu)001:4957: 'khor bar bzlog pa'i bar chad yod la /
NK076(mu)001:4958: tshogs bsgrub man chod la 'khor bar bzlog pa'i bar
NK076(mu)001:4959: chad med pas spyi sgra bye brag la zhugs te
NK076(mu)001:4960: / spyir tshogs bsgrub man chad la bar chad med kyang /
NK076(mu)001:4961: bye brag du tshogs bsgrub la sgra de zhugs de bar chad med ces bya /
NK076(mu)001:4962: tshogs ni rnal 'byor pa du ma la byas la /
NK076(mu)001:4963: bsgrub pa ni nyams su blang pa'o gsung /
NK076(mu)001:4964: bdag na zag bcas nas zag med du sbyor ba
NK076(mu)001:4965: la rten skye ba gzhan gyis bar du ma chod
NK076(mu)001:4966: cing / bgrod bya lam gzhan gyis bar du ma
NK076(mu)001:4967: chod pas na bar chad med par sbyor bas lam
NK076(mu)001:4968: zhes bya'o snyan du sems so //
NK076(mu)001:4969: brtsod pa med pas spang mi dgos so //
NK076(mu)001:4970: spyi don gnyis pa thod rgal gyi lam bstan pa la bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:4971: thod rgal nyid gang nas 'byung ba'i sa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4972: ji ltar 'byung ba'i tshul bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4973: 'byung mi 'byung gi rgyu mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:4974: sgros 'dogs kyi blos tha snyad bsam pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:4981: tshogs bsgrub dang gsum nas 'byung la /
NK076(mu)001:4982: zag med ni tshe dbang dang phyag rgya chen po gnyis nas 'byung na'o //
NK076(mu)001:4984: dang por de bzhin gyi skabs su shes rab rkyang pa bsgom zhing /
NK076(mu)001:4985: kun tu snang du thabs rkyang pa bsgom pas mi 'byung la /
NK076(mu)001:4986: de'i rjes su phyag rgya gcig par dbyer med pa la /
NK076(mu)001:4987: goms par nas thong rgal 'byung ste /
NK076(mu)001:4988: 'di nas spros pa dor de blo chung na tshogs bsgrub la sbyor zhing /
NK076(mu)001:4989: blo che na spros tshogs gnyis char dor nas rig 'dzin la sbyor te /
NK076(mu)001:4991: phyag rgya gcig brtan 'pho ba yang //
NK076(mu)001:4992: khyung dang seng ge ji bzhin te //
NK076(mu)001:4993: spros tshogs skabs na smos ci dgos //
NK076(mu)001:4995: yang rnam smin rigs la the tshom med ces so //
NK076(mu)001:4996: spros pa nas kyang rig 'dzin la sbyor te /
NK076(mu)001:4997: spros tshogs skabs nas smos ci dgos zhes sngar bstan pa nyid kyi shes so //
NK076(mu)001:4998: tshogs sgrub nas kyang phyag rgya chen po la sbyor te /
NK076(mu)001:5000: yo byad rnams pa bzhi la lta spyod gnyis su
NK076(mu)001:5001: med par bsgrubs nas 'bras bu sku phyag rgya chen
NK076(mu)001:5002: po'i rig 'dzin thob po zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:5003: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin nas kyang lhun grub la sbyor te /
NK076(mu)001:5005: kha cig dbang sgyur rigs nyid nas //
NK076(mu)001:5006: bcu drug rgyun gyis sku lnga rdzogs //
NK076(mu)001:5008: phyag rgya chen po nas kyang sangs rgyas kyi sa la sbyor te /
NK076(mu)001:5010: kha cig phyag rgya chen po nas //
NK076(mu)001:5011: bla med kun tu bzang por sbyor zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:5012: de rnams ma yin pa ni thod rgal med gsungs /
NK076(mu)001:5013: thod rgal 'byung mi'abyunga gi rgyu mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:5014: spyir thod rgal 'byung pa la chos gsum dang ldan dgos te /
NK076(mu)001:5015: de dang mi ldan na ni mi 'byung ngo //
NK076(mu)001:5016: gsum gang zhe na lam gzhan gong na bgrod bya yod pa /
NK076(mu)001:5018: blo che ba dang gsum mo /
NK076(mu)001:5019: des na gong du stan pa de rnams la chos gsum po de dang ldan la /
NK076(mu)001:5020: gzhan la mi ldan no de ji ltar zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5021: stong pa chen po don dam rkyang pa bsgom pas thod rgal mi 'ong zhing /
NK076(mu)001:5022: snying rje chen po kun rdzob brkyang pa bsgoms pas mi 'ong /
NK076(mu)001:5023: rnam smin blo chung bas mi 'ong /
NK076(mu)001:5024: lhun grub lam gzhan la gong na bgrod bya med pas mi 'ong ste /
NK076(mu)001:5027: rnam pa kun ldan stong chen mthong //
NK076(mu)001:5029: yang rang rig ye shes snying rje gzigs //
NK076(mu)001:5031: stobs chung skye smos zhan pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:5032: rnam rtog 'byung ba'i lhag lus bzhag /ces pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:5033: de nyid dang ni mthar sbyor lam //
NK076(mu)001:5034: zhes pa bdag gis shes so //
NK076(mu)001:5035: sgros 'dogs kyi blos tha snyad bsal ba ni /
NK076(mu)001:5036: kha cig stong pa chen po nas kyang thod rgal 'byung bar 'dod de /
NK076(mu)001:5037: sngon byas lhag pa'i chos kun sbyor zhes pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5040: de ni stong pa chen po chos sku dang phyogs mthun pas de skad brjod kyi /
NK076(mu)001:5041: dngos su sbyor ba'i khungs min no //
NK076(mu)001:5042: 'o na gcig spros nas bshad pa'i thod rgal de yang dngos su sbyor ba min te /
NK076(mu)001:5043: de yis mgo mi 'dre ste thod rgal 'ong ba
NK076(mu)001:5044: la chos gsum ldan zhig dgos pa la 'dir dbyer
NK076(mu)001:5045: med bsgoms mi nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5046: yang sgyu ma lta bu nas thod rgal 'ong bar 'dod te /
NK076(mu)001:5047: mi bzlog dbang sgyur rigs su nges zhes gsung pa'i phyir zhes smra ba yang mi 'thad ste /
NK076(mu)001:5048: 'dir yang dbyer med bsgom mi nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5049: lung yang dgongs pa can yin te //
NK076(mu)001:5050: sgyu ma'i ting nge des rig pa la dbang bsgyur
NK076(mu)001:5051: ba dang dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa gsang sngags
NK076(mu)001:5052: la sbyor ba la bshad pa yin gyi /
NK076(mu)001:5053: thod rgal gyi khungs du min /
NK076(mu)001:5054: mi bzlog ba'i sgra'ang phal che ba'ang /
NK076(mu)001:5055: lta ba rtogs pa'i yon tan la dgongs pa yin gsung /
NK076(mu)001:5056: kha cig ni tshogs bsgrub na thod rgal mi 'ong par 'dod lo /
NK076(mu)001:5057: 'di ni rigs pa ma yin te sngar gyi lung gis kyang zin la /
NK076(mu)001:5059: thod rgal 'byung ba'i chos gsum char dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5060: de gsum ni gzhan gyi sgros 'don bsal ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:5061: bdag gi bla ma ni rnam smin la'ang thod rgal 'ong bar 'thad gsung /
NK076(mu)001:5064: de ni blo chung pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5065: 'o na de bas dma' ba'i phyag rgya gcig spros pa'ang thod rgal 'ong pa la /
NK076(mu)001:5066: de bas kyang rnam smin blo chung par thal /
NK076(mu)001:5067: 'dod na lam gong ma'i gong du bgrod pa don med du 'gyur zhing /
NK076(mu)001:5068: lam mtha' ru song ba bzhin du blo ngan du 'gro bar thal lo //
NK076(mu)001:5069: de ni lam gong ma phyag rgya chen po dang
NK076(mu)001:5070: khad mnyam pa'i tshe dbang la ltos nas ngan pa
NK076(mu)001:5071: yin zhe na / de tshod du phyag rgya gcig
NK076(mu)001:5072: pa 'di lam gong ma spros tshogs la ltos nas
NK076(mu)001:5073: blo ngan pas 'di nas kyang mi 'ong par thal
NK076(mu)001:5074: yin zhe na / lo // lung nas kyang 'byung bar bshad de /
NK076(mu)001:5077: rnam smin tshe'i lus phye nas //
NK076(mu)001:5078: lhag pa yod med lung bstan pa //
NK076(mu)001:5079: thar lam dngos la sbyor bar byed //
NK076(mu)001:5080: ces lhun grub la sbyor bar bshad do //
NK076(mu)001:5081: ces gsungs pa yang lung rigs kyis grub pa'i phyir mi 'thad par mi sems so //
NK076(mu)001:5082: zag pa dang bcas pa'i lam bstan to //
NK076(mu)001:5083: skabs 'dir zag zlog yod mod kyi tha snyad kyang gsung ste /
NK076(mu)001:5085: spyir zag bcas zag med kyi khyad par rjes su
NK076(mu)001:5086: 'brel ba'i don zag zlog yod med kyi sa mtshams
NK076(mu)001:5088: dang po ni lha rje chen po nya ri ba /
NK076(mu)001:5089: nyid kyis zag pa'i gtso bo skye gnas kyi zag
NK076(mu)001:5090: med kyi zag med de yod pas zag bcas yin
NK076(mu)001:5092: rig 'dzin dang rang bzhin gyi don du bsam bzhin
NK076(mu)001:5093: skye ba len pa dag kyang zag bcas su thal
NK076(mu)001:5094: / zag pa dang bcas pa'i skye ba 'dzin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:5097: lha dang mi dang tshangs pa ni //
NK076(mu)001:5098: skye ba rnam dag 'dzin mod kyang //
NK076(mu)001:5099: khyad par sa la gnas gyur yin //
NK076(mu)001:5102: khyab pa ma grub na dam bca' nyams so //
NK076(mu)001:5103: yang mkhas pa'i skye bo slas rda la kha cig /zag bcas rang gi mtshan nyid mthong //
NK076(mu)001:5104: zag pa dang bcas zag bcas /
NK076(mu)001:5105: zag med rang gi mtshan nyid mthong //
NK076(mu)001:5106: zag pa gsum po med pas zag med ces zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:5107: dang por de dag 'tshogs pa mtshan nyid du gtong
NK076(mu)001:5108: kha yar gyi chog /dang po ltar na tshe dbang
NK076(mu)001:5109: gi rig 'dzin nyid kyang zag bcas su thal te
NK076(mu)001:5110: / lung gi zag pa ma spangs ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:5111: rtag ma grub te spang ngo zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5113: gnyis pa ltar na rnam smin dang khyad med du 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)001:5115: dang po ltar na spangs par 'dod pa nyams so //
NK076(mu)001:5117: dpyad yar gyi chog na lha gnas gong ma dag kyang zag med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:5118: lus khams kyi zag pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5120: khyab pa med na dam bca' bud ces bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:5121: rang lugs ni mkhas pa gnyos kha cig gi rjes
NK076(mu)001:5122: su kun nas nyon mongs pa dang bcas pa'i las
NK076(mu)001:5123: kyis kun nas bslang nas khams gsum du zag cing
NK076(mu)001:5125: de las log pa ni zag med ces bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:5127: de dag 'jig rten pa la yod pa'i phyir zag par 'gyur te zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:5128: bye brag tu zhen pa phyin ci log gi sgro btags nyon mongs pa'i zag pa /
NK076(mu)001:5130: dbang med par len cing snyigs ma'i dngos po dor
NK076(mu)001:5131: bya dang bcas pa zag pa lus kyi zag pa
NK076(mu)001:5132: / bde sdug rang dbang med pa khams kyi zag pa /
NK076(mu)001:5133: skye ba bzhir rang dbang med par 'jug pa skye gnas kyi zag pa zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:5134: gnyis pa rjes su 'brel ba'i don gyis mtshams nye bar gzung ba ni /
NK076(mu)001:5135: phyir lam rim gyis pa'i dbang du byas na gsum gsum ste /
NK076(mu)001:5136: zag pa yang yod la bzlog pa yang yod pa'i lam dang /
NK076(mu)001:5137: zag pa yang med la bzlog pa yang med pa'i lam dang /
NK076(mu)001:5138: zag pa ni yod la bzlog pa ni med pa'i lam mo //
NK076(mu)001:5139: dang po ni spros pa man chod do //
NK076(mu)001:5141: rdo rje sems dpa'i bkas bshad yi //
NK076(mu)001:5142: sdom pa'i rtsa ba thams cad kun //
NK076(mu)001:5143: de bzhin nyid du ma bsrungs na //
NK076(mu)001:5144: yag sha khro bo me dbal gyis //
NK076(mu)001:5145: snying nas drangs shing khrag 'thung pas //
NK076(mu)001:5146: de'i sdug bsngal bzod blags med //
NK076(mu)001:5147: de phyir lam dang zlog zag yod //
NK076(mu)001:5149: yang zlog chos bzhi dang sbyor lam bcu zhes pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:5151: zag yod zlog pa lam chung /
NK076(mu)001:5153: mthu yis ngan 'gror bzlog mi bzlog /sngon gyi shes 'jug brgyad la yod //
NK076(mu)001:5154: mthar shes 'jug la ga la yod //
NK076(mu)001:5157: dngos grub mchog gi dang po ni /
NK076(mu)001:5158: dang po'i don dam rtogs mthar mi zlog /chu srin phyag rgya ji bzhin du //
NK076(mu)001:5159: skye ba bgrangs kyang ltung mi srid //
NK076(mu)001:5161: lta ba'i rtogs pa'i yon tan gyis 'khor bar mi zlog pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:5162: 'dir spros pa nas kyang 'khor bar ldog par bshad pa 'gal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5163: lan ni mi 'gal te 'dir spros pa nas zlog
NK076(mu)001:5164: par bshad pa de dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes pa
NK076(mu)001:5166: lta ba'i skabs nas mi ldog par bshad pa de
NK076(mu)001:5167: dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes pas re shig ngan song
NK076(mu)001:5168: du skyes kyang lta ba rtogs pa'i yon tan gyi
NK076(mu)001:5169: sdug bsngal drag po mi 'byung zhing yun thung pa
NK076(mu)001:5171: dper na lha mo sked med ma bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:5172: ji skad du lung las kyang /
NK076(mu)001:5173: dper na pho long sdabs pa bzhin /
NK076(mu)001:5174: 'phen 'gro'i stobs kyis der mi gnas ces bshad ces ru gong ma yam shud gsung ngo //
NK076(mu)001:5175: bla ma kha cig po gis spros pa nas bzlog
NK076(mu)001:5176: par bshad pa de dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes pas
NK076(mu)001:5177: spyir 'khor ba tsam po bzlog par bshad kyi /
NK076(mu)001:5178: ngan song du zlog pa'i nyes pa med gsung /
NK076(mu)001:5179: lta bas skabs nas mi zlog par bshad pa de
NK076(mu)001:5180: ni lta ba rtogs pa'i yon tan gyi 'khor ba'i
NK076(mu)001:5181: bye brag ngan song du mi ltung pa la dgongs
NK076(mu)001:5182: pa yin pas 'gal ba med gsung /
NK076(mu)001:5183: yang kha cig na re slas nyang lo 'dir spros
NK076(mu)001:5184: pa nas bzlog par bshad pa de dam tshig nyams
NK076(mu)001:5185: pa'i nyes pa na dam chos /
NK076(mu)001:5186: lta ba'i ngos nas mi zlog par bshad pa de
NK076(mu)001:5187: lta ba rtogs pa'i che ba phyung pa yin te
NK076(mu)001:5188: gnyis ka dgongs pa can min gsung skad /
NK076(mu)001:5189: bdag ni 'dir spros pa nas bzlog par bshad pa
NK076(mu)001:5190: ni rim gyis pas da rung lta bar rang mtshan
NK076(mu)001:5191: du ma rtogs pas nyes la /
NK076(mu)001:5192: lta ba'i skabs nas mi zlog par bshad pa ni
NK076(mu)001:5193: cig char bas dang po nyid nas dbyer med chig
NK076(mu)001:5194: chod du rtogs pa'i sngon gyis brjod pa yin sems
NK076(mu)001:5195: / zag pa yang med la zlog pa yang med pa ni rig 'dzin bzhi ste rnam smin /
NK076(mu)001:5196: lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang /
NK076(mu)001:5197: phyag rgya chen po lhun gyis grub pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:5199: de nas bzhi yis zag dang bral zhes pa dang yang zag kun zad pa'i rigs chen 'di /
NK076(mu)001:5200: ji ltar spyad kyang zlog pa med //
NK076(mu)001:5202: zag pa ni yod la bzlog pa med pa ni tshogs bsgrub ste /
NK076(mu)001:5203: de ltar bden pa dngos su mthong pa yod yang
NK076(mu)001:5204: bsgrub pa pa'i 'bras yon tan gyi dus grangs bzhin
NK076(mu)001:5205: du zag med du sbyor ba la skad cig gzhan
NK076(mu)001:5206: gyis gegs kyis bar ma chod par 'thob pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:5207: / zag pa phye ma'i rigs mthun gyis 'bras bu mi byed pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:5208: sa bon yongs su bsngo ba bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:5210: bar chad med par sbyor ba'i zhes pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:5211: sngon gyi shes 'jug brgyad la yod //
NK076(mu)001:5212: mthar shes 'jug la ga la yod /
NK076(mu)001:5214: yang na tshe 'adi'am bar do tshun chad du zag
NK076(mu)001:5215: med ma thob kyang tshogs sgrub pa'i yon tan gyis
NK076(mu)001:5216: phyin chad ngan 'gro bzlog ste thun mong theg pa'i
NK076(mu)001:5217: sbyor lam gyi bzod thob dang 'dra bar sems so
NK076(mu)001:5218: // lam du gyur pa'i 'bras bu'am zag med kyi lam la rig 'dzin rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:5219: mthong lam gyi rig 'dzin gnyis dang /
NK076(mu)001:5220: bsgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)001:5221: mthar lam lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK076(mu)001:5223: lhag med mya ngan las 'das pa rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)001:5224: lhag bcas su mya ngan 'das pa'i tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin te /
NK076(mu)001:5226: dus tshigs bar chad med pa nas //
NK076(mu)001:5227: lhag med med dang yod pa 'di //
NK076(mu)001:5228: mya ngan 'das par mthar sbyor ba //
NK076(mu)001:5229: thun mong lta bur zung du 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:5230: zhes lam khad mnyam du bshad do //
NK076(mu)001:5231: de dag kun kyang bslab gzhi mthun par gzhan don byed pa dang sbyar te /
NK076(mu)001:5232: thams cad lam las thogs med par //
NK076(mu)001:5233: gzhan gyi lam la 'jug par byed /
NK076(mu)001:5235: bye brag du dang por rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin la don bcu ste /
NK076(mu)001:5244: mtshan nyid theg pa'i sa lam dang sbyar ba /
NK076(mu)001:5247: dang po gcig spros kyi ting nge dang ldan pas
NK076(mu)001:5248: tshogs sgrub pas rab 'bring dus bzhin lhag med kyi
NK076(mu)001:5251: gcig dang du mas rnal 'byor pas //
NK076(mu)001:5252: brtan byas nyid pa'am de thob nas /
NK076(mu)001:5253: zla drug bcu drug bsnyen bsgrub tshe //
NK076(mu)001:5254: rdo rje'i lus su ma gyur par //
NK076(mu)001:5256: rang gi ngo bo ni chos bzhi ldan pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:5257: lus rdos bcas sha khrag gi phung po dang ma bral ba yin te /
NK076(mu)001:5258: lus kyi d+r+wa bas bsgrib gyur cing //
NK076(mu)001:5259: lus lha'i sku bgos dang bskyed dbyung du med par gsal te /
NK076(mu)001:5260: lha'i rnal 'byor gsal rdzogs smin zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:5261: lus dang bral ma thag tu phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sbyor ba ste /
NK076(mu)001:5262: lus kyi rgya mdud grol byas nas //
NK076(mu)001:5263: phyag rgya'i sku nyid gsal gyur pa //
NK076(mu)001:5265: rang gi ngo bo nus thob kyi mthong lam la gnas pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:5266: tshe dbang khad mnyam pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5267: rnam grangs sngar gyi rnam smin lus 'di nyid myang 'das kyi sar khyer mi nus pas /
NK076(mu)001:5269: lhag med kyi myang 'das zhes kyang bya /
NK076(mu)001:5270: rang don du srid pa'i mngal phyi mar mi len pa'i srid pa tha ma ces kyang bya /
NK076(mu)001:5271: rnam par yid lha'i skur smin pas /
NK076(mu)001:5272: smin pa'i rig 'dzin zhes kyang bya ste //
NK076(mu)001:5273: lhag med 'byung med las lus med /
NK076(mu)001:5274: mya ngan 'das par smin zhes brjod //
NK076(mu)001:5276: spyod dpyod pa ni rang gzhan gyi don du bkod
NK076(mu)001:5277: pa dkyil 'khor gyi bya bas tshogs gnyis rdzogs par
NK076(mu)001:5278: byed de / dkyil 'khor rol pa'i tshul spyod pa //
NK076(mu)001:5279: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa bdag gi don //
NK076(mu)001:5280: smin pas phrin las rdzogs byed pa //
NK076(mu)001:5283: cha lugs ni yid rtsa ba'i lha gang yin gyi cha lugs 'dzin pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:5284: yid kyi lha'i gzugs bzung zhing //
NK076(mu)001:5286: mngon shes kyi don yul ni /
NK076(mu)001:5287: zag pa med pa'i lha'i spyan rnam par dag pa
NK076(mu)001:5288: la sogs pas gling bzhi 'khor yug tsam yul du
NK076(mu)001:5289: gyur cing de dag gi don byed par nus te
NK076(mu)001:5291: bar chad med pa'i smin pa'i //
NK076(mu)001:5292: mngon par shes pa de ming can //
NK076(mu)001:5294: dpag tshad gling khams yul du sbyor //
NK076(mu)001:5297: rnam smin gyi lus 'di dang bral ma thag tu
NK076(mu)001:5298: lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po 'od kyi lus la
NK076(mu)001:5299: sbyor ba ste / gang de bral ma thag pa ru //
NK076(mu)001:5300: rgya bzhi rdzogs par bdag 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:5301: rdo rje lnga rtsogs rig pa 'dzin //
NK076(mu)001:5302: phyag rgya chen po rig 'bras bu //
NK076(mu)001:5307: sngon du mi 'gyur sgribs gyur kyang //
NK076(mu)001:5309: rnam rtog lus ni bor ma thag /thams cad kun la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK076(mu)001:5312: mtshan nyid theg pa'i sa lam dang sbyar na /
NK076(mu)001:5313: mthong lam dang po dang mo tshod mnyam ste /
NK076(mu)001:5314: de la dang po'i dang po dang skal mnyam //
NK076(mu)001:5316: zhal la dogs bsal ba dang /
NK076(mu)001:5318: dang por ngo bo la log par rtog pa ni kha cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:5319: rim kyis pa dbang btsan du byas nas tshogs bsgrubs nas tshe 'pho ba'i dus su /
NK076(mu)001:5320: skad cig ma dang po la tshogs sgrub /
NK076(mu)001:5322: gsum pa la phyag rgya chen po zer te rnam smin skad cig la med /
NK076(mu)001:5324: rnam smin gyis gzhan don byed dam mi byed /
NK076(mu)001:5325: mi byed na smin pas phrin las rdzogs mdzad par //
NK076(mu)001:5328: byed na skad cig ma grub pa'i phyir sangs rgyas dang khyad med du thal lo /
NK076(mu)001:5330: rgyu gong ma ni rtags pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:5331: mtshan nyid pa gnyis su 'dod pa'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:5332: rgyu tshogs sgrub la rnam smin du 'dogs na phyis
NK076(mu)001:5333: 'ong pa'i sgra la zhugs pa rgyu 'bras go log
NK076(mu)001:5334: la / 'bras bu phyag rgya chen po la rnam smin du 'dod pa'ang mi rigs te /
NK076(mu)001:5335: 'bras bu la sbyor tshul gyi khungs nyid brtags pa'i shes byed mi rung rgyu gsung /
NK076(mu)001:5336: yang lha rje nya ri ba /
NK076(mu)001:5337: chen po ni chos gsum ldan du 'dod de /
NK076(mu)001:5338: gdos bcas sha khrag gi lus dang ma bral ba /
NK076(mu)001:5339: yid lha'i sku ji lta ba bzhin gsal ba /
NK076(mu)001:5340: lus dang bral ma thag par gzhan gyis bar ma chod par phyag rgya chen po la sbyor ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:5341: zhes gsungs pa yang mi 'thad do //
NK076(mu)001:5342: de ltar na tshogs sgrub bsgres po blo yang rab
NK076(mu)001:5343: nas phyag rgya chen por sbyor ba de yang rnam
NK076(mu)001:5345: chos gsum dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:5346: gtan tshigs ma grub na gang dang mi ldan par brtag par bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:5347: lus dngos su yod par gsal /
NK076(mu)001:5348: rtsod kyang lha'i skur bskyed dbyung du med par gsal te /
NK076(mu)001:5349: de ltar smin na phyag rgya chen po'i rgyu nus
NK076(mu)001:5350: pa thogs med du mi 'thad de lam gzhan gyis
NK076(mu)001:5351: skyed dbyung du med par de nyid thod rgal du
NK076(mu)001:5353: 'dod na mthong sbyor khyad med du 'gyur gsung ngo //
NK076(mu)001:5354: bdag gi bla ma ni chos bzhi ldan du bzhed de /
NK076(mu)001:5356: lus kyi rgya mdud ma bral /
NK076(mu)001:5357: bral ma thag tu phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sbyor ba /
NK076(mu)001:5358: rang gi ngo bo nus thob kyi mthong lam la gnas pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:5359: phyi ma 'dis tshogs bsgrub bsgres po blo yang rab
NK076(mu)001:5360: la las byas pa'o zhes gsung pa ni mkhas pa'i
NK076(mu)001:5361: man ngag go /yang thob pa'i dus la log par
NK076(mu)001:5362: rtog pa ni / snga rabs pa dag blo khyad
NK076(mu)001:5363: par gyis rnam smin la sbyor ba'i dus kyang gsum
NK076(mu)001:5364: rtog pa ni / ste / rab 'di la sbyor /
NK076(mu)001:5366: tha ma'ang lan grangs gzhan la sbyor te /
NK076(mu)001:5369: lan grangs gzhan du rab 'bring gis //
NK076(mu)001:5370: thob phyir skal bar mi 'gyang ste //
NK076(mu)001:5373: de nyid sar phyi'am lan grangs gzhan zhes bshad pa'o zhes zer ro //
NK076(mu)001:5374: de ltar na bar do la rnam smin thob pa de lus grub par yod dam med /
NK076(mu)001:5375: yod na bar do mi gtub ste /
NK076(mu)001:5376: bar do'i lus 'byung pa las grol ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5377: med na'ang rnam smin mi btub ste /
NK076(mu)001:5378: rnam smin ni tshe snga ma'i las kyi rnam smin
NK076(mu)001:5379: las grub pa'i lhag ma'i lus dang ma bral ba
NK076(mu)001:5380: la zer bas so zhes pa la /
NK076(mu)001:5381: lan du kha cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:5382: bar do la thob pa'i rnam smin de lus kyi bag chags kyi tshul du yod /
NK076(mu)001:5383: dgongs pa lha'i skur gsal ba yin zhes zer ba ni mi 'thad do //
NK076(mu)001:5384: yid bag chags kyi lus la rnam smin sha khrag gi lus mi btub ste /
NK076(mu)001:5386: yang kha cig kha rag pa /
NK076(mu)001:5389: dgongs pa ni chos nyid do zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:5390: lus lha'i skur snang ba'i phyir phyag rgya chen po dang khyad med du 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:5391: bdag gi bla ma ni 'di la tshig gi 'jug pa gsum yod do //
NK076(mu)001:5392: bar do ru thob pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:5393: bar do la thob pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:5395: dang po ni tshe 'dir tshogs bsgrub kyang bden pa ma mthong ste /
NK076(mu)001:5397: lus dang bral ma thag du 'chi ba'i 'od gsal la brten pas mthong ste rnam smin thob bo /
NK076(mu)001:5398: bar do la thob pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:5399: 'chi ba'i 'od gsal kyang ngo ma shes te bar
NK076(mu)001:5400: do dngos kyi snang ba shar ba'i dus su spyod
NK076(mu)001:5401: yul sgyu mar mthong pa la brten nas bden pa
NK076(mu)001:5402: mthong ste rnam smin thob bo //
NK076(mu)001:5403: 'o na de gnyis la rnam smin grub pa'i lus
NK076(mu)001:5404: med pa rnam smin gyi nges tshig nyams so zhe
NK076(mu)001:5405: na / de ni rnam smin btags pa yin gyi 'byung ba las grub pa'i lus med mod kyi /
NK076(mu)001:5406: bden pa mthong ba tsam gyi cha nas 'jog go /
NK076(mu)001:5407: 'o na tshe dbang dang 'dra mod zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5408: ma yin te tshe dbang ni 'byung ba dngas ma'i lus su yod la /
NK076(mu)001:5409: 'dir ni bag chags kyi lus so //
NK076(mu)001:5410: phyag rgya chen po dang khyad ci yod zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5411: de ni lha'i sku'i cha lugs su yod cing /
NK076(mu)001:5412: rnam smin ni mi gzugs kyi bag chags su yod do //
NK076(mu)001:5413: bar do nas thob pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:5414: bar do'i snang ba nub ste lus len kar bden pa mthong ste /
NK076(mu)001:5415: de ni rnam smin gyi lus su 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)001:5416: dgongs pa lha'i skur gsal ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:5417: zhes gsungs pa ni re shig dpyad par bya mod
NK076(mu)001:5418: kyi bdag ni tshogs sgrubs pas rnam smin gyi rig
NK076(mu)001:5419: 'dzin tshe 'di la ma thob na bar do dag
NK076(mu)001:5420: la thob par 'dod pa ni slob dpon sangs rgyas
NK076(mu)001:5421: pa / nyid kyi gzhung gi dgongs pa ma lon zhing 'khrul par sems ste /
NK076(mu)001:5422: de dag rnam smin gyi mtshan nyid dang mi ldan pa'i phyir dang /
NK076(mu)001:5423: tshogs bsgrub nas zag med du sbyor ba la rnam
NK076(mu)001:5424: smin mtshan nyid pa la blo chung pa med pa'i
NK076(mu)001:5425: phyir dang / 'di nyid phyag rgya chen po la
NK076(mu)001:5426: sbyor ba'i srid pa tha ma pa yin pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:5427: phyir dang / / rim pa bzhin gyi ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:5429: lus kyi d+r+wa bas sgribs gyur zhing //
NK076(mu)001:5430: ka la ping ka mi 'jigs bzhin //
NK076(mu)001:5431: bral nas snang byed de rnam smin //
NK076(mu)001:5434: stobs chung skyed mos zhan pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:5435: rnam rtog 'byung ba'i lhag lus gzhag /ces pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:5437: rgya mig rgya ba ji lta bar //
NK076(mu)001:5438: phyag rgya thob la ma drag pa'i //
NK076(mu)001:5439: gzugs rdzogs stobs chen de kho na //
NK076(mu)001:5440: gang de bral lam thag pa ru //
NK076(mu)001:5441: rgya bzhi rdzogs par bdag 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:5443: sngar gyii sbyor dus ni lung kyang //
NK076(mu)001:5444: tshogs sbyor gyi dang po nas smin pa yin gyi /
NK076(mu)001:5445: tshogs sgrubs nas zag med la sbyor ba'i dus ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:5446: mtshan nyid theg pa'i tshogs sbyor la grangs med dang
NK076(mu)001:5447: po thogs pa las khyad par du bya ba'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:5448: / de lta ma yin na sngar tshogs 'grub pa'i
NK076(mu)001:5449: dus gsum smos pa don med du 'gyur ro snyam
NK076(mu)001:5450: / du sems so // rtsod pa spangs pa dang bcas pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:5451: rnam smin gyi rig 'dzin 'di lam gyi shan 'byed
NK076(mu)001:5452: pa'i dus su zag bcas yin nam zag med yin
NK076(mu)001:5453: drang / dang po ltar na mya ngan 'das par smin zhes brjod ces pa dang 'gal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:5454: chos nyid kyi bden pa ma mthong bar 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:5455: 'khor ba'i zag pa ma spang pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:5457: gnyis pa ltar na lus kyi d+r+wa bas sgrib gyur zhing /
NK076(mu)001:5458: zhes pas lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa yod par gsal lo zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5460: gzhan gyi 'dod pa sun dbyung pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:5461: rang gzhung dri ma rnam par bzhag pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:5462: dang po ni snga rabs kha zur tsham bsgres po cig na re /
NK076(mu)001:5463: spyir rnam smin la gnyis ste /
NK076(mu)001:5464: rang gi nga bo'i lus dang /
NK076(mu)001:5465: sgrib byed lhag ma'i lus so //
NK076(mu)001:5466: des na rnam smin dngos kyi lus ni /
NK076(mu)001:5467: lha'i skur gsal ba de nyid de zag med yin la /
NK076(mu)001:5468: sha khrag gi lus dang po la sgrib byed yin te /
NK076(mu)001:5470: seng ge'i mngal dang khyung gi sgong nga bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:5471: zhes zer ba ni mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:5472: de ltar na rnam smin lha'i skur gsal ba de lus yin nam yid yin /
NK076(mu)001:5473: yid yin na gcig spros pa'ang rnam smin du thal /
NK076(mu)001:5474: yid lhar gsal brtan thob pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5475: lus yin na de mi 'dor bar sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'gro bas lhag bcas su thal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:5476: yid kyi lha'i gzugs bzung zhing ces pa dang 'gal te /
NK076(mu)001:5477: rtag dang po nang gi mda' gcig ma 'dra gsung ngo //
NK076(mu)001:5478: yang kha cig na rlan re rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin 'di zag med yin te /
NK076(mu)001:5479: thugs thig las kyang rig 'dzin bzhi ka zag med du bshad /
NK076(mu)001:5481: spyir zag pa'i go ba ni lus khams skye gnas la bshad pa yin pas /
NK076(mu)001:5483: lus kyi zag pa 'di lus 'dis phyi ma mi bskyed /
NK076(mu)001:5484: khams dang skye gnas kyang de dang 'dra'o zhes phyir zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:5485: tshogs sgrub bgres po blo yang rab de'ang zag med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:5486: thod rgal du phyag rgya chen po la sbyor bas phyi ma'i zag pa gsum mi len pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:5489: spyis bye brag la khyab cing /
NK076(mu)001:5490: nad par 'gro ba la 'du ba gsum ka tshang
NK076(mu)001:5491: mi dgos pas lus kyi zag pa 'jug pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:5492: zag bcas su / bde zhes zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:5493: rnam smin 'di mya ngan las 'das pa yin nam min /
NK076(mu)001:5494: min na mya ngan 'das par smin zhes brjod ces pa dang 'gal lo //
NK076(mu)001:5495: yin na mya ngan 'das pa zag bcas su thal /
NK076(mu)001:5496: 'dod na zag pa zad nas 'jig rten 'das zhes pa gsal /
NK076(mu)001:5497: khyab pa ma grub na dam bca' nyams so //
NK076(mu)001:5498: yang kha cig na yang zheng re /
NK076(mu)001:5499: 'dug zag bcas su bdag kyang gda' zag med kyi khong su gdab ste /
NK076(mu)001:5500: dper na nya lcags kyus bzung ba'am /
NK076(mu)001:5501: skyes bu'i gnad du mtshon snun pa bzhin zhes zer ba mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:5502: dper ma grub cing don mi gnas so //
NK076(mu)001:5503: dang por ma grub ste skyes bu dang gcig nya
NK076(mu)001:5504: gnyis ka ma shi'i bar du gshin po'i khongs su
NK076(mu)001:5505: ci'i phyir 'debs / 'chi nges pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5506: sems can thams cad gshin por thal /
NK076(mu)001:5508: khyab pa med de myur du 'chi bas so zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5509: nyi tshe ba la sogs pa'i sems can tshe thung ba kun kyang gshin por thal lo //
NK076(mu)001:5510: don yang mi gnas te zag pa dang bral gyi bar du bgrang bar mi rigs so //
NK076(mu)001:5511: zag med du gyur nges pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5512: tshogs sgrub kyi skad cig rgyun mtha' yang zag med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:5513: zag med du 'gyur nges pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5514: yang lha rje nya ri chen po /
NK076(mu)001:5515: rnam smin la skye gnas kyi zag pa med pas zag med du 'dod pa yin gsung lo //
NK076(mu)001:5516: de ces na skye gnas kyi zag pa yod na lus dang khams kyang zhar la 'ong la /
NK076(mu)001:5517: skye gnas med na de gnyis kyang med pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:5518: skye gnas gtso bo che ba zer ba'ang mi 'thad
NK076(mu)001:5519: de / de tsam du rig 'dzin bzhi sangs rgyas su thal /
NK076(mu)001:5520: sgrib pa'i gtso bo nyon sgrib med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5521: nyon mongs sgrib pa med kyang shes bya'i sgrib pa
NK076(mu)001:5522: yod pas sangs rgyas su mi 'gro te khyab pa
NK076(mu)001:5524: rnam smin la'ang skye gnas kyi zag pa med kyang
NK076(mu)001:5525: lus khams kyi zag pa yod pas zag med du
NK076(mu)001:5526: mi 'gro na ci sto ste khyab pa ma grub
NK076(mu)001:5527: ces bya la / skye gnas la zag pa'i gtso bor bshad pa'ang med gsung ngo //
NK076(mu)001:5528: bdag gi ru ni kyi me nyag dang spar khab kyi rjes su 'brangs nas 'di ltar bzhed de /
NK076(mu)001:5529: spyir zag pa la gtso bo dang bran gnyis su gnas te /
NK076(mu)001:5530: gtso bo ni nyon mongs pa'i 'dzin pa yin te /
NK076(mu)001:5531: des 'khor bar zag pa'i rgyu'i sa bon drung por 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5532: bran ni lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa yin te /
NK076(mu)001:5533: de tsam gyis 'khor bar 'ching mi nus pa'i phyir bran du 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:5534: nyon mongs pa'i 'dzin pa la zag par bshad pa med par zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5536: spar khab de dag 'jig rten pa la yod pa
NK076(mu)001:5537: ni 'dzin pa'i phyir zag par 'gyur la zhes bshad
NK076(mu)001:5538: do // de bas na rnam smin la myang 'das kyi dang po mthong lam gyi khyab cing /
NK076(mu)001:5539: mthong lam la nyon sgrib spang pas khyab pa'i phyir zag med du 'jog ste /
NK076(mu)001:5540: mya ngan 'das par smin zhes brjod //
NK076(mu)001:5542: 'o na rig 'dzin bzhi la yang sgrib pa'i gtso
NK076(mu)001:5543: bo nyon sgrib med pas sangs rgyas su thal zhe
NK076(mu)001:5544: na / des ni mgo mi 'dre nyon mongs pa'i
NK076(mu)001:5545: 'dzin pa dang bral nas lus khams skye gnas kyi
NK076(mu)001:5546: zag pas 'khor bar 'ching mi nus shing skye na'ang
NK076(mu)001:5547: rang dbang can du byed la /
NK076(mu)001:5548: nyon sgrib med kyang shes bya'i sgrib pas lam du 'ching nus pa'i phyir sangs rgyas su mi 'agro'o //
NK076(mu)001:5549: gal te shes sgrib pas lam du 'ching pa bzhin
NK076(mu)001:5550: du lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pas kyang 'khor
NK076(mu)001:5552: byang chub sems dpa' chen po rang gzhan gyi don
NK076(mu)001:5553: du bsam bzhin srid pa'i skye ba nye bar blangs
NK076(mu)001:5554: pa dag kyang 'khor ba par thal /
NK076(mu)001:5555: lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa yod pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:5556: zhes gsung pa ni 'thad du rung gi phyogs su
NK076(mu)001:5558: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin la don bcu las /
NK076(mu)001:5559: dang po thob pa'i rgyu dus ni /
NK076(mu)001:5560: blo che bas shes rab gsum gyis chos nyid kyi
NK076(mu)001:5561: don la rtog gom khyad par du gyur pa'i tshul
NK076(mu)001:5562: gyis tshogs sgrub pa'i 'grub dus rgyud las bshad pa
NK076(mu)001:5563: las mi 'gyang par thob pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:5564: shes rab rnam gsum gom byas pas //
NK076(mu)001:5565: ting 'dzin mnyam pa'i don rtogs te //
NK076(mu)001:5566: kun rgyu yangs pa chen por bsgom //
NK076(mu)001:5567: shes 'jug lnga rtogs gom pa ni //
NK076(mu)001:5568: zla zhag brgyud bzhin bsgrub 'dod pa //
NK076(mu)001:5569: rdo rje'i lus su the tshom med //
NK076(mu)001:5571: rang gi ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:5573: zhar la tshe tshad bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:5574: dang po chos nyid kyi don rang gi mtshan nyid
NK076(mu)001:5575: du gsal ba'i ngo bor bskyed dbyung du med par
NK076(mu)001:5576: mthong zhing zag pa kun zad de /
NK076(mu)001:5577: 'pho 'dzin 'jig dpyad med pa rdo rje'i lus su gyur pa te /
NK076(mu)001:5578: don mthong 'jug pa mthar phyin pa //
NK076(mu)001:5579: tshogs spyod bsgrub pa'i dngos su kyis //
NK076(mu)001:5580: lus khams skye gnas zag pa zad //
NK076(mu)001:5584: bdag don du stong drug gi bar du gnas zhing /
NK076(mu)001:5585: gzhan don du tshe la dbang thob pa'i tshul gyis ji ltar 'dod bzhin phyir bsgyur ba nus te /
NK076(mu)001:5586: bdag phyir don du gnyer ba ni //
NK076(mu)001:5587: brgya phrag bcu drug tshe yi rdzogs //
NK076(mu)001:5588: gzhan gyi don du bya ba ni //
NK076(mu)001:5589: brgya brgya dag du bsgyur zhing gnas //
NK076(mu)001:5591: rnam grangs rnam par dbye na bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:5592: sman las grub pa'i tshe dbang dang //
NK076(mu)001:5593: thabs las grub pa'i tshe dbang dang //
NK076(mu)001:5594: sgron ma rlung las grub pa'i tshe dbang dang //
NK076(mu)001:5595: lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang te //
NK076(mu)001:5596: ngo bo sman dang thabs rig 'dzin //
NK076(mu)001:5598: lam mchog rdzogs pa'i rim pa bzhi //
NK076(mu)001:5600: spyod pa ni rang don du shes rab gsum la spyod cing /
NK076(mu)001:5601: gzhan don du cho 'phrul bzhi dang phrin las bzhi la sogs pa ston te /
NK076(mu)001:5602: gsang thos bsam rig sgom sbyor bas //
NK076(mu)001:5603: dkyus sar phyin pa'i cang shes bzhin //
NK076(mu)001:5604: kun tu 'gro ba bdag po'i don //
NK076(mu)001:5605: rdzu 'phrul chos snang rjes ston spyod //
NK076(mu)001:5607: cha lugs ni rang gi ngo bo skye 'jig med pa rdo rje'i lus la /
NK076(mu)001:5608: zhes sprul pa ni lha mi gtod rims kyi cha byad du bstan pa don byed de /
NK076(mu)001:5610: dbang bsgyur rtsa ba rdo rje'i lus //
NK076(mu)001:5613: lha dang mi dang tshangs pa yi //
NK076(mu)001:5614: skye ba rnam dag 'dzin mod kyang //
NK076(mu)001:5615: khyad par sa la gnas gyur yin //
NK076(mu)001:5618: mngon shes kyi yul don ni /
NK076(mu)001:5619: spyi'i mngon par shes pa drug dang /
NK076(mu)001:5620: bye brag tu sgo dpyad snod lnga'i dbang shes nyi
NK076(mu)001:5621: shu rtsa lngas gling bzhi bye ba phrag brgya sprul
NK076(mu)001:5623: mnyam pa yul du gyur cing de nyid kyi don byed par nus te /
NK076(mu)001:5624: sngon bzhin yul khyon 'dul bar byed //
NK076(mu)001:5625: skye mched rang byung ye shes phyir //
NK076(mu)001:5626: de nyid gcig dang du ma'i mtha' //gnyis su med par mngon rtog gom //
NK076(mu)001:5627: mthong pas dri ma drug sbyangs phyir //
NK076(mu)001:5628: de nyid gzugs sgra dri ro reg /shes pa'i bye brag rtsa lngar bshad //
NK076(mu)001:5629: gcig gi yul lnga gcod byed pa'i //
NK076(mu)001:5630: tshang dang ma tshang 'jig dgos med //
NK076(mu)001:5631: gzhan du lha'i rna ba dang //
NK076(mu)001:5632: spyan gyi mngon par shes pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:5633: sngon gnas rjes su dran pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:5634: pha rol rnams kyi sems shes dang //
NK076(mu)001:5636: rdzu 'phrul shes pa'am zag zad shes //
NK076(mu)001:5637: de rnyed tshun chad yul shes pa //
NK076(mu)001:5638: gang dang gang rnams 'dul bar mdzad //
NK076(mu)001:5639: de phyir mi ldog zag med de //
NK076(mu)001:5640: dbang bskur rigs kyi cha la brjod //
NK076(mu)001:5643: rang gzhan gyi don du tshe la dbang thob pa'i
NK076(mu)001:5644: sgo nas mnyam bzhag du mi bzlog pa'i ting nge
NK076(mu)001:5645: 'dzin la gnas pa de rim gyis so thod rgal
NK076(mu)001:5646: gyi tshul gyi lam dang mthar lam dang ci rigs
NK076(mu)001:5647: su sbyor te / bdag gom gzhan phyir dbang can des /
NK076(mu)001:5648: sku tshe'i tshad dam ji snyed par //
NK076(mu)001:5649: bzhugs mthar rang gi bsgrub sbyor ba /
NK076(mu)001:5650: sngon bzhin rim dang rims min pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:5653: dbang sgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK076(mu)001:5655: mtshan nyid theg pa'i sa lam dang sbyar na /
NK076(mu)001:5656: mthong lam sa dang po'i bden pa dang mo tshod snyam te /
NK076(mu)001:5657: rgyu'i dang por skal mnyam mo //
NK076(mu)001:5659: rang dbang thob pa'i dbugs thob phyir //
NK076(mu)001:5660: skabs 'dir bden pa bar ma mthong //
NK076(mu)001:5663: tshe dbang phyag rgya chen po la sbyor ba'i dus
NK076(mu)001:5664: rdo rje'i lus de 'bor ram de ka ltar khyer
NK076(mu)001:5665: / dang po ltar na lhag bcas ma yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:5666: gnyis pa ltar na phyag rgya chen po lha'i sgyu
NK076(mu)001:5667: ma'i cha lugs su yod pa'i phyir rdo rje'i lus
NK076(mu)001:5668: tha mal gyi cha lugs dang mi mtshungs so zhe
NK076(mu)001:5669: na / ma yin te 'bor yang mi 'bor la /
NK076(mu)001:5670: de kho na bzhin du'ang mi 'khyer de /
NK076(mu)001:5671: rdo rje'i lus de nyid ye shes sgyu ma'i skur gnas 'gyur ba ni /
NK076(mu)001:5672: dper na gser dngul gyi gang bu bzhu btul byas nas lha'i skur byas pa bzhin no gsung /
NK076(mu)001:5673: yang tshe dbang de bdag don du lo stong drug brgyad sdod pa min nam /
NK076(mu)001:5674: min na sdod par bshad pa dang 'gal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:5675: yin na tshe dbang las rnam smin blo che bar thal /
NK076(mu)001:5676: phyag rgya chen po la sbyor ba rnams smin myur ba'i phyir rtags khyab ni /
NK076(mu)001:5677: gang dag blo chen mo na rtogs pas /
NK076(mu)001:5678: brgyud de cig char gang 'jug pa zhes pas 'grub cing 'dod na /
NK076(mu)001:5679: stobs chung bskyed smos zhan pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:5680: rnam rtog 'byung ba'i lhag lus gzhag ces pas gsal lo zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5682: rgyu gong ma ni gdam ngag tu rang don du'ang
NK076(mu)001:5683: phyag rgya chen po la nam sbyor kyang rang dbang
NK076(mu)001:5684: yod de / tshe la dbang ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:5686: bdag gam gzhan phyir dbang can des /
NK076(mu)001:5687: zhes pas mngon no gsung skad do //
NK076(mu)001:5688: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la don bcu las /
NK076(mu)001:5689: dang po thob pa'i rgyu dus ni /
NK076(mu)001:5690: gcig spros kyi ting nge'i la gom pa'i rgyun dang /
NK076(mu)001:5691: lta ba ched 'dzin gyi ched snang kun 'gro'i sgrib
NK076(mu)001:5692: pa dag pa'i sgo nas dus nges pa med par
NK076(mu)001:5693: phyag rgya chen por yin gyi /
NK076(mu)001:5694: rgyu 'bras mi 'dra bar skyes pa ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:5695: gcig dang du ma'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK076(mu)001:5696: 'byung lus sems phyir rang bzhin lta //
NK076(mu)001:5697: mthong gom bsags pa'i mthar sgrubs pas //
NK076(mu)001:5698: kun 'gro'i sgrib dag ngo bo'i rgyu //
NK076(mu)001:5700: rang gi ngo bo ni sngon du gang gom pa'i
NK076(mu)001:5701: lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po rigs lnga gang rung
NK076(mu)001:5702: gi cha lugs 'dzin cing mi g.yo ba'i ting nges
NK076(mu)001:5703: lhan ga cig gnas pa'i dri ma spangs pa la
NK076(mu)001:5704: zhugs pa ste / rang lugs gdod nas phyag rgya che //
NK076(mu)001:5705: bsgom pas mngon du gyur pa'i lha //
NK076(mu)001:5706: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen dang //
NK076(mu)001:5709: ye shes sku'i cha lugs can //
NK076(mu)001:5710: 'byung ba rdo rje'i lus las grol //
NK076(mu)001:5712: dbye na kri ya'i phyag rgya chen po rigs gsum dang //
NK076(mu)001:5713: u pa ya'i rigs bzhi dang //
NK076(mu)001:5715: ma h+aa yo ga'i mchog lnga ste //
NK076(mu)001:5716: de nyid rigs gsum rigs bzhi dang //
NK076(mu)001:5717: lnga dang mchog lnga'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK076(mu)001:5720: rang don dgongs pa las mi g.yo bar byed cing /
NK076(mu)001:5721: gzhan don sprul pa'i lus rngon pa dang smad 'tshong
NK076(mu)001:5722: la sogs par kyang bstan nas dag ma dag kun
NK076(mu)001:5724: mnyam bzhag ngang las ma g.yos bzhin //
NK076(mu)001:5725: zhing grangs med pa brgya stong phrag /bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK076(mu)001:5726: rngon dpyad mngon dang smad 'tshong la sogs pa //
NK076(mu)001:5727: sprul pa'i lus kyi 'dul bar byed //
NK076(mu)001:5729: mngon shes kyi yul don nam /
NK076(mu)001:5730: sngar tshe dbang pas gsal brtan bas khyab par snang
NK076(mu)001:5731: zhing longs sku'i zhing khams dang mnyam pa yul du
NK076(mu)001:5732: gyur la don yang de snyed du byed pa nus
NK076(mu)001:5733: te / drug dang lnga'i yan lag bcas //
NK076(mu)001:5734: shes pa'ang 'dra mod bzhi rtsogs kun //
NK076(mu)001:5735: de snyed yul gyi khyad par dang //
NK076(mu)001:5736: don rdzogs mthu dang gdul byas spags /
NK076(mu)001:5739: de ltar snang stong dbyer med ting nge 'dzin la
NK076(mu)001:5740: mnyam rjes zung 'brel du gom par byas pas lhan
NK076(mu)001:5741: gcig gnas pa phra mo'i dri ma dag par byas
NK076(mu)001:5742: shing mthar lam 'bad med du thob pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:5743: rang rig mi g.yo mthong gol dang //
NK076(mu)001:5744: don du gnyer rims rtsol ba ni //
NK076(mu)001:5745: lam kun rdzogs pa'i byin stobs kyis //
NK076(mu)001:5746: lhan ga cig gnas pa'i dri ma dag /rnal 'byor bral nas lhun gyis grub /
NK076(mu)001:5747: rtsol ba med par lhun grub thob //
NK076(mu)001:5750: gnyis med gyur na phyag rgya che /
NK076(mu)001:5752: mtshan nyid zhig theg dpyad pa'i sa lam dang sbyar na /
NK076(mu)001:5753: sa na gnyis pa ni nas dpyad dgu pa'i bar dang mo tshod mnyam ste /
NK076(mu)001:5754: gnyis pa'i rig chog 'dzin pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:5755: brgyad pa'i sems dpa' skal mnyam mo //
NK076(mu)001:5757: lam ni sgom lam pa ste /
NK076(mu)001:5758: phyag rgya chen po bsgom pa'i lam //
NK076(mu)001:5759: mi g.yo'i rnal 'byor nyid du brjod //
NK076(mu)001:5761: dgos bsal dang rtsod spong med do //
NK076(mu)001:5762: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin la don bcu las /
NK076(mu)001:5763: dang po thob pa'i rgyu dus ni /
NK076(mu)001:5764: bsgom pa'i lam gyi rgyun dang longs sku la brten
NK076(mu)001:5765: pa'i shes rab gsum brgyud la brten pa'i dus nyid
NK076(mu)001:5766: du ste / snga ma'i rigs la mthu rdzogs pas //
NK076(mu)001:5767: bshad pa bzhin du d+r+wa mi dag /sangs rgyas gnyis pa'i shes rab gsum //
NK076(mu)001:5768: lhun gyis grub pa'i rigs su 'byung //
NK076(mu)001:5769: rang gi dgongs spyod nus pa can //
NK076(mu)001:5770: sa mthar dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK076(mu)001:5772: rang gi ngo bo ni sku lnga lhun grub kyi
NK076(mu)001:5773: rgyal tshab dbyer med lam gyi rtogs pa mthar phyin
NK076(mu)001:5774: pa'i rang bzhin can sangs rgyas kyi sa thob ma
NK076(mu)001:5775: rag pa ste / de dag ltar dag pa'i shes pa nyid /
NK076(mu)001:5776: sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje 'dzin //
NK076(mu)001:5777: lhun mnyam ngang la mi g.yo zhing //
NK076(mu)001:5778: mi rtogs ngang du bzhugs na'ang //
NK076(mu)001:5779: bag la nyal ba 'joms byed cing //
NK076(mu)001:5780: skad cig rag las rig 'dzin mtha'o /
NK076(mu)001:5782: rnam grangs rnam par dbye na /
NK076(mu)001:5786: lhun grub kyi rgyal tshab rnam pa gsum ste /
NK076(mu)001:5787: bya ba lhun grub kyi rnal 'byor gyi //
NK076(mu)001:5791: rang don sku lnga lhun grub kyi rgyal ba legs
NK076(mu)001:5792: par brten zhing sgrib spong ba'i phyir shes rab gsum
NK076(mu)001:5793: brgyud la brten zhing slob la /
NK076(mu)001:5794: gzhan don du sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams mthar thug
NK076(mu)001:5795: med dag du sprul pa'i mdzad pa sna tshogs su
NK076(mu)001:5796: ston cing gsang ba'i bsdud pa po mdzad /
NK076(mu)001:5797: nyid kyi rdo rje 'dzin rtsogs la /
NK076(mu)001:5798: skad cig dus kyi bslab pa rdzogs //
NK076(mu)001:5799: de tshe sgrib pa'i cha yod kyang /
NK076(mu)001:5800: lhun grub rig 'dzin sar bzhugs nas //
NK076(mu)001:5801: zhing khams mthar thug med pa dag /gdul phyir sprul sku'i mdzad pa ston //
NK076(mu)001:5802: gsang ba'i tan tra'ang ston byed cing //
NK076(mu)001:5803: de bzhin bsdu ba mdzad pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:5805: cha lugs ni sku lnga lhun grub kyi rgyal ba nyid kyi tshul 'dzin te /
NK076(mu)001:5806: cha byed rgyal ba nyid du ste de 'dra de nyid rgyal tshab ston //
NK076(mu)001:5808: mngon shes kyi yul don ni /
NK076(mu)001:5809: ji snyed mkhyen pa'i yul che long du rgyal ba
NK076(mu)001:5810: nyid dang mtshungs shing nam mkha'i khyab tshad kyi don
NK076(mu)001:5811: yang ci rigs par byed de /
NK076(mu)001:5812: kun mkhyen ye shes lnga'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:5813: yul ni tshad med rgyal ba nyid //
NK076(mu)001:5814: ji ltar me long lta bu'i tshul //
NK076(mu)001:5817: lhun grub kyi skad cig rgyun gyi tha ma la
NK076(mu)001:5818: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin bdag tu rtog
NK076(mu)001:5819: pa bzang ngan gyi mtshan ma'i bag chags tha ma
NK076(mu)001:5820: shes bya'i sgrib pa cha phra ba yang bcom ste
NK076(mu)001:5821: / b+hud+d+ha nyid kyi sar sbyor nyid de /
NK076(mu)001:5822: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis /
NK076(mu)001:5823: bdag rtogs mtshan ma kun bcom nas //
NK076(mu)001:5824: rdo rje'i dbyings su thim par byed //
NK076(mu)001:5825: rgyan gyi da la ma d+ha la //
NK076(mu)001:5826: bsam yas kun rdzogs kun mkhyen mdzod //
NK076(mu)001:5829: rang byung sku lnga lhun gyis grub //
NK076(mu)001:5831: 'og ma'i sa lam dang sbyar na /
NK076(mu)001:5832: sa bcu pa chos kyi sprin lam ni mthar lam ste /
NK076(mu)001:5833: sa bcu sa gsum dang mnyam mo //
NK076(mu)001:5835: de nyid dang ni mthar sbyor lam zhes so //
NK076(mu)001:5836: zhar las byung ba'i log rtog ni /
NK076(mu)001:5838: lhun gyi grub pa'i rig 'dzin de dgongs pa la
NK076(mu)001:5839: mnyam pa'i dus su sangs rgyas dang khyad med kyi
NK076(mu)001:5840: mnyam pa la bzhag 'jog yod pa tsam gyis khyab
NK076(mu)001:5841: pa du byas so zer ro //
NK076(mu)001:5843: gsang ba'i bye brag rim par 'gro zhes pas /
NK076(mu)001:5844: lam rims kyi sa'i dus su rdzogs lta bar rtog
NK076(mu)001:5845: pa'i rang gi ngo bo la khyad yod par bshad
NK076(mu)001:5846: pa yin nam / yin na mnyam pa la bzhag pa'i dus su'ang khyad yod par thal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5847: rtog pa'i ngo bo la khyad yod pa'ang cis //
NK076(mu)001:5848: rtogs tshul gyi khyad yod pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:5849: mnyam pa la bzhag pa'i phyir dus su khyad yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5851: mnyam pa la ma bzhag pa'i dus na khyad yod
NK076(mu)001:5852: pa'i gnad kas shes bya'i sgrib pa phra mo rgyun
NK076(mu)001:5854: mnyam par bzhag pa'i dus su'ang khyad yod de /
NK076(mu)001:5855: de gnyen po rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge de
NK076(mu)001:5856: bcom nas sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'gro ba'i phyir
NK076(mu)001:5857: zhes gsungs ngo // rtsod pa spang pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:5858: 'dir rdo rje lta bu ting nges shes sgrib spang pa'i tshe gnyen po spong bya spang ngam /
NK076(mu)001:5859: de gnyen spang bya dag pa'i shul du gnyen po skye /
NK076(mu)001:5860: dang po ltar na rdo rje lta bu skyes tsam
NK076(mu)001:5861: na spang bya shes sgrib yod dam med yod na
NK076(mu)001:5862: spang gnyen dngos 'gal ma yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:5863: shes rgyun cig la lhan cig du 'tshogs pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:5864: 'dod na gnyen po don med du 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:5865: med pa'am dag pa'i shul du gang skyes kyang don med 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:5866: spang bya med pa'i phyir mun pa sangs pa'i shul gyi snang byed bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:5867: lan ni gnyen po skyes pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:5868: spangs bya spangs pa dus mnyam ste //
NK076(mu)001:5869: mun pa dang mar me bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:5871: yang rig 'dzin bzhi po lam mthar thug gi 'bras bu yin nam min /
NK076(mu)001:5872: min na mthar phyin 'bras bu mtshan nyid bshad ces pa dang 'gal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:5873: yin na sangs rgyas dang khyad med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:5875: sangs rgyas spangs rtogs rnams mthar thug pa yin la /
NK076(mu)001:5877: da dung phra ba'i sgrib pa dag ma spangs par ldan pa'i phyir ro ce na /
NK076(mu)001:5878: lan ni 'bras bu la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:5879: lam du gyur 'bras mthar thug 'bras zhes gsungs pas /
NK076(mu)001:5880: rig 'dzin bzhi ni lam du gyur pa'i 'bras bu
NK076(mu)001:5881: ste 'dir zag bcas kyi lam mthar phyin pa'i 'bras
NK076(mu)001:5883: mthar thug gi 'bras bu mtshan nyid pa sangs rgyas kyi sa nyid de /
NK076(mu)001:5884: de las bskyed du byar med pas so //
NK076(mu)001:5885: rig 'dzin bzhi ni lam du gyur pa'i sgrib par
NK076(mu)001:5886: rags pa spangs pa tsam la'ang 'bras bur ming brtags
NK076(mu)001:5887: te / lha mo skye med bzhin no zhes gsung ngo //
NK076(mu)001:5889: spyi don gsum pa shes bya 'bras bu'i don la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:5896: dang po la yang gnyis ste /
NK076(mu)001:5897: dngos dang rtsod pa spang pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:5898: dang po ni spangs thob med par rang snang du sngon du byas pa'o //
NK076(mu)001:5900: lam rim ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK076(mu)001:5901: gzhan nas yod 'ongs ma yin te //
NK076(mu)001:5902: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK076(mu)001:5903: de lta bu'i ngang du spyod //
NK076(mu)001:5907: 'bras bu thob pa'i tshe gzhi'i dus kyi ma rig
NK076(mu)001:5908: pa spangs sam ma spangs kyi brtag pa ni gzhi'i
NK076(mu)001:5910: gnyis pa ni mthar thug gi 'bras bu dang theg
NK076(mu)001:5911: pa rim pa dgu'i 'bras bu la khyad par yod
NK076(mu)001:5912: dam med drangs / khyad med na rgyu'i theg pa'i
NK076(mu)001:5913: 'bras bu de gsang sngags kyi 'ang mthar thug tu
NK076(mu)001:5914: dam med drangs / 'gyur pas / de nas gsang sngags la bgrod mi dgos par thal /
NK076(mu)001:5916: 'dod na khyod kyi 'bras bu kun tu 'od /
NK076(mu)001:5917: thabs chen theg pa'i gting bsti dpyad gnas pa //
NK076(mu)001:5920: kun tu 'od la gnas pa las pad ma can du 'gyur zhes /
NK076(mu)001:5921: da sdod gsang sngags du bgrod //
NK076(mu)001:5922: dgos par gsungs pas gsal lo //
NK076(mu)001:5923: gnyis pa ltar tha dad na'ang dgongs 'dus las /
NK076(mu)001:5924: gsang nyid nges pa 'jug par du /
NK076(mu)001:5925: theg pa'i sgo'ang bsam mi khyab //
NK076(mu)001:5926: gsang nyid snying por nges pa na //
NK076(mu)001:5927: theg pa'i sgo'ang ga cig las med /
NK076(mu)001:5929: gsang sngags nyid ring lam du'ang 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)001:5930: thun mong gi 'bras bu thob zin nas kyang bgrod dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5932: lan ni 'dod pas bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu re re
NK076(mu)001:5933: thun mong gi theg pa kun gyis kyang mi bslu
NK076(mu)001:5934: bar thob pas / tha dad par bshad pa dang yang mi 'gal te /
NK076(mu)001:5935: nor bu phal pa'i gling don grub pa'i bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:5936: mthar thug bla na med pa'i 'bras bu gcig du
NK076(mu)001:5937: gyur pas gcig par bshad pa dang mi 'gal te
NK076(mu)001:5938: / nor bu yid bzhin gyi gling don grub pa bzhin zhes gsungs mod kyi /
NK076(mu)001:5939: bdag ni 'dir gsang sngags kyi lam du 'bras bu
NK076(mu)001:5940: bde zhing myur bar thob pa'i thabs kyis khyad par
NK076(mu)001:5941: du byas shing / dmigs yul mthar thug gi 'bras
NK076(mu)001:5942: bu sku gsum ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid can thams
NK076(mu)001:5943: cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang bla na med pa de
NK076(mu)001:5944: ni rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa chen po gnyis kar
NK076(mu)001:5945: yang khyad par cung zad kyang med par sems te
NK076(mu)001:5946: du byas shing / / rtogs bya don gyi mthar
NK076(mu)001:5947: thug bdag med gnyis las zlog phyogs gzhan du grub
NK076(mu)001:5950: dus bzhi phyogs bcu gang nas kyang //
NK076(mu)001:5951: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:5952: sems nyid rtogs pas sangs rgyas te //
NK076(mu)001:5953: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma 'tshol cig /ces pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:5955: legs par sgrub pa'i rgyud ste /
NK076(mu)001:5956: don ga cig na'ang ma rmongs dang //
NK076(mu)001:5957: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:5958: dbang po rnon bos rkyen byas nas //
NK076(mu)001:5959: sngags kyi gdams pa khyad par 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:5962: theg pa gcig cing lugs kyang ga cig /gtso bo'i
NK076(mu)001:5963: stan pa 'di yang gcig /gang du theg pa gsum
NK076(mu)001:5964: bstan pa // nga ni thabs la mkhas pa'i dngos //
NK076(mu)001:5966: de'i phyir tha dad par gsungs pa'i lung rnams ni
NK076(mu)001:5967: rgyu'i theg pa dag rang gi 'bras bu la khyad
NK076(mu)001:5968: par can du dmigs shing rlom pa dag zhe dam
NK076(mu)001:5969: dag pa'i tshul gyis 'dir bzhugs pa'i dgongs pa can
NK076(mu)001:5971: gnyis pa mtshan nyid la gnyis ste /
NK076(mu)001:5974: sems tsam pa ltar tha dad pa /
NK076(mu)001:5975: dbu ma ba ltar gaca ga du bral 'dod pa min ste /
NK076(mu)001:5977: chu la chu thim pa ltar /
NK076(mu)001:5978: dang po ni ga cig du ma lags pa'i gzung
NK076(mu)001:5979: yul las grol zhing mthar thams cad dang bral bar
NK076(mu)001:5982: gcig dang du ma bral ba'o //
NK076(mu)001:5983: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK076(mu)001:5986: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams dgongs pa gcig gam tha dad //
NK076(mu)001:5987: dang po ltar na'ang snang phyogs su ga cig gam /
NK076(mu)001:5990: dang po ltar na sangs rgyas gzung 'dzin can du thal /
NK076(mu)001:5991: snang ldan gyi rdzas ma spangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5992: gnyis pa ltar na 'gog 'bras dang khyad med du thal /
NK076(mu)001:5993: stong pa gcig pu bar grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5994: gsum pa ltar na ye shes dang ye shes kyi khyad par yang mi rung par thal /
NK076(mu)001:5995: thams cad du dbyer med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:5996: yang tha dad na'ang ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:5997: rgyal tshab lnga la rigs yod de /
NK076(mu)001:5998: yang dag rdzogs sangs rgyas la med ces so //
NK076(mu)001:5999: mthar thug gi 'bras bu la rigs dbyer med du gsungs pa dang 'gal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:6000: gnas kyi ma rig pa yang ma spangs par thal te /
NK076(mu)001:6001: chos nyid gzhi'i dus na rgyud ga cig tha dad las grol ba las /
NK076(mu)001:6002: de'i don ma rig pa tha dad du snang ba'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:6004: spyir sangs rgyas kyi sa rgyud gcig dang tha dad las grol bar gnas te /
NK076(mu)001:6005: gcig ma spangs du mar snang ba'i phyir gcig gi
NK076(mu)001:6006: mtha' las grol ba ni chu snod bum du snang
NK076(mu)001:6007: ba'i zla ba lta bu dang /
NK076(mu)001:6008: du ma ma spangs gcig du gnas pa'i phyir du
NK076(mu)001:6009: ma'i mtha' las grol ba ni nam mkha' dang cho
NK076(mu)001:6010: 'phrul lta bu'o // de ltar na'ang khyab byed gcig
NK076(mu)001:6011: ma grub pas des khyad par du byas pa'i khyab
NK076(mu)001:6012: byed du ma'ang lo zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:6014: gcig med du ma zer ba min /
NK076(mu)001:6015: gcig ma spangs du ma'i mtha'i las grol bas du ma med ces bya /
NK076(mu)001:6016: du ma spangs gcig gi mtha' las grol bas gcig med ces bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:6017: des na skyon mtha' dag las grol ba'o gsung /
NK076(mu)001:6018: rnam grangs la gsum ste ming gi rnam grangs dang /
NK076(mu)001:6023: lam rim thun mong min pa'i rgyal ming grangs //
NK076(mu)001:6024: bde gshegs de bzhin gshegs pa ste //
NK076(mu)001:6025: bcom ldan 'das dang sangs rgyas dang //
NK076(mu)001:6026: dgyes chen brjod stsol bsam mi khyab //
NK076(mu)001:6028: ngo bo'i rnam grangs la bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:6029: rgyas par dbye na sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab ste ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:6030: kun du sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang //
NK076(mu)001:6031: zhes pa la sogs pa gsung ngo //
NK076(mu)001:6032: 'bring du dbye na sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK076(mu)001:6033: las re re la lnga lngar phye ba nyi shu
NK076(mu)001:6034: rtsa lngar ste ji skad du //
NK076(mu)001:6035: nyi shu lngar bsdus mtha' yas rnams //
NK076(mu)001:6037: bsdus te dbye na sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga ste /
NK076(mu)001:6038: de dag gi don ni ji skad du mdo /
NK076(mu)001:6039: brten byed pas na sku nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:6040: go brda' spros pas na gsung nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:6041: rig cing mkhyen pas na thugs nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:6042: dgos 'dod 'byung bas yon tan nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:6043: bya ba byed pas phrin las nyid do //
NK076(mu)001:6045: shin tu bsdus na brten sku dang brten pa'i ye shes so //
NK076(mu)001:6047: rang don rtogs pa'i mthar phyin pa'i ngo bo dbyings
NK076(mu)001:6048: thog tu rig pa'i ye shes grol ba'i rang bzhin
NK076(mu)001:6049: chos kyi sku / chos thams cad rig pa'i ngang
NK076(mu)001:6050: du skyon med par chub par rtogs pa mngon byang
NK076(mu)001:6051: chos kyi sku / gi sku / brten lus nyid
NK076(mu)001:6052: zag med du gyur pa'i rgyu 'bras 'od kyi mtshan
NK076(mu)001:6053: dpe dang ldan pa'i las dag pa'i las can la
NK076(mu)001:6054: snang ba ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku /
NK076(mu)001:6055: ma dag pa'i ngo la cha lugs dang mdzad pa
NK076(mu)001:6056: du mar snang ni byed pa dang ldan pa sprul
NK076(mu)001:6057: pa'i sku / de dag kyang tha mi dad de
NK076(mu)001:6058: snang stong dbyer med du gyur pa ni rdo rje'i
NK076(mu)001:6059: pa'i sku / sku zhes bya'o // brten pa'i ye shes de la dbye ba'i don dngos /
NK076(mu)001:6062: kun gzhi sa bon gyi cha'i gnas 'gyur /
NK076(mu)001:6063: cing yang mi dmigs pa chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
NK076(mu)001:6064: de nyid rnam smin shes dpyad gyis cha'i gnas 'gyur
NK076(mu)001:6065: snang la mi rtog pa me long lta bu'i ye
NK076(mu)001:6066: shes / nyon mongs yid gnas 'gyur bzang ngan blang dor med pa mnyam nyid kyi ye shes /
NK076(mu)001:6067: yid gnas 'gyur shes bya'i yul dus gsum gyi chos
NK076(mu)001:6068: thams cad gsal la ma 'dres pa rma'i pad+ma'i dpyad
NK076(mu)001:6069: 'dab ma ltar rtogs pa so sor rtogs pa'i ye
NK076(mu)001:6070: shes des bdag gzhan gyi don 'bad pa med par
NK076(mu)001:6071: lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes sgo lnga gnas 'gyur
NK076(mu)001:6072: / de dag nges 'byed kyi lung ni ha cang
NK076(mu)001:6073: mngas kyis dogs nas 'dir ma spros kyi gnas gzhan
NK076(mu)001:6077: mdo las mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi skad cig la
NK076(mu)001:6078: ma 'ongs pa dang 'das pa'i chos snang ngam mi
NK076(mu)001:6080: mkhyen pa'i ye shes gcig nyid kyis /
NK076(mu)001:6081: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor kun khyab can //
NK076(mu)001:6083: dus gsum mkhyen par mi 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:6084: snang na'ang 'gags pa dang ma skyes pa'i med chos
NK076(mu)001:6085: mngon gsum du mkhyen pa'i phyir gzung don la 'khrul
NK076(mu)001:6086: pa'i log shes su 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:6090: da lta ba skyes la ma 'gags par mkhyen pas
NK076(mu)001:6091: nyes pa med do ces gsungs pa ni mkhas pa'i
NK076(mu)001:6092: bla ma gzhan gyi man ngag de'o go /yang thams
NK076(mu)001:6093: cad gnyis pa / mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas kyis lam ma sbyang ba'i rgyud dag mkhyen nam mi mkhyen /
NK076(mu)001:6094: gnyis pa ltar na sems can thams cad 'bad med du grol bar mdzad par rigs la /
NK076(mu)001:6095: dang po ltar na kun mkhyen nyams so zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:6096: dang po ltar gyi lan ni /
NK076(mu)001:6097: mkhyen par 'os pa'i srid pa ma lus par mkhyen zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:6098: 'o na chos ma byas par grol bar mkhyen nam mi mkhyen ce na /
NK076(mu)001:6100: thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin par thal zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:6101: chos ma byas par grol ba ni 'os shing srid pa ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:6102: 'os shing srid pa dag mkhyen pa ma yin par
NK076(mu)001:6103: mi 'gyur na ci sto ste khyab pa ma grub
NK076(mu)001:6105: de tsam du lha'i bzo bo byi shwa karma des
NK076(mu)001:6106: 'jig rten gyi bzo gnas ma lus par mkhyen pa
NK076(mu)001:6107: yin nam / yin na rkyen gyis ma bcol ba'i bzo shes sam mi shes /
NK076(mu)001:6108: dang po ltar na rgyu 'tshogs pa tsam gyis so //
NK076(mu)001:6109: bdag gi 'dod bya grub par thal /
NK076(mu)001:6110: rkyen la ltos med du shes pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:6111: mi shes na bzo gnas ma lus par shes pa ma yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:6113: kho na re rkyen dang ma 'tshogs par bzo ga la 'ong /
NK076(mu)001:6114: rgyu rkyen 'tshogs pa'i bzo ma lus par mkhyen pa nyid do zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:6115: 'dir kyang chos ye nas ma byas par ga na mkhyen /
NK076(mu)001:6116: chos byas na dbang po rno brtul gyi rim pa
NK076(mu)001:6117: dang bstun nas dus nye ba dang ring par grol
NK076(mu)001:6118: ba ci rigs su mkhyen pa nyid do ces bya'o
NK076(mu)001:6119: gsungs / gzhan don mdzad pa'i 'bras bu la gsum /
NK076(mu)001:6120: gdul bya la thugs rjes gzigs pa'i tshul dang /
NK076(mu)001:6121: gzigs nas thugs rje skyes pa'i tshul dang skyes nas don mdzad tshul lo //
NK076(mu)001:6123: ye shes rgyun chad nas mi gzigs par thal 'gyur pa 'dod pa'i lugs dang /
NK076(mu)001:6124: rgyun ma rang rgyud chad cing gzigs par 'dod pa'i lugs //
NK076(mu)001:6125: cig char gyi mtha' dang bral bas las yul med rang gsal du gzigs par 'dod pa'i lugs so //
NK076(mu)001:6130: spyir sangs rgyas la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)001:6133: 'dir mtshan nyid pa ni chos kyi sku ste /
NK076(mu)001:6134: dper na bsregs bya bud shing zad pa'i tshe bsre byed me'i rgyun yang mi gnas pa bzhin du /
NK076(mu)001:6135: sgrib pa phra rags thams cad spangs pa'i shul du
NK076(mu)001:6136: spong byed gnyen po'i ye shes kyang chos kyi dbyings
NK076(mu)001:6137: su zhi ste brten dang brten pa'i ye shes kyang
NK076(mu)001:6138: rgyun chad pa'i phyir gzigs bya gzigs byed med la
NK076(mu)001:6139: / brtags pa gzugs kyi sku ni /
NK076(mu)001:6140: sngon du bsod nams kyi tshogs mi 'gag pa'i 'bras
NK076(mu)001:6141: bu'am rmi lam gyi 'phen pa tsam gyis gdul bya
NK076(mu)001:6144: sangs rgyas dngos ni chos kyi sku la bya //
NK076(mu)001:6145: de la mi rtog mnga' yang smon lam mthus //
NK076(mu)001:6146: gzugs sku rnam gnyis gdul bya'i zhing khams khyab //
NK076(mu)001:6147: ces gsungs pa'i phyir zhes zer to //
NK076(mu)001:6149: ci ye shes de nyid rang log nas rgyun chad dam /
NK076(mu)001:6150: gnyen po gzhan zhig gis rgyun chad drang /
NK076(mu)001:6151: dang po ltar yang mi 'thad de sgrib pa spangs
NK076(mu)001:6152: pa'i rig tsam gyi rdzas yang mtha' thug med du
NK076(mu)001:6154: gal te sangs rgyas kyi sa na rig tsam yang med do zhes kyang brjod par mi nus te /
NK076(mu)001:6155: de ltar na khyed kyis sangs rgyas de bems po yin par thal zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:6156: gnyis pa ltar na yang ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:6157: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis gnyen por gyur pa'i chos gzhan mi srid pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:6158: gtan tshigs ma grub na yang gnyen po thug med du 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:6159: de lta bu'i grub mtha' ngan pa des ni sangs
NK076(mu)001:6160: rgyas kyi yon tan la bkur pa zhes btab cing
NK076(mu)001:6161: lam gyi 'bad pa'ang don med du 'gyur ro /
NK076(mu)001:6164: ye shes med na byang chub 'phel med 'grib pa
NK076(mu)001:6165: med rgyal mtsho 'dra ba'i sangs rgyas chos kyang med
NK076(mu)001:6167: yang ye shes de ni de bzhin gshegs /
NK076(mu)001:6168: bsgrub bya'i chos dang de ldan phyir /
NK076(mu)001:6172: ye shes ye shes khyad par che //
NK076(mu)001:6173: ye shes ldan pas yod med shes //
NK076(mu)001:6177: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi don gyi dbang de
NK076(mu)001:6178: lta bu mkhyen nas sems can rnams la chos ston
NK076(mu)001:6179: par mdzad do // ces pa la sogs pa'i lung du ma bzhugs so //
NK076(mu)001:6180: gnyis pa rgyun bcas pa la'ang gnyis /
NK076(mu)001:6184: sangs rgyas kyis ni rdo rje lta bu ting nge
NK076(mu)001:6185: sgrib pa spangs pa'i lag rjes su ye shes rgyun
NK076(mu)001:6187: de las kyang kun rdzob mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi yul dang yul can du gzigs te /
NK076(mu)001:6188: sngar rgyun chad bkag pa'i lung gis grub po zhes zer to //
NK076(mu)001:6190: sangs rgyas kyis sa yi ye shes de nyid chos can /
NK076(mu)001:6192: kun rdzob yul du byed pa'i phyir //
NK076(mu)001:6193: so sor skye bo bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:6194: de'i lan du mkhas pa kha cig snang tsam yul
NK076(mu)001:6195: du byed kyang yul du mi 'dzin pas 'khrul par
NK076(mu)001:6196: mi 'gyur na ci sto ste khyab pa ma grub
NK076(mu)001:6197: ces ze ba'ang mi rigs te /
NK076(mu)001:6198: de ltar na sangs rgyas kyi ye shes de spang pa phyogs gcig par thal ste /
NK076(mu)001:6199: zhen yul la 'khrul pa'i log shes spang kyang /
NK076(mu)001:6200: snang yul la 'khrul pa'i log shes ma spangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:6201: ji skad du lung mdo las kyang /
NK076(mu)001:6202: yang dag sangs rgyas chos kyi sku //
NK076(mu)001:6203: 'dres pa med cing snang ba med //
NK076(mu)001:6205: yang ye shes dam pa bdag med pas //
NK076(mu)001:6206: snang ba med pas ma gzigs so //
NK076(mu)001:6209: dper na mi shi de yis 'gro rgyu med pa bzhin /
NK076(mu)001:6210: rgyu des de ni mya ngan 'das zhes rab du brjod /
NK076(mu)001:6211: ces pa la sogs pas lung du ma bzhugs pas so //
NK076(mu)001:6212: rang lugs ni ye shes rgyun chad ma chad kyi
NK076(mu)001:6213: sgro bskur dang bral ba'i ngo bo nyid kyis tshul
NK076(mu)001:6214: gyis snang stong dbyer med du gzigs te /
NK076(mu)001:6216: snying po stong nyid gcig med ye mkhyen rang rigs thugs //
NK076(mu)001:6217: dmigs bya dmigs byed med par dran pa rang dbang sgyur //
NK076(mu)001:6219: de nyid la brtsad pa spang ba ni /
NK076(mu)001:6220: de ltar na'ang sangs rgyas kyi thugs rjes yul du byas nas gzigs sam /
NK076(mu)001:6223: dang po ltar na sangs rgyas gzung 'dzin can du thal /
NK076(mu)001:6224: yul dang yul can dbyung ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:6225: 'dod na rgyud dag ma yin par thal /
NK076(mu)001:6228: yang yul du ma byas par gzigs na mig gis kyang sgra thos pa thal /
NK076(mu)001:6229: yul du ma byas kyang gzigs pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:6231: yang sangs rgyas nyid 'khrul bar thal //
NK076(mu)001:6232: med pa gzigs pa'i phyir nam mkha' la skra shad 'dzings snang bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:6233: dbyer med du gzigs pa'ang mi 'thad de /
NK076(mu)001:6234: gzigs bya gzigs byed du 'gal lo zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:6236: sngon gyi mkhas pa kha cig na 'da' rag na re /
NK076(mu)001:6237: yul du byas shing sgros mi 'dor shing ma byas zhes skur ba mi 'debs te /
NK076(mu)001:6238: yul dang yul can dbyer med du gzigs gsung /
NK076(mu)001:6239: dbyer med la gzigs bya gzigs byed 'thad de byas pa la /
NK076(mu)001:6240: gzigs bya gzigs byed tha dad du /
NK076(mu)001:6242: dbyer med du lhangs kyis rtogs pa de kho na thugs rje chen po skyes pa yin te /
NK076(mu)001:6243: phan pa kun gyi gzhir gyur pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:6245: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med gcig rtogs na /
NK076(mu)001:6246: thugs rje skye zhes de la bya //
NK076(mu)001:6248: 'o na thugs rje dang ye shes khyad ci yod zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:6249: dbyer med du lhag gis rtogs pa ni ye shes yin la /
NK076(mu)001:6250: de de gnyis ka nyid phan pa thams cad kyi gzhir gyur pa'i dngos nas thugs rje'o gsung lo //
NK076(mu)001:6252: re thugs rje'i ngo bo la skye bya skye byed
NK076(mu)001:6253: med kyang gdul bya'i ngos la snang ba mi 'gal
NK076(mu)001:6254: te / bzhin dang me long bzhin no skad /
NK076(mu)001:6255: lha rje chen nya ri po ni /
NK076(mu)001:6257: dog par 'khyer ba gnyis yin gsungs /
NK076(mu)001:6258: dang po ni yul du byas nas kyang gzigs /
NK076(mu)001:6260: dbyer med du yang gzigs ces bya'o //
NK076(mu)001:6261: dang po ltar na sangs rgyas gzung 'dzin can du mi 'gyur ram zhe na /
NK076(mu)001:6262: mi 'gyur te yul du byas la ris med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:6264: mdo mgon med pa yi 'jig rten rnams //
NK076(mu)001:6265: mkhyen te thugs rjes gdung pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:6267: skad dog par 'khyer mnga' slas ba ni /
NK076(mu)001:6269: gzigs yul ni don dam mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi
NK076(mu)001:6270: ji lta ba rang bzhin med par nam mkha' ltar
NK076(mu)001:6271: gzigs / kun rdzob mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis chos
NK076(mu)001:6272: can ji snyed pa ma 'dres pa pad+ma'i 'dab ma
NK076(mu)001:6273: gzigs / ltar gzigs / yongs rdzogs mkhyen pa'i ye
NK076(mu)001:6274: shes kyis snang stong dbyer med pa chu zla ltar
NK076(mu)001:6275: gzigs / ltar gzigs / gzigs so // yang sems
NK076(mu)001:6276: can gyi sdug bsngal nyams su myong nas gzigs sam
NK076(mu)001:6277: gzigs / ltar gzigs / gzigs so // / ma myong par gzigs /
NK076(mu)001:6278: gnyis pa ltar na mig gis kyang sgra shes par thal /
NK076(mu)001:6279: dang po ltar na sangs rgyas dang sems can khyad med du 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)001:6280: zhe na lan ni kha cig slas na re /
NK076(mu)001:6281: ming yang mi 'dzin pa'i tshul du gzigs te /
NK076(mu)001:6282: des na nyams su myong pa kun mkhyen ma yin par gsal /
NK076(mu)001:6283: mi 'dzin pas khyad med du 'gyur pa gsal gsung lo //
NK076(mu)001:6285: nyams su myong pa mi rtogs pa'i tshul du gzigs te /
NK076(mu)001:6286: dper na mngon shes dang ldan pa gcig gi drung
NK076(mu)001:6287: du skyes bu zhig gnyid kyi 'khrul pas sdug bsngal
NK076(mu)001:6288: ba mngon shes kyi yul du myong yang bden zhen
NK076(mu)001:6292: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs rnam kun mkhyen //
NK076(mu)001:6293: ma grub blo la rtags grub gzigs /
NK076(mu)001:6294: dper na bus bu chung lta bu'i ming dpyad pas khrom mthong bzhin //
NK076(mu)001:6295: bus pa rang gi rtags bsreg bzhin //
NK076(mu)001:6297: mgo bsgre yang byar rung ste /
NK076(mu)001:6298: skyes bu zhig la rmi lam du mdze byung ba
NK076(mu)001:6299: mngon shes can gyis mngon shes kyi yul du shes
NK076(mu)001:6301: shes na dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal yang thams cad mkhyen pas shes so //
NK076(mu)001:6302: nyams su myong zhe na khyed kyi yang mtshungs so //
NK076(mu)001:6303: myong na khyed med du thal zhing /
NK076(mu)001:6304: ma myong na thams cad mkhyen pa bud ce na /
NK076(mu)001:6305: der yang myong na khyad med du thal zhing //
NK076(mu)001:6306: ma myong na mngon shes bud do //
NK076(mu)001:6307: des mi mtshungs te dngos po la mdze med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:6309: mtshungs te yang dag par sdug bsngal med pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)001:6310: lam don med du thal zhe na gnyid sad pa don med du thal zhes bya ste /
NK076(mu)001:6311: tshangs pas kyang dgag mi spyod do //
NK076(mu)001:6312: gnyis pa gzigs nas thugs rje skye tshul ni /
NK076(mu)001:6315: rtag rgyun rang bzhin shugs gsol dang //
NK076(mu)001:6316: yul dang phrad pas 'byung par snang //
NK076(mu)001:6317: zhes pa'i don gyis bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)001:6318: rtag pa rgyun du thugs rje skye ba ni chu'i rgyun lta bu'o //
NK076(mu)001:6319: rang bzhin shugs kyi thugs rje skye ba ni nyi ma dang zer lta bu'o //
NK076(mu)001:6320: yul dang phrad pas thugs rje skye ba ni mdzangs
NK076(mu)001:6321: bu med pa spyod log byed pa mthong ba lta
NK076(mu)001:6322: bu'o // gsum pa skyes nas 'gro don mdzad tshul la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)001:6323: rten can bram ze mchod sdong grub pa lta bu /
NK076(mu)001:6324: gyi don byed par 'dod pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:6325: rten med drang srong smod pa grub pa lta bu /
NK076(mu)001:6326: gyi don byed par 'dod pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:6327: ngo bo nyid kyi don byed par nam mkha' lta bu /
NK076(mu)001:6330: rgya gar gyi ru seng ge bzang po bod kyi
NK076(mu)001:6331: 'bri mtshams chos kyi zhang shes rab bla ma'i 'dod
NK076(mu)001:6332: / chos kyi sku nam mkha' lta bu la brten nas longs sku sprin lta bu 'byung /
NK076(mu)001:6333: de la brten nas sprul sku char gyi rgyun lta bu byung nas /
NK076(mu)001:6334: 'gro ba lo tog lta bu smin par mdzad pa yin te /
NK076(mu)001:6335: sangs rgyas kyi sku mtshan gyi me tog la dpe byad bzang po'i 'bras bu spras pa dang /
NK076(mu)001:6336: zhing khams dang bkod pa phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan zhing /
NK076(mu)001:6337: lha dang lha mo rol zhing spyod pa yang yod pas don byed zer ro //
NK076(mu)001:6339: thug po bkod pa'i rgyal ba yang //
NK076(mu)001:6340: bde gshegs snying po bzhugs pas na //
NK076(mu)001:6341: de yis 'gro ba mi smin phyir //
NK076(mu)001:6342: gzugs skur bstan nas tshogs lam brjod //
NK076(mu)001:6344: rten med kyi don mdzad pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:6345: chos kyi sku la gnyen po sangs rgyas kyi ye
NK076(mu)001:6346: shes rten dang rten pa'i rgyun dang bcas pa med
NK076(mu)001:6347: ste / dper na bsreg bya shing zad pas bsreg byed me'ang zad pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)001:6348: gzugs sku gnyis la sogs pa gdul bya'i ngo bo la snang pa tsam yin gyis /
NK076(mu)001:6349: sangs rgyas dngos ni ma yin te /
NK076(mu)001:6351: sangs rgyas dngos ni chos kyi sku la bya //
NK076(mu)001:6352: de la rtog mi mnga' yang smon lam mthus /
NK076(mu)001:6353: gzugs sku rnam gnyis gdul bya'i zhing khams khyab ces pa dang /
