NK076(mu)001:6355: srid pa dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams
NK076(mu)001:6356: cad gzhi dang brten ci yang med pa las snang
NK076(mu)001:6358: ngo bo rgya gar gyi ru bu ta g+hu ya /
NK076(mu)001:6359: bod kyi zur me nyag bzhed pas /
NK076(mu)001:6360: nyid kyi don mdzad pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:6361: gong ltar brten can gyi don byed ces sgros mi dogs /
NK076(mu)001:6362: rten med kyi don byed ces skur pa mi 'debs te /
NK076(mu)001:6363: sangs rgyas kyi sa ni rten can dang brten med cha gnyis mi zhugs pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)001:6364: gsang sngags ngo bo nyid kyis don mdzad pa yin te /
NK076(mu)001:6365: ji ltar na snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sems yin la /
NK076(mu)001:6366: sems nyid gsang sngags kyi ngo bo ye nas gnas shing /
NK076(mu)001:6367: rtogs pa dang ldan pa'i blo la snang ba de
NK076(mu)001:6368: nyid kyis dbyer med kyi don dam gsal bar byed
NK076(mu)001:6370: lam rim rtogs dang ldan pa'i blo rnams la //
NK076(mu)001:6371: dngos po sna tshogs sems gsang sngags //
NK076(mu)001:6372: nges lung yin phyir chos tshul ston //
NK076(mu)001:6374: bde gshegs khro phug pa ni /
NK076(mu)001:6375: 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad sems yin la /
NK076(mu)001:6376: sems nyid la yod med rtag chad /
NK076(mu)001:6377: bya rtsol la sogs pa rang gzhan gyis rnam par dag pa'i rang byung gi ye shes yin te /
NK076(mu)001:6378: de lta bu'i sems nyid de thams cad du ma 'gags par snang nas /
NK076(mu)001:6379: des gdul bya dang ji ltar mthun pa bzhin du /
NK076(mu)001:6381: chos thams cad rang byung gi sems chen por 'dus la /
NK076(mu)001:6382: de nyid thams cad du snang zhing don byed pas
NK076(mu)001:6383: na ngo bo nyid kyi don byed pa ces de
NK076(mu)001:6384: la bzhed te / ji skad du /
NK076(mu)001:6385: gnyis med thugs rje chen po ni //
NK076(mu)001:6386: mdzad pa cing yang mi 'gogs ste //
NK076(mu)001:6388: yang stong nyid nam mkha'i rang bzhin la /
NK076(mu)001:6389: sprul pa bye ba cir yang snang //
NK076(mu)001:6392: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK076(mu)001:6393: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK076(mu)001:6394: 'gro ba'i don rnams bsam mi khyab //
NK076(mu)001:6396: de rnams kyis shes bya 'bras bu'i don bshad zin to //
NK076(mu)001:6397: gsang don bdud rtsi'i rol mtsho bden pa'i chu rgyun dri med ro ldan pa //
NK076(mu)001:6398: bdag blo gus pa'i snyim pas yongs blangs blo'i pad+mo tshim byas shing /
NK076(mu)001:6399: rigs lam ge sar 'dab ma rnam rgyal de gang 'gro ba'i gsos gyur phyir //
NK076(mu)001:6400: sngon phyogs mkhas rig dbus 'dir rigs 'phags dri bsung mtshungs med yin //
NK076(mu)001:6401: yang dag kun khyab 'od zer bye ba yis //
NK076(mu)001:6402: ma rtog log rtog the tshom tshang tshing dag /nges par bsal nas 'phags lam snang byed pa //
NK076(mu)001:6403: bden pa'i ngag 'di spyi bos bslang par rigs //
NK076(mu)001:6404: phyi ma'i dus na'ang blo gsal skye bo dag /nga yi rigs lam me tog 'phreng 'di la //
NK076(mu)001:6406: 'jug yul nges pa'i dga' ba mchog du skye //
NK076(mu)001:6407: rigs ldan bzang po'i rjes skyes gzhon nu dag /rigs nor lang tsho'i grags pas ma 'phrogs par //
NK076(mu)001:6408: dus ring thos bsam blo gros sbyongs shig dang //
NK076(mu)001:6409: 'dzam bu'i rgyal mtshan rtse mor mngon par 'gyur //
NK076(mu)001:6410: de sang rgyal po'i bca' khrims nyams 'gyur zhing //
NK076(mu)001:6411: lung rigs 'dor ba skye bo'i tshogs mang gis //
NK076(mu)001:6412: ci bder spyod la rang dgar byed rnams kyi //
NK076(mu)001:6413: gsal byed bdun pa'i yid 'phrog ma gyur cig /bdag kyang deng nas tshe rabs kun tu yang //
NK076(mu)001:6414: lung rigs 'brel don bdun pas mda' bkang ste /
NK076(mu)001:6415: 'phags bden nges pa'i don la reg byed cing //
NK076(mu)001:6416: bshad rtsom rtsod po'i sgyu rtsal 'phel gyur cig /gal te rgyal ba'i gsungs la bdag blo yis //
NK076(mu)001:6417: ma nges ma grub log par drangs ba'i skyon //
NK076(mu)001:6418: skye bo'i rgyud la srid mtha' mi khegs phyir //
NK076(mu)001:6419: chos kyi rje btsun bla ma nyid la bshags //
NK076(mu)001:6420: 'bad pa las thob bsod nams 'bras bu gang //
NK076(mu)001:6421: rjes 'jug shes rab dbang po rgyal gyur cig /mi shes log sde'i tshogs kun pham byas te //
NK076(mu)001:6422: bstan pa yang dag yun ring gnas gyur cig /rnal
NK076(mu)001:6423: 'byor chen po'i rgyud rdo rje sems dpa'i sgyu 'phrul
NK076(mu)001:6424: d+r+wa ba'i don bsdus pa'i man ngag mkhas pa chen
NK076(mu)001:6425: po pradz+ny+aa pra ba'i zhabs kyi rdul spyi bos blangs
NK076(mu)001:6426: shing / skyes thob kyi shes rab phra mos lung
NK076(mu)001:6427: dang rigs pa'i gnas la blo cung zad phyogs pa
NK076(mu)001:6428: shing / / shar rig par smra ba /
NK076(mu)001:6430: jo sras bsod nams dpal gyis gong thugs la zhog mdzod bka' drin che /
NK076(mu)001:6431: mkhas pa'i skye bo gzhan dag dang bla ma /
NK076(mu)001:6432: ma'i gsung rnams nyer bar blangs te /
NK076(mu)001:6433: rang gi 'thad phyogs lung rigs kyi grub pa /
NK076(mu)001:6434: 'ga' zhig yang ston pa shes rab kyi skul nas /
NK076(mu)001:6435: bkod cing sbyar gra'i snying mdo lha khang du /
